\id LUK - Abureni 
\h A̠luk 
\toc1 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ A̠luk Age̠ Bho̠ 
\toc2 A̠luk 
\toc3 A̠luk 
\mt2 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ 
\mt1 A̠luk 
\mt2 Age̠ Bho̠ 
\iot Otighom 
\ip Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ A̠luk Age̠ Bho̠ na̠ a̠leriom agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ Witenemeni ebhugh Izre̠l na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠ma-ra̠nwunom. A̠luk age̠ ma̠a̠, E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠rileghom A̠zizo̠s ma̠ obhin ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba oruom ronyigoiny (A̠luk 4:18), sa̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ imuzo na̠ okpon igbirigbir ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠kparama ado̠l i̠te̠i̠. O̠mar o̠ge̠ omutiom ezin ola̠ o̠tu̠n obo ibo d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire ta̠ A̠luk, okunukun d̠a̠ ri̠pu̠r aru̠mu̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ ya̠ i̠gba igboloma̠ ma̠ eruoma̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ okunugiom bho̠, ma̠ igiel wa̠ i̠na a̠bhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠. Onin o̠ge̠d̠ire onon agba a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire Rogir Ogbo Ogir bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ologi-ima̠ra̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Akrai̠st a̠bhin asu̠, sa̠ asi̠saragi̠an d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠man ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. I̠wal re̠kal od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ (d̠a̠ E̠mu̠ 1 ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ E̠mu̠ 2, na̠ d̠a̠ E̠mu̠ 9 ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ E̠mu̠ 19) ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠a̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n ku̠ku̠m. I̠nye̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ aso̠r itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ma̠zua̠n rokponom ro̠nana bho̠ d̠a̠ i̠mara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ ogir i̠gbara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ Otu-a̠siseiny bho̠, na̠ ra̠sidogh Ob̠eb̠i O̠ni̠ Asameria̠ bho̠ na̠ Obhebhia̠n O̠nyi̠ bho̠. O̠ge̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠siseiny, na̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ilei abar i̠te̠i̠, na̠ ogir ya̠ anwani̠ igir d̠a̠ erile-a̠duom ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 Otighom \ior (1:1-4)\ior* 
\io1 I̠mara na̠ igiel i̠gbara ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m na̠ A̠zizo̠s \ior (1:5—2:52) \ior* 
\io1 Erile-a̠duom ta̠ Azo̠n Owurma̠mu̠m bho̠ \ior (3:1-20)\ior* 
\io1 Owura̠ amu̠m na̠ ad̠agi̠an ya̠ u̠d̠agi̠an A̠zizo̠s bho̠ \ior (3:21—4:13)\ior* 
\io1 A̠zizo̠s a̠rile ma̠ erile-a̠duom d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mutiom e̠ma d̠a̠ Agalili \ior (4:14—9:50)\ior* 
\io1 Ob̠eton d̠a̠ Agalili ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m \ior (9:51—19:27)\ior* 
\io1 Esi-a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wekunuguma̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ aka A̠zeruse̠le̠m \ior (19:28—23:56)\ior* 
\io1 Ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ Omugh, imutuma̠, na̠ obhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ \ior (24:1-53)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 E! Wa̠ a̠lei abar A̠tiofilo̠s, a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom na̠ e̠ge̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ omuzoghod̠iom d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠a̠ i̠yar,  
\v 2 ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠pu̠r ronyob̠a̠ bho̠ i̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ inigha̠ i̠yar bho̠.  
\v 3 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, agu̠o̠ bho̠ ami̠ na̠ amar a̠bhin obhel a̠lelegi ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ka̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, akpe̠ ami̠ ma̠ o̠ge̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n oselegi onigha̠ onyom,  
\v 4 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ amar a̠loghom iya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠, ma̠ d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ anwa bho̠. 
\s1 Ogua̠n I̠mara ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m 
\p  
\v 5 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ E̠ro̠d aro̠ ma̠ O̠li̠la ebhugh A̠zudia̠, okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Azakaraya d̠a̠ ebu rokur ta̠ Abi̠za aro̠. E̠li̠zabe̠t ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ eka̠ ola̠ eghun ta̠ Ero̠n.  
\v 6 I̠wal awa irugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ikoko ma̠ eb̠la̠ roloko na̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠; e̠kal ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m awa na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 7 Ya̠a̠ awa o̠nyi̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, ezin bho̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t aro̠ ma̠ e̠marani̠. Awa na̠ e̠mar eten ikei-a̠nwunom. 
\p  
\v 8 Igiel bho̠ a̠gir ate̠i̠ ebu rokur ta̠ Azakaraya ma̠ ogir ogir-okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ Otuta̠zib̠a̠ bho̠,  
\v 9 sa̠ awa irobh okob̠a̠ ibhin i̠so̠n Azakaraya ma̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ighiom i̠di̠ar rokur bho̠, ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ o̠su̠o̠m i̠tani̠ ed̠u-e̠nu̠nu̠.\f + \fr 1:9 \fq I̠tani̠: \ft I̠tani̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠. I̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ na̠ ebhur ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠, ya̠ na̠ o̠bhu̠gi̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ aru̠mu̠gh; na̠ obhin na̠ o̠ko̠l i̠ko̠l.\f* 
\v 10 Igiel bho̠ a̠lei o̠su̠o̠m i̠tani̠ ed̠u-e̠nu̠nu̠ bho̠, eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n bho̠, i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ etire na̠ esiseiny. 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠mutuma̠ i̠na d̠a̠ agba od̠iom enwen i̠ko̠l i̠tani̠ ed̠u-e̠nu̠nu̠ bho̠.  
\v 12 Igiel bho̠ Azakaraya abi̠gh orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ Azakaraya a̠kpa̠ra̠noma̠, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh i̠na.  
\v 13 Ya̠a̠, orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: “Azakaraya, ko oghil a̠rugugu; na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n a̠siseiny d̠oyom. Ani̠ d̠oyom E̠li̠zabe̠t ta̠ amar olobhiri o̠nyi̠ a̠nigha̠ nya̠m, sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠ghol i̠na ma̠ Azo̠n.  
\v 14 I̠na ta̠ a̠bhin a̠libhon ologi na̠ ibo a̠ruom anwa, sa̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhon ologi d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠mara d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 15 I̠na ta̠ abu̠gh d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠. I̠na ko o̠d̠a d̠o̠ na̠ o̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min ya̠ na̠ epuru ma̠ o̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ ta̠ obhin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, omuzoghod̠i d̠a̠ okurogh, kisa̠ ta̠ o̠mar i̠na.  
\v 16 I̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom Izre̠l ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ eru d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠awa.  
\v 17 I̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠ru na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien e̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠limon ya̠ I̠lai̠za a̠rughom bho̠, a̠tulugi ma̠ rologi ta̠ ronweni na̠ ro̠we̠de̠, na̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠awa; sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ bho̠ ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ erugh a̠ghud̠um igielake̠, na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ Azakaraya a̠pura̠n orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ abar onon, i̠se̠n wa̠ ani̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ ami̠ na̠ o̠kpo̠ bho̠?”  
\v 19 Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ A̠gebre̠l. Ami̠ na̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ I̠na a̠ruom ami̠ ma̠ o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n onigha̠ oyom.  
\v 20 Nagha, anwa ko orue mu a̠fugh abar tu̠tu̠n ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite bho̠; ezin bho̠, anwa na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠ami̠ ya̠ ta̠ emite d̠a̠ obhel bho̠ na̠ o̠to̠ oguri bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 21 Igiel bho̠ a̠nwunom na̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ Azakaraya bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n o̠bi̠gh ma̠ i̠na na̠ aro̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.\fig Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m d̠a̠ amu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s|alt="Herod's Temple at the time of Jesus Christ" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 1:21" copy="LB00250" ref="1:21" \fig* 
\v 22 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠mite a̠ru bho̠, i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, sa̠ awa iloghom ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ abi̠gh aghi̠m d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ i̠tu̠o̠gho̠m i̠tu̠o̠gho̠m ya̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ ofugh abar omutiom. 
\p  
\v 23 Obhel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir a̠muzoghod̠iom d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ya̠ u̠to̠ unigha̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ten a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 24 Na̠ obia̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠mumor, sa̠ a̠bhin ogho uwetire aro̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ o̠yo̠.  
\v 25 Sa̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “I̠se̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠kpon ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom.” 
\s1 Ogua̠n I̠mara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 26 Igiel bho̠ eghun ta̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠lei odin uwetire bho̠, sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠ruom orileduom d̠o̠yo̠ A̠gebre̠l, ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Anazare̠t e̠ma ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ Agalili,  
\v 27 ka̠ o̠bi̠ghan e̠kar o̠nyani̠, ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠meri, ola̠ odi o̠nyi̠ eghun ta̠ A̠devidi, ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠, na̠ a̠sibh obhin ani̠.  
\v 28 Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ A̠meri a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ a̠bheleguma̠ ma̠ anwa o, anwa wa̠ e̠no̠gho̠man na̠ e̠te̠i̠ bho̠! Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ od̠i na̠ anwa.” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ ikpo a̠fugh d̠o̠yo̠ i̠lo̠gh e̠mi̠ i̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠ ma̠ A̠meri, sa̠ i̠na aru̠ru̠an a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ezin ipelegima̠ bho̠.  
\v 30 Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠meri, ko oghil a̠rugugu, e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ anwa.  
\v 31 Anwa ta̠ a̠mumor amar olobhiri o̠nyi̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠ghol a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 32 I̠na ta̠ abu̠gh e̠mi̠ sa̠ ta̠ obhelegi i̠na ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠. Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ i̠kasi̠ o̠li̠le̠ma e̠ma o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ A̠devidi,  
\v 33 sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rileghom otu ta̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠, ad̠u̠a ma̠ amu̠m a̠ten amu̠m; ekunuguma̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠.” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠meri a̠pura̠n orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Abar onon ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠mite, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ ta̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ olobhiri-o̠ni̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠sor a̠ru ra̠ a̠mutuma̠ nyam, sa̠ a̠limon ta̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠ ta̠ a̠ghughuom anwa; ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠nyi̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ wa̠ ta̠ o̠mar bho̠, ta̠ obhelegi ma̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 36 Kpone, E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠ghisia̠n d̠oyom eka̠ na̠ a̠mumor olobhiri-o̠nyi̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n i̠na na̠ akpo̠ bho̠. Ughol gha̠n i̠na ma̠ a̠d̠ien ma̠ i̠na e̠marani̠, ya̠a̠ onon odin uwetire i̠na od̠i na̠ eghun.  
\v 37 Ezin bho̠, abar ola̠ akpar a̠pu ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ogir bo̠.” 
\p  
\v 38 Sa̠ A̠meri awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠. Omuzughod̠iom onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa i̠gba bho̠.” Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ awe̠le̠man i̠na a̠ten ad̠u̠a. 
\s1 A̠meri agi̠ ka̠ a̠zua̠n E̠li̠zabe̠t 
\p  
\v 39 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠meri a̠nugia̠n a̠kokod̠ia̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ebhugh a̠rugugum\f + \fr 1:39 \fq A̠rugugum: \ft A̠d̠ien a̠rugugum i̠nye̠n bo̠ d̠a̠ A̠b̠ureni; i̠nye̠n od̠i ka̠ i̠gbara rigu. \f* d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠,  
\v 40 sa̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Azakaraya sa̠ a̠bheleguma̠ ma̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t.  
\v 41 Igiel bho̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t amu̠gho̠n ibheleguma̠ ta̠ A̠meri bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ wa̠ ta̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ bho̠, wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu-imara d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ a̠nyegia̠n, sa̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu ta̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠muzo.  
\v 42 Sa̠ a̠bhin okoroko ola̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ anwa a̠pu d̠a̠ e̠ma ra̠ anwani̠, na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ o̠nyi̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu-imara d̠oyom bho̠!  
\v 43 Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ e̠no̠gho̠man iya̠ o̠ko̠no̠n na̠ eru ra̠ e̠te̠i̠ ami̠, ma̠ ola̠ onweni ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠zua̠n ami̠?  
\v 44 Agu̠o̠ okoroko ibheleguma̠ d̠oyom a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ a̠to d̠ami̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ okurogh d̠ami̠ bho̠ a̠bhin a̠libhon ologi a̠nyegia̠n.  
\v 45 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ i̠na wa̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠muzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠.” 
\s1 Aso̠r itutumeni ta̠ A̠meri 
\p  
\v 46 Sa̠ A̠meri a̠fugh ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Eloghoma̠n ozu d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠. 
\q1  
\v 47 E̠mu̠gh d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠bhon ologi na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠ami̠, 
\q1  
\v 48 ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠loghom ado̠l o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠. 
\q1 A̠b̠eton i̠se̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, 
\q1 ad̠u̠a ma̠ amu̠m a̠ten amu̠m ta̠ obhelegi ami̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 wa̠ na̠ otutumeni bho̠, 
\q1  
\v 49 ezin bho̠, i̠na Wa̠ A̠limon i̠bu̠gh ipu bho̠ na̠ a̠gir ibom i̠di̠ar a̠nigha̠ ami̠. 
\q1 E̠tu̠tu̠ bha̠ a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠. 
\q1  
\v 50 Igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eghila̠n i̠na bho̠, 
\q1 ad̠u̠a ma̠ amu̠m a̠ten amu̠m. 
\q1  
\v 51 I̠na na̠ a̠bhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gir ibom i̠di̠ar; 
\q1 i̠na na̠ asasaragi̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠a̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa. 
\q1  
\v 52 I̠na na̠ a̠sorogi ma̠ ogbo i̠rileghom bho̠ d̠a̠ ra̠dila̠de d̠awa, 
\q1 ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ a̠b̠egion ogbo ya̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 53 I̠na na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ bho̠ ma̠ od̠e olegha̠n, 
\q1 sa̠ a̠ze ma̠ aru̠li̠la bho̠ ma̠ oyel obhobho i̠kpo̠. 
\q1  
\v 54 I̠na aru̠ru̠an okpon igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠ abhe̠l ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ Izre̠l, 
\q1  
\v 55 na̠ Ebraham na̠ anwi̠i̠ny igha̠la̠ d̠o̠yo̠ kid̠ud̠ul, 
\q1 ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ro̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar bho̠.” 
\m  
\v 56 A̠meri a̠bhin agu̠o̠ i̠sar uwetire aro̠ na̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t ka̠ a̠mula̠ a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠. 
\s1 I̠mara ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m 
\p  
\v 57 Obhel bho̠ eghun ta̠ E̠li̠zabe̠t a̠legha̠n bho̠, sa̠ amar olobhiri o̠nyi̠.  
\v 58 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh na̠ etua̠n i̠na bho̠, na̠ ogbo a̠ghisia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠na ibhon ologi ma̠ d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠kpon i̠na ma̠ ibom igbirigbir bho̠. 
\s1 Oghol a̠d̠ien ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\p  
\v 59 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠lei o̠bhabhanya a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa iru ra̠ oti ipo d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ awa iru ra̠ ogholom o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ Azakaraya,  
\v 60 ya̠a̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “E̠nyi̠! Ta̠ oghol i̠na ma̠ Azo̠n.” 
\p  
\v 61 Sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Eb̠la̠ a̠ghisia̠n d̠inyin, o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ a̠d̠ien obha̠ bo̠.” 
\p  
\v 62 Sa̠ awa ibhin i̠tu̠o̠gho̠m ipura̠n o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ghol o̠nyi̠ bho̠.  
\v 63 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin i̠tu̠o̠gho̠m a̠puru ma̠ ad̠u̠b̠o̠ ola̠ obhin o̠ge̠ abar, sa̠ age̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ Azo̠n.” Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠.  
\v 64 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠ sa̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ akpati̠na, sa̠ a̠nem d̠o̠yo̠ ako̠gi̠na, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, sa̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 65 Sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh d̠a̠ eghighira̠ d̠awa bho̠. Sa̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠ i̠te̠i̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh a̠rugugum A̠zudia̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n.  
\v 66 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba bho̠ ibhin i̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “O̠gbara-o̠nyi̠ onon ta̠ a̠mite aro̠ eka̠?” Agu̠o̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ od̠i na̠ i̠na. 
\s1 Iwowa̠ ta̠ Azakaraya 
\p  
\v 67 Sa̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ Azakaraya a̠muzo, 
\q2 sa̠ i̠na a̠wa̠ ma̠ iwowa̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1  
\v 68 “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠, A̠zib̠a̠ Izre̠l, 
\q2 ezin bho̠, I̠na na̠ a̠zua̠n a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠, ata awa a̠bhin. 
\q1  
\v 69 I̠na na̠ a̠b̠eton o̠bhal itenemeni a̠nigha̠ i̠yar 
\q2 d̠a̠ eghun otu ta̠ A̠devidi ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, 
\q1  
\v 70 agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠rughom a̠riwil e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gua̠n d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ bho̠, 
\q1  
\v 71 ma̠ omiza̠n d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠i̠yar, 
\q2 na̠ d̠a̠ a̠limon ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠su̠a i̠yar bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 72 I̠na aru̠ru̠an i̠zo̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠o̠yo̠, 
\q2 sa̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ okpon igbirigbir a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ibom ro̠we̠de̠ id̠ud̠ul d̠i̠yar, 
\q1  
\v 73 i̠zo̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠d̠ed̠ia̠n na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar Ebraham bho̠: 
\q1  
\v 74 ma̠ otenemeni i̠yar d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠i̠yar, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar ubhin a̠rugugu o̠ko̠l i̠na, 
\q1  
\v 75 ya̠a̠ obhin d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala na̠ ado̠l igielake̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠, 
\q2 ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠i̠yar. 
\q1  
\v 76 Sa̠ anwa, o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, 
\q2 ta̠ obhelegi nyam ma̠ owil ta̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠; 
\q2 ezin bho̠ anwa ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man eten bho̠ onigha̠ o̠yo̠, 
\q1  
\v 77 na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ eloghom abar oten, 
\q2 wa̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ okpon i̠karabh o̠si̠ghe̠ a̠d̠ien a̠ru bho̠, 
\q1  
\v 78 d̠a̠ ebula̠ okpon igbirigbir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠i̠yar, 
\q2 ogogo wa̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ ad̠i̠ro̠ bho̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny amu̠o̠m i̠yar 
\q1  
\v 79 ma̠ onigha̠ e̠b̠alab̠al ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ azi̠m, 
\q2 na̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ omugh bho̠, 
\q1 na̠ orileghom re̠b̠ab̠a a̠sike d̠i̠yar ka̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ eten ekima̠.” 
\p  
\v 80 Sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ a̠bhobh sa̠ aghu̠a d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh. A̠rugh d̠a̠ e̠ghana tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ obhel wa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ Izre̠l bho̠. 
\c 2  
\s1 I̠mara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 1:18-25) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠, sa̠ A̠siza̠\f + \fr 2:1 \fq A̠siza̠: \ft A̠nwunom A̠rom ibhelegi ma̠ o̠li̠le̠ma d̠awa ma̠ A̠siza̠\f* O̠go̠sto̠s alo̠gh oloko ma̠a̠, o̠wal eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpukpu ebhugh A̠rom.  
\v 2 (Onon o̠pu̠r o̠wal a̠nwunom wa̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ amu̠m igiel wa̠ Akwi̠ri̠ni̠o̠s na̠ a̠rileghom ebhugh A̠siria̠.)  
\v 3 Sa̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ka̠ o̠ge̠ a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 4 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ eka̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma Anazare̠t d̠a̠ Agalili a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na ola̠ eghun otu ta̠ A̠devidi.  
\v 5 I̠na ab̠ar na̠ A̠meri, wa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠sibh obhin ani̠ bho̠ a̠bhin agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠wal a̠nwunom bho̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ eghun bho̠ na̠ a̠legha̠n.  
\v 6 D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ awa od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ sa̠ eghun ta̠ A̠meri ake̠ ma̠ ogun.  
\v 7 Sa̠ i̠na amar o̠kpana o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠, olobhiri. Sa̠ a̠bhin a̠rukpe a̠bhurugi i̠na, sa̠ amu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ i̠na d̠a̠ igba̠ ola̠ na̠ obhin na̠ o̠lo̠gh ed̠ia̠n na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ i̠nam, ezin bho̠ e̠kpe̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ otu esul bho̠. 
\s1 Ikponom ro̠nana bho̠ na̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\p  
\v 8 Ikponom ro̠nana e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ e̠sala i̠gho̠gho̠ ola̠ a̠tua̠n, na̠ ekponom i̠nam d̠awa ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n obha̠.\fig Ikponom ro̠nana i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de na̠ ekponom i̠nam d̠awa ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n|alt="Shepherds sitting by fire watcing their flock at night" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 2:8" copy="LB00013" ref="2:8" \fig* 
\v 9 Odi orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠mutuma̠ awa, sa̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ amu̠o̠m awa ma̠ ola̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa.  
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu. Ami̠ ibhin ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ibom a̠libhon ologi ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom a̠ruom inyin.  
\v 11 Na̠ o̠mar Witenemeni bho̠ onigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ e̠ma ta̠ A̠devidi ma̠ a̠didon. I̠na Akrai̠st Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.  
\v 12 Onon ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh a̠nigha̠ inyin: Inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠nyi̠ ola̠ ubhin a̠rukpe ubhurugi, sa̠ u̠mu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ d̠a̠ igba̠ ola̠ na̠ obhin na̠ o̠lo̠gh ed̠ia̠n na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ i̠nam.” 
\p  
\v 13 D̠a̠ awai̠, sa̠ o̠lo̠gh itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny iru ra̠ i̠b̠aragu̠ma ma̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ efugh ma̠a̠, 
\q1  
\v 14 “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny wa̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠pu bho̠, 
\q2 ya̠a̠ ekima̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ a̠de onon a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 15 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ i̠we̠le̠ awa ibhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠, sa̠ ikponom ro̠nana bho̠ odi a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠a̠, “Id̠ighi o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m ka̠ o̠bi̠gh abar onon wa̠ na̠ a̠mite bho̠, wa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠yar bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ awa inugia̠n i̠gi̠ sa̠ i̠bi̠gh A̠meri na̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ na̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠, wa̠ awa i̠mu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ d̠a̠ igba̠ ola̠ na̠ obhin na̠ o̠lo̠gh ed̠ia̠n na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ i̠nam bho̠.  
\v 17 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠bi̠gh o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gba i̠sasaragi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, na̠ iya̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ onon a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠.  
\v 18 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba ya̠ ikponom ro̠nana bho̠ i̠gba inigha̠ awa bho̠. 
\p  
\v 19 Ya̠a̠ A̠meri a̠bhin eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n alo̠gh d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ a̠guri, sa̠ aru̠ru̠an ghan a̠gboloma̠.  
\v 20 Ikponom ro̠nana bho̠ imula̠ iyel, sa̠ itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠na d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh bho̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ u̠gba unigha̠ awa bho̠. 
\p  
\v 21 Oleghemeni o̠bhabhanya a̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠mara bho̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠lei oti ipo o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ ughol i̠na ma̠ A̠zizo̠s, a̠d̠ien wa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠ghol kisa̠ umumor i̠na bho̠. 
\s1 Ubhin A̠zizo̠s o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\p  
\v 22 Obhel wa̠ ate̠i̠ i̠ko̠l o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ozu bho̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi bho̠, sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ na̠ A̠meri ibhin i̠na i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ma̠ ob̠eton o̠yo̠ onigha̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠,  
\v 23 (ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ oloko ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Kerekere o̠kpana olobhiri o̠nyi̠ ma̠ ta̠ ob̠eton onigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠.”)\x - \xo 2:23 \xt E̠d̠u̠a 13:2,12\x* 
\v 24 Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠ko̠l i̠ko̠l o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ozu, ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠to̠ d̠a̠ oloko ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠. I̠di̠ar i̠ko̠l bho̠ bha̠ i̠wal ikpo rokur osege, bo̠d̠o̠ i̠wal ikubh rukpugh. 
\p  
\v 25 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠simio̠n aro̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, ma̠ ola̠ a̠rugh ado̠l igielake̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. I̠na aro̠ na̠ a̠gon Witenemeni bho̠ ma̠ oru ra̠ otenemeni Izre̠l. E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 26 E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba a̠nigha i̠na ma̠ i̠na ko omugh d̠o̠, a̠ten ka̠ i̠na na̠ abi̠gh Witenemeni wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n bho̠.  
\v 27 E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠rileghom i̠na ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ ologi Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Obha̠ onin obhel wa̠ A̠meri na̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ ibhin o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ A̠zizo̠s id̠igh bho̠, ma̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠to̠to̠gi̠ oloko bho̠.  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠simio̠n a̠bube i̠na sa̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 29 “Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠limon bho̠, 
\q2 d̠ighi ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠oyom agi̠ d̠a̠ ekima̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa igua̠n bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 30 A̠rid̠ien d̠ami̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh itenemeni d̠oyom, 
\q2  
\v 31 wa̠ anwa i̠to̠ iguri ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom eb̠la̠ ra̠dede ta̠ e̠bi̠gh bho̠: 
\q1  
\v 32 ma̠ o̠ro̠ e̠b̠alab̠al onigha̠ ogbo o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awa eloghom itenemeni ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ obhin edim onigha̠ a̠nwunom d̠oyom Izre̠l.” 
\p  
\v 33 Ed̠igh ilologia̠n onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s o̠mu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠gba̠ ugboloma̠ i̠na bho̠.  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠simio̠n a̠du ma̠ o̠gho̠r a̠tutumeni awa sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠meri, onweni o̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: “A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ aso̠n o̠nyi̠ onon obhin emel na̠ ob̠etina̠ oruom a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom d̠a̠ Izre̠l, na̠ o̠ro̠ elegh ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ eghel.  
\v 35 Sa̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an e̠wo̠gi̠na ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ologi a̠d̠izo ogbo bho̠ ta̠ eb̠ugh emite. Sa̠ anwa ta̠ aku̠nu̠ ma̠ e̠mi̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ ya̠ ta̠ e̠gu̠b̠an ka̠ alapa ogidi a̠gim ologi d̠oyom awo̠lo̠me̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 36 Owil ani̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Ana, o̠nyani̠ ta̠ Afanu̠e̠l d̠a̠ eghun ta̠ Asa eka̠ aro̠. I̠na a̠d̠um, akpo̠ zighizighi. I̠na awal ilom, sa̠ irugha̠n od̠ua̠l ala ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ owolom d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mugh.  
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ten ekpukele ani̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠um i̠wal e̠wala na̠ inya̠ ala ma̠ igiel bho̠. I̠na na̠ o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ghan d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ ogir ogir, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ako̠l ghan A̠zib̠a, a̠ne ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, a̠siseiny a̠siseiny, a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n.  
\v 38 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa, sa̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Sa̠ agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ egon itenemeni A̠zeruse̠le̠m. 
\p  
\v 39 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ A̠meri na̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ na̠ egir eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ Oloko ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ato̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa imula̠ iyel d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠awa Anazare̠t, d̠a̠ ebhugh Agalili.  
\v 40 Sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ a̠bhobh na̠ alu̠kpo̠ a̠luzu, sa̠ eloghom abar imuzo d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 41 Kerekere ala o̠we̠de̠ na̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ghan d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ka̠ od̠e E̠yal Opel Oten.  
\v 42 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠lei d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ala bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠yal bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ od̠i d̠a̠ od̠ud̠ul bho̠.  
\v 43 E̠yal bho̠ a̠ten, sa̠ awa na̠ emula̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠sobha̠n aro̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, ya̠a̠ awa iloghoma̠n d̠o̠.  
\v 44 Awa na̠ erile ma̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ kisa̠ awa iloghoma̠n ma̠ i̠na bo̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, ezin bho̠, awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ i̠na od̠i ani̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa. Sa̠ awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ rebu a̠ghisia̠n na̠ ra̠tologha̠n d̠awa.  
\v 45 Agu̠o̠ awa o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ awa imula̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ka̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠yo̠.  
\v 46 I̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, kisa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de, d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. I̠na aro̠ na̠ anagha awa, na̠ a̠pura̠n ipupura̠n.  
\v 47 Ilologia̠n ed̠igh eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠na bho̠, d̠a̠ e̠mi̠ amu̠gho̠nyan na̠ awo̠yo̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 48 Obhel awa i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ awa ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠. Sa̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, a̠mite eka̠ ka̠ anwa na̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠yar o̠ko̠no̠n? O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom na̠ ami̠ na̠ obhin ekpoyogh ologi na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan anwa kesikesi.” 
\p  
\v 49 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Inyin u̠tu̠n ere na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan ami̠? Inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ otu O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠, d̠u̠ko̠?”  
\v 50 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ i̠na na̠ agba bho̠. 
\p  
\v 51 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh na̠ awa a̠sor agi̠ d̠a̠ Anazare̠t, sa̠ anagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠awa. Ya̠a̠, oweni d̠o̠yo̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠guri ma̠ iya̠ eko d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 52 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhobh d̠a̠ eloghom abar na̠ d̠a̠ ozu, sa̠ ate̠i̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠. 
\c 3  
\s1 Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ asam eten bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 3:1-12; Amaki̠ 1:1-8; Azo̠n 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Oleghemeni a̠d̠iobh na̠ ogho ala wa̠ A̠siza̠\f + \fr 3:1 \fq A̠siza̠: \ft A̠siza̠ bha̠ a̠d̠ien O̠li̠le̠ma (Ob̠a̠ne̠ma) A̠rom\f* A̠tiberi̠o̠s, o̠li̠le̠ma A̠rom, na̠ a̠rileghom ebhugh bho̠, Apo̠nti̠o̠s Apai̠let aro̠ ma̠ o̠li̠la ebhugh A̠zudia̠, sa̠ E̠ro̠d na̠ a̠rileghom Agalili, odi a̠bin ebhugh bho̠, ya̠a̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ A̠filip sa̠ na̠ a̠rileghom Ituria̠ na̠ Atrakonitis, odi a̠bin ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ Ali̠sani̠as na̠ a̠rileghom A̠bilene, odi a̠bin ebhugh bho̠.  
\v 2 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, Anas na̠ Akai̠afas i̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, sa̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ate̠i̠ Azo̠n o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Azakaraya d̠a̠ e̠ghana.  
\v 3 I̠na a̠rile ma̠ eb̠la̠ eghighira̠ O̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh, na̠ owura̠ amu̠m oleriom ma̠ awa na̠ etiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa e̠te̠i̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 4 ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire ta̠ Ai̠zaya owil bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “Okoroko o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠si na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ e̠ghana bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 ‘I̠tu̠ghu̠mane̠ ma̠ eten ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ eguri, 
\q2 ma̠ eselegi ma̠ reten bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ i̠na. 
\q1  
\v 5 Kerekere ogugua̠ ta̠ ob̠a̠la̠me̠ni̠, 
\q2 kerekere igu na̠ egugum ta̠ ogbo o̠de̠bhe̠me̠ni̠. 
\q1 Sa̠ reten ya̠ ib̠eb̠elegia̠n bho̠ ta̠ oselegi, 
\q2 sa̠ ta̠ otulugi ma̠ rigbogolo reten bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 6 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ ra̠dede bho̠ ta̠ ebi̠gh itenemeni ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.’ ” 
\p  
\v 7 Igiel bho̠ eb̠olob̠ol a̠nwunom na̠ eru d̠a̠ Azo̠n ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠wur awa ma̠ amu̠m bho̠, sa̠ Azo̠n a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin anwi̠i̠ny i̠bho̠ru̠bho̠ru̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar!\f + \fr 3:7 \fq I̠karabh i̠di̠ar: \ft i̠karabh i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠ ibom i̠gagaman ya̠ od̠i ka̠ epulepu, ob̠il na̠ owoghowogh\f* A̠nyen a̠kikiom inyin oghil o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ibom i̠gam ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ na̠ eru bho̠?  
\v 8 Imume ma̠ itu otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ efugh enigha̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ obom o̠we̠de̠ a̠ko Ebraham.’ Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ikputu\f + \fr 3:8 \fq Ikputu: \ft I̠gbaki̠ghe̠; ikpokpogh i̠gbaki̠ghe̠ \f* i̠nye̠n ta̠ eten anwi̠i̠ny enigha̠ ma̠ Ebraham.  
\v 9 Na̠ oguri ma̠ u̠do̠ d̠a̠ igbolo iriren bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ kerekere oriren ola̠ omum d̠o̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i imuma̠ sa̠ ta̠ ogu okoton, orobh o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ anya bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ i̠yar ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠?” 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ Azo̠n awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “I̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ i̠wal rakapa bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ bho̠. I̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠ eka̠ aru̠gi̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 12 Igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠ eka̠ eru ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ owur awa ma̠ amu̠m. Sa̠ awa ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠?” 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko obhin epeleni ma̠ agu̠o̠ usobh otua̠ bho̠,”  
\v 14 Sa̠ idi iweme̠gham bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ya̠a̠ i̠yar ka̠ eka̠, i̠yar ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠?” 
\p I̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko oghum okpoki d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ ebhin; o̠ni̠ ko obhin d̠a̠ igunugha̠ ma̠ eb̠ologiom a̠nwunom abar nyen, ikpoki ya̠ na̠ o̠kpe̠ inyin bho̠ elegha̠n inyin.” 
\p  
\v 15 A̠nwunom bho̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ egon Witenemeni bho̠, sa̠ awa na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ku̠gba ma̠ Azo̠n Witenemeni bho̠\f + \fr 3:15 \fq Witenemeni bho̠: \ft Akrai̠st\f*.  
\v 16 Azo̠n awo̠ran eb̠la̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin amu̠m na̠ a̠wur inyin; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon a̠pu ami̠ na̠ a̠ru. I̠na o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠dila̠de d̠ami̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠gi̠o̠n id̠id̠igh ragbaka d̠o̠yo̠. I̠na ta̠ a̠bhin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ na̠ anya a̠wur inyin.  
\v 17 I̠na na̠ a̠sibh okporoma̠\f + \fr 3:17 \fq Okporoma̠: \ft Okporoma̠ onon ubhin okurogh o̠le̠m. \f* d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠, ma̠ obhin ozeghe, okokod̠i i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ esi eko d̠o̠yo̠ oguri. Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ ab̠i̠r esi ogir bho̠ a̠kpo ma̠ ibhobho bho̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ anya wa̠ od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.”\fig Ozeghe ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ od̠i ka̠ i̠bu̠kpa|alt="Winowing grains" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 3:17" copy="HK00097" ref="3:17" \fig* 
\v 18 Azo̠n a̠bhin a̠d̠izo ro̠nu̠ o̠kpe̠ ya̠ o̠ku̠a a̠kikiom a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. 
\p  
\v 19 D̠a̠ obhel onon, Azo̠n agam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ E̠ro̠d\f + \fr 3:19 \fq E̠ro̠d: \ft O̠li̠lema odi a̠bin d̠a̠ inya̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠rom. (Kpone nyen d̠a̠ o̠gu̠r 1)\f* o̠li̠la ebhugh Agalili, ezin bho̠ i̠na akpakpa ma̠ E̠ro̠di̠as ani̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ a̠bhin, na̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ eb̠la̠ ipa̠n i̠karabh ya̠ i̠na a̠gir.  
\v 20 E̠ro̠d a̠din o̠ku̠a adu̠o̠m Azo̠n d̠a̠ ikoli, sa̠ a̠bhin i̠karabh i̠nye̠n ab̠aram d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠ iyed̠i. 
\s1 Owura̠ amu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 3:13-17; Amaki̠ 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 21 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ na̠ owur eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom amu̠m bho̠, sa̠ uwur ani̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ d̠a̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠siseiny\f + \fr 3:21 \fq I̠na na̠ a̠siseiny: \ft I̠na na̠ aghalam\f* bho̠, sa̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠gurona̠.  
\v 22 Sa̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠sor a̠ru d̠a̠ i̠pulupul ozu ma̠ agu̠o̠ okur osege, sa̠ okoroko ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru ma̠a̠: “Anwa o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ ami̠ itula̠n ibom bho̠, wa̠ ologi d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠bhon na̠ a̠ni̠gha̠ bho̠.” 
\s1 Igba̠iny ro̠we̠de̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 1:1-17) 
\p  
\v 23 A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠lei agu̠o̠ a̠d̠usubh d̠iobh ala d̠a̠ obhel bho̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. A̠nwunom iloghom i̠na ma̠ i̠na o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠, a̠wa̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an o̠ku̠a. 
\li1 A̠zose̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠li̠. 
\q1  
\v 24 E̠li̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amatat. 
\li1 Amatat o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠livai̠. A̠livai̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ame̠lki̠. 
\li1 Ame̠lki̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Azana. Azana o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠. 
\li1  
\v 25 A̠zose̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amatatayas. Amatatayas o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Emo̠si̠. 
\li1 Emo̠si̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Anahu̠m. Anahu̠m o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Esili. 
\li1 Esili o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Anagayi̠.  
\v 26 Anagayi̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amat. 
\li1 Amat o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amatatayas. Amatatayas o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠semeiny. 
\li1 A̠semeiny o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠. A̠zose̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zuda̠. 
\li1  
\v 27 A̠zuda̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Azo̠anan. Azo̠anan o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Are̠sa. 
\li1 Are̠sa o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zorobabe̠l. A̠zorobabe̠l o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ase̠lati̠e̠l. 
\li1 Ase̠lati̠e̠l o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠neri.  
\v 28 A̠neri o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ame̠lki̠. 
\li1 Ame̠lki̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Adi̠. Adi̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠kosam. 
\li1 A̠kosam o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠lmadam. E̠lmadam o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠r. 
\li1  
\v 29 E̠r o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zosu̠a. A̠zosu̠a o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠li̠eza̠. 
\li1 E̠li̠eza̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zorim. A̠zorim o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amatat. 
\li1 Amatat o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠livai̠.  
\v 30 A̠livai̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠simio̠n. 
\li1 A̠simio̠n o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zuda̠. A̠zuda̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠. 
\li1 A̠zose̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zonam. A̠zonam o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠li̠aki̠m. 
\li1  
\v 31 E̠li̠aki̠m o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠melea̠. A̠melea̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ame̠na. 
\li1 Ame̠na o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Amatata. Amatata o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠netan. 
\li1 A̠netan o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi.  
\v 32 A̠devidi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Aze̠si̠. 
\li1 Aze̠si̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Obe̠di̠. Obe̠di̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠boa̠z. 
\li1 A̠boa̠z o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Asalmo̠n. Asalmo̠n o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Anaso̠n. 
\li1  
\v 33 Anaso̠n o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ami̠nadab. 
\li1 Ami̠nadab o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Admin. Admin o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Arni̠.\f + \fr 3:33 \ft Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire bho̠, i̠ge̠ ma̠ Aram e̠we̠le̠man Admin na̠ Arni̠\f* 
\li1 Arni̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠zro̠n. E̠zro̠n o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ape̠re̠zi̠. 
\li1 Ape̠re̠zi̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zuda̠.  
\v 34 A̠zuda̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠. 
\li1 A̠zeko̠pu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Azi̠ki̠. Azi̠ki̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ebraham. 
\li1 Ebraham o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ate̠ra. Ate̠ra o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Anaho̠. 
\li1  
\v 35 Anaho̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ase̠ru̠g. Ase̠ru̠g o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠rewu. 
\li1 A̠rewu o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ape̠le̠g. Ape̠le̠g o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠be̠r. 
\li1 E̠be̠r o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ase̠la.  
\v 36 Ase̠la o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Akayi̠nan. 
\li1 Akayi̠nan o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Afakzad. Afakzad o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ase̠m. 
\li1 Ase̠m o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠nua̠. A̠nua̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Alame̠k. 
\li1  
\v 37 Alame̠k o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ame̠tuse̠la. Ame̠tuse̠la o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠no̠k. 
\li1 E̠no̠k o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Azare̠d. Azare̠d o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ame̠halale̠l. 
\li1 Ame̠halale̠l o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠kenan.  
\v 38 A̠kenan o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Eno̠s. 
\li1 Eno̠s o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ase̠fu̠. Ase̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Adam. 
\li1 Adam o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\c 4  
\s1 Ad̠agi̠an ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 4:1-11; Amaki̠ 1:12-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Agu̠o̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠muzo bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ O̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan. Sa̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠rileghom i̠na ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ e̠ghana.  
\v 2 Eru bho̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠na d̠a̠ eruba̠l ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ya̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠. I̠na na̠ od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ abar eb̠la̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠, sa̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠ sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na. 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ Eru bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, bha̠ d̠ighi o̠gbaki̠ghe̠ onon a̠tenegia̠n ed̠ia̠n.” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: ‘O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ko obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n ku̠ku̠m a̠d̠um.’\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Oloko 8:3\x*” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ Eru bho̠ a̠rileghom i̠na agi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠, sa̠ a̠leriom i̠na d̠a̠ ekud̠i obhel ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠de e̠ma e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 6 Sa̠ Eru bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam eb̠la̠ a̠limon na̠ isosorogia̠n d̠awa. Ezin bho̠ na̠ onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠yi, ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠nigha̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh ami̠ ma̠ ologi.  
\v 7 Oku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ka̠ anwa ikpud̠ia̠n i̠ko̠l ami̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam eb̠la̠ a̠yi.” 
\p  
\v 8 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: ‘Kpud̠ia̠ne ma̠ a̠siseiny Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom ma̠ ako̠l i̠na ku̠ku̠m.’\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Oloko 6:13\x*” 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ Eru bho̠ a̠rileghom i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ a̠bhin i̠na ka̠ amarame̠ni̠ ma̠ esi wa̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠pu d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠. Sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, bha̠ pele ma̠ a̠sor d̠a̠ a̠de.  
\v 10 Ezin bho̠, u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠nugiom itileduom d̠o̠yo̠ 
\q2 ma̠ o̠mar okponom onyom. 
\q1  
\v 11 Awa ta̠ e̠le̠l aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa e̠su̠ar anwa, 
\q2 b̠o̠ka̠ anwa na̠ omel a̠d̠ighia̠nma̠ ma̠ a̠wel d̠oyom d̠a̠ o̠gbaki̠ghe̠.’\x - \xo 4:11 \xt Raso̠r 91:11-12\x*” 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “U̠gba d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: ‘Ko o̠d̠agi̠an Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom.’\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Oloko 6:16\x*” 
\p  
\v 13 Igiel bho̠ Eru bho̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠na awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a na̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ opa̠n igiel ola̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n i̠na ma̠ omula̠ o̠d̠agi̠an o̠yo̠. 
\s1 O̠pu̠r o̠ke̠ ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ Agalili 
\p  
\v 14 Agu̠o̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠muzo bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili. Na̠ obia̠ d̠o̠ sa̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n oghur d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 15 I̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala d̠awa atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ a̠tutumeni i̠na.  
\v 16 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ Anazare̠t, esi bho̠ i̠na aro̠ a̠d̠igh e̠mu̠ bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh d̠awa, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir gha̠n bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ amara ma̠ osen A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.  
\v 17 Sa̠ unigha̠ i̠na ma̠ obhurugho a̠d̠ire ta̠ owil Ai̠zaya. I̠na agbado̠n a̠d̠ire bho̠ sa̠ abi̠gh esi bho̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠:\fig Obhurugho a̠d̠ire|alt="Scroll" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 4:17" copy="HK00150" ref="4:17" \fig* 
\q1  
\v 18 “E̠mu̠gh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ akpasan ami̠, 
\q2 ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠zuom ami̠ ma̠ amu̠nu̠ ma̠ o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba o̠nigha̠ ronyigoiny bho̠. 
\q1 I̠na na̠ a̠ruom ami̠ ma̠ o̠gba ma̠ na̠ o̠kagi̠o̠n igoni bho̠ omutioghom d̠a̠ ikoli d̠awa, 
\q2 na̠ o̠kpagi̠on a̠rid̠ien ogbo ya̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar bho̠, 
\q1 na̠ otenemeni ogbo ya̠ na̠ oponoma̠ bho̠, 
\q2  
\v 19 na̠ o̠gba omutiom ma̠a̠ obhel wa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ta̠ a̠leriom e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠lei.”\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Azaya 61:1-2\x* 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpor a̠d̠ire bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ogir otu u̠gala bho̠, sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de. Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠ igbi ma̠ a̠rid̠ien na̠ ekpon i̠na.  
\v 21 Sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba onigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin u̠mo̠gho̠n ya̠ usen unigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, na̠ omuzoghod̠iom a̠didon d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠inyin!” 
\p  
\v 22 Eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom i̠se̠n i̠na ma̠ ib̠eb̠i. Sa̠ id̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n o̠mu̠gho̠n a̠d̠ien ib̠eb̠i ikpo a̠fugh ya̠ imite d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. Sa̠ awa ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Onon o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh ma̠ inyin ta̠ orogh a̠sidogh onon onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠a̠: ‘Owil, koko ma̠ ozu d̠oyom!’ Sa̠ inyin ta̠ omula̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘Gire ma̠ i̠se̠n d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠oyom ma̠ a̠d̠ien ilologia̠n ya̠ anwa igir d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m bho̠.’ ” 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba alo̠gho̠m ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, owil ogbo e̠ma na̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar.  
\v 25 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠gi̠a̠ga̠i̠ ma̠a̠, rekpukele anwani̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l d̠a̠ amu̠m ta̠ I̠lai̠za, ma̠ igiel bho̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠gugia̠n a̠sibhom o̠lo̠bha ma̠ i̠sar ala na̠ atu̠gi̠an bho̠, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n a̠sor d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ a̠de bho̠.  
\v 26 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, uruom d̠o̠ ma̠ I̠lai̠za ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ odi awa. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, uruom i̠na ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ ekpukele ani̠ ola̠ Azare̠fat d̠a̠ ebhugh Asi̠do̠n.  
\v 27 A̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l d̠a̠ amu̠m ta̠ owil I̠lai̠sa, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ awa ola̠ ukoko na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, a̠ten A̠neman wa̠ A̠siria̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠, i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ rologi d̠awa igurom ibom.  
\v 29 Sa̠ awa ib̠etina̠ sa̠ inugi i̠na imutiom d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu esi bho̠ ulo ma̠ e̠ma bho̠. Awa i̠ru̠ru̠an onu o̠yo̠ oteb̠eli d̠a̠ a̠gbo\f + \fr 4:29 \fq A̠gbo: \ft a̠kule\f* bho̠.  
\v 30 Ya̠a̠, i̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠rile a̠ten ad̠u̠a. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:21-28) 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ i̠na a̠sor agi̠ d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m, e̠ma ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ebhugh Agalili, sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠ ma̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.  
\v 32 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ed̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n o̠mu̠gho̠n, ezin bho̠, i̠na a̠bhin a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 33 Odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠nyegi, aro̠ d̠a̠ ologi otu u̠gala bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin obom okoroko a̠mulughuom A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠,  
\v 34 “Tene ma̠ ad̠u̠a! A̠zizo̠s Anazare̠t, anwa idin ere na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ i̠yar? Anwa na̠ a̠ru ra̠ o̠pi̠e̠gi̠ i̠yar o̠man ke̠re̠? Ami̠ a̠loghom anwa. Anwa We̠b̠ab̠ala wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin a̠ru bho̠!” 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mulughuom i̠na ma̠a̠, “Nima̠ ma̠ aro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m! Ma̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠!” Sa̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠robh i̠na a̠teb̠eli d̠a̠ a̠de, d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ e̠d̠ighia̠n ola̠ ate̠i̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ imogha̠, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠pura̠n odi ma̠a̠, “Woo, i̠nye̠n ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠! I̠na na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ na̠ a̠limon na̠ a̠mulughuom i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ awa na̠ emite na̠ e̠d̠u̠a!”  
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, i̠si̠saragi̠an i̠te̠i̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom 
\r (Amatiu 8:14-17; Amaki̠ 1:29-34) 
\p  
\v 38 A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ otu u̠gala bho̠ a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n. Obom amu̠m-o̠bhi̠i̠y a̠sibh o̠yo̠go̠-onweni ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n ma̠ igiel bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ okoko o̠yo̠.  
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na a̠zuma̠n a̠mulughuom amu̠m-o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠ a̠ze asi̠ghe̠. Sa̠ amu̠m-o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠ ad̠u̠a, sa̠ o̠yo̠go̠-onweni ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ d̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ed̠ia̠n aki̠o̠m awa. 
\p  
\v 40 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ ogogo bho̠ na̠ a̠sor bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom ibhin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere rasu̠nwe̠r iruom i̠na. Sa̠ i̠na agbam agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠ten o̠ni̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ awa a̠d̠umeni.  
\v 41 I̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh emiteghu d̠a̠ a̠ruzu a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom, sa̠ imulughu ma̠a̠, “Anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” Ya̠a̠, i̠na a̠bhin o̠kparakpar okoroko a̠mulughuom awa, sa̠ aghaghana awa ma̠ ofugh abar. Ezin bho̠, awa eloghom ma̠ i̠na Akrai̠st\f + \fr 4:41 \fq Akrai̠st: \ft O̠li̠le̠ma na̠ Witenemeni wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n o̠fi̠ri̠ma bho̠.\f*. 
\p  
\v 42 A̠d̠io ab̠al sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m a̠mite agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ a̠sigima̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠. Sa̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠bho̠ro̠gha̠n i̠na kesikesi. Igiel bho̠ awa i̠ki̠karaghan i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ awa iwia̠n agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ko o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ awa a̠ten agi̠ ma̠ opa̠n esi.  
\v 43 Ya̠a̠, i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ agba ani̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ re̠ma iyed̠i, ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠n o̠ku̠a a̠ruom ami̠ ma̠ oru.”  
\v 44 Sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠zudia̠. 
\c 5  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi ma̠ i̠pu̠r Ogbo-atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ A̠zizo̠s amara d̠a̠ aka o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko Age̠ne̠sare̠t\f + \fr 5:1 \fq O̠bhi̠i̠y-eko Age̠ne̠sare̠t: \ft Ubhelegi ma̠ O̠bhi̠i̠y Eko Agalili, bo̠d̠o̠ Abadi̠ Agalili nyen.\f* sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iwia̠n o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠yo̠, sa̠ awa i̠ni̠ran iko i̠na ikiton agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠nagha o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ i̠na na̠ agba bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh i̠wal a̠rughugh d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠, ya̠ i̠ku̠mi̠ku̠ bho̠ isul iguri na̠ etitol i̠gbo̠ d̠awa.  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ odi oghugh bho̠, wa̠ Asai̠mo̠n a̠nwuna̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠ruom i̠na ma̠ onu oghugh bho̠ d̠a̠ esi wa̠ i̠na a̠sul bho̠ omutiom d̠a̠ obodo\f + \fr 5:3 \fq Obodo: \ft Esi-ekud̠um\f* ma̠ i̠ki̠kara. Sa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠. 
\p  
\v 4 Igiel i̠na na̠ agba awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n ma̠a̠, “Nue ma̠ oghugh bho̠ ma̠ a̠mutiom d̠a̠ obodo, ma̠ a̠sorogi ma̠ i̠gbo̠ bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ esin ina̠.” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ Asai̠mo̠n awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar ugbologhu ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n bho̠; ya̠a̠, i̠yar u̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar. O̠ku̠a eka̠, agu̠o̠ bho̠ anwa na̠ a̠fugh bho̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠sorogi ma̠ i̠gbo̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 6 Igiel awa igir o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ i̠gbo̠ bho̠ isin obom o̠lo̠gh ina̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ i̠gbo̠ bho̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠go̠gu̠a̠n.  
\v 7 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ awa ibhelegi ma̠ ogbo i̠ku̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ oghugh uwed̠i bho̠ ma̠ oru ra̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ awa. Sa̠ i̠sai̠ ina̠ bho̠ imuzoghod̠i ma̠ i̠wal a̠rughugh bho̠, sa̠ i̠de̠bh ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ iru ra̠ owi. 
\p  
\v 8 Igiel bho̠ Asai̠mo̠n A̠pita̠ abi̠gh abar wa̠ na̠ a̠mite bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, d̠u̠a d̠a̠ d̠ami̠; ami̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh o̠ni̠!”  
\v 9 Ezin bho̠, ed̠igh i̠na ma̠ ilologia̠n na̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ i̠na id̠igh onin oghugh bho̠, ma̠ o̠bi̠gh e̠mi̠ ina̠ ya̠ awa i̠ze̠ bho̠.  
\v 10 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ id̠igh ilologia̠n A̠zemsi̠ na̠ Azo̠n, anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Aze̠bidi, ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh na̠ Asai̠mo̠n na̠ e̠ku̠ ghan i̠ku̠ bho̠. 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n ma̠a̠, “Ko oghil a̠rugugu! Ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, anwa ta̠ aku̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠ a̠nwunom.”  
\v 11 Sa̠ awa id̠ur a̠rughugh d̠awa ibhuneni d̠a̠ egbolom, sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠man kabar kabar i̠se̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh 
\p  
\v 12 Obhel aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ odi e̠ma bho̠. D̠a̠ e̠ma obha̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh na̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ ozu bho̠, abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s sa̠ a̠mel a̠b̠obhia̠n d̠a̠ a̠de. Sa̠ a̠siseiny i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ka̠ anwa ima̠ra̠, anwa ta̠ a̠koko ami̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kula̠n o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Yii, ami̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ okoko oyom. B̠ab̠ala!” Onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin o̠kparakpar okoroko a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ko o̠gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ o̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠leriom ozu d̠oyom ma̠ okur bho̠, ma̠ ako̠l i̠ko̠l o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ozu ya̠ A̠mozizi ato̠ a̠guri bho̠. Obha̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin eloghom ma̠ ozu d̠oyom na̠ ab̠ab̠ala.” 
\p  
\v 15 Eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠kikiom o̠ku̠a bho̠ eka̠, o̠du̠ ogir ilologia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ asi̠saragi̠an agi̠ ma̠ egbeiny, ma̠ ola̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iru d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ani̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠, na̠ okokua̠n d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠awa.  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ghan a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ esi ola̠ od̠i kukunum ka̠ a̠siseiny a̠siseiny. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠b̠oga̠na̠ a̠d̠umeni 
\r (Amatiu 9:1-8; Amaki̠ 2:1-12) 
\p  
\v 17 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, a̠nwunom Afarisi na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ e̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠. Awa i̠d̠u̠a ke̠ma ke̠ma d̠a̠ rebhugh Agalili na̠ A̠zudia̠, na̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m e̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠se̠. Sa̠ a̠limon ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ obhin okoko a̠nwunom d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠awa od̠umeni.  
\v 18 Sa̠ idi a̠nwunom irol o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠b̠oga̠na̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠kporokporo, sa̠ iwia̠n od̠igh ka̠ o̠mu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 19 Igiel bho̠ awa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh e̠ti̠ti̠gha od̠igh ma̠ ebula̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ a̠wa i̠si̠n ibhun d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ i̠wo̠lo̠me̠ni̠ i̠na d̠a̠ ipopula̠ repele ya̠ ubhin uzu ma̠ i̠galaga bho̠, sa̠ isoroni i̠na d̠a̠ a̠kporokporo d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.\fig Otu uzu ma̠ etutula̠|alt="Single storey flat--roofed house" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 5:19" copy="LB00234" ref="5:19" \fig* 
\p  
\v 20 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh e̠mi̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠tologha̠n, na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠oyom onigha̠ nyam.” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ a̠nwunom Afarisi bho̠, na̠ ogbo-atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, ibhin id̠igh d̠a̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ epura̠n d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ onon wa̠ ozuruna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ eghoi, sa̠ na̠ a̠fugh e̠mi̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ iya̠ o̠ko̠no̠n bho̠? A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue awe̠le̠man i̠karabh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠, a̠ten A̠zib̠a̠?” 
\p  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa bho̠ sa̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ opura̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ku̠a, d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin?  
\v 23 Oken a̠b̠ur a̠pu ma̠ ofugh, ‘I̠karabh d̠oyom na̠ o̠we̠le̠man onigha̠ nyam,’ bo̠d̠o̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠rile?’  
\v 24 Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh inyin ologhom ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh onigha̠ a̠nwunom i̠se̠n a̠de no̠.” Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠b̠oga̠na̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, b̠etina̠, ma̠ a̠bhin a̠kporokporo d̠oyom ma̠ a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom.”  
\v 25 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa, sa̠ a̠b̠eton abar wa̠ i̠na a̠bhin gha̠n amanaghan bho̠, sa̠ a̠ten a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 26 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ ilologia̠n, sa̠ awa inigha̠ ma̠ itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ifugh ma̠a̠, “I̠yar na̠ o̠bi̠gh irorua̠ i̠di̠ar ilologia̠n a̠didon.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi ma̠ A̠livai̠ sa̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠d̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n 
\r (Amatiu 9:9-13; Amaki̠ 2:13-17) 
\p  
\v 27 Onon a̠ten sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mite, sa̠ abi̠gh odi ogun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠livai̠ ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ e̠fe̠m ogir d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Tu̠o̠no̠me̠ ami̠.”  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠livai̠ a̠b̠etina̠ amara, sa̠ awe̠le̠man kabar kabar atu̠o̠no̠m i̠na. 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠livai̠ a̠soroni ma̠ obom o̠d̠e̠ d̠a̠ ologi otu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom id̠igh na̠ awa i̠d̠e̠ ma̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠.  
\v 30 Ya̠a̠, a̠nwunom Afarisi bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko ya̠ id̠umom ani̠ ma̠ e̠kal id̠umom d̠awa bho̠, i̠go̠ya inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, ka̠ inyin na̠ od̠igh na̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠ka̠rabh a̠nwunom na̠ od̠e na̠ o̠d̠a?” 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “A̠nwunom ya̠ a̠ruzu ibhon ko o̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ owil; ya̠a̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ anwe̠r bho̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ owil.  
\v 32 Ami̠ iru d̠o̠ ma̠ ra̠ obhelegi ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom, ya̠a̠ ami̠ i̠tu̠n id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠ru, b̠o̠ka̠ awa etiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa.” 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ one o̠ko̠i̠ 
\r (Amatiu 9:14-17; Amaki̠ 2:18-22) 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ awa ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n na̠ ene gha̠n o̠ko̠i̠ na̠ esiseiny a̠siseiny, ogbo atu̠ghan Afarisi bho̠ eka̠ na̠ egir o̠ku̠a nyen; ya̠a̠ itoyom obha̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ od̠e o̠d̠a od̠e o̠d̠a.” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Inyin ta̠ orue od̠ighi̠ ma̠ ola̠ ra̠tologha̠n o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠, ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ i̠na od̠i na̠ awa d̠a̠ otu erogh bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 35 Ya̠a̠, obhel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa. D̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠ sa̠ awa ta̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠.” 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ ko o̠ghe̠r d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠go̠go̠ra ukpe d̠a̠ omom akapa a̠bhin ab̠ad̠i̠ ma̠ ugba̠iny akapa. Ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a, bha̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ omom akapa bho̠, sa̠ o̠go̠go̠ra ukpe wa̠ u̠ghe̠r u̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ omom bho̠, ko osora̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ugba̠iny akapa bho̠.  
\v 37 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ alo̠gh imom a̠min d̠a̠ ugba̠iny akana ozu e̠nam\f + \fr 5:37 \fq Akana ozu-e̠nam: \ft A̠nwunom Izre̠l igied̠i ikpogh gha̠n ozu e̠nam e̠le̠m abar ola̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠min, ma̠ agu̠o̠ eb̠a̠b̠a̠ bo̠d̠o̠ afa.\f* bo̠; ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a, bha̠ imom a̠min bho̠ ta̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ akana ozu-e̠nam bho̠ ta̠ a̠pol, sa̠ a̠min bho̠ ta̠ ezugia̠n ebhe, sa̠ ko orue mu orughom akana bho̠.\fig Akana ozu-e̠nam|alt="Wineskin" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 5:37" copy="LB00145" ref="5:37" \fig* 
\v 38 Ya̠a̠, imom a̠min na̠ o̠lo̠gh ghan d̠a̠ imom rakana ozu e̠nam.  
\v 39 Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ad̠a ma̠ igba̠iny a̠min a̠b̠eghenom, ola̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠d̠a imom a̠min bo̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Igba̠iny bho̠ ibhon epu.’ ” 
\c 6  
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 12:1-8; Amaki̠ 2:23-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu, A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ ari̠si̠ i̠bu̠kpa\f + \fr 6:1 \fq I̠bu̠kpa: \ft I̠se̠n ubhin i̠bu̠kpa o̠tu̠o̠m a̠ga̠i ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ na̠ e̠su̠ d̠a̠ Izre̠l bho̠\f*, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠ku̠ ma̠ idi itu bho̠, sa̠ i̠kpi̠r ikpo bho̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa id̠e.  
\v 2 Sa̠ idi Afarisi bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ anwa na̠ a̠gir abar ola̠ oloko bho̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ ogir d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu?”  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ o̠bi̠gh agu̠o̠ A̠devidi a̠gir igiel bho̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na sekina̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠, ke̠re̠?  
\v 4 I̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠bhin abe̠re̠di̠ e̠tu̠tu̠, ya̠ uguri usisa̠n rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m ma̠ od̠e bho̠, a̠d̠e. Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton idi abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na bho̠ nyen.”  
\v 5 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ bha̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu 
\r (Amatiu 12:9-14; Amaki̠ 3:1-6) 
\p  
\v 6 Opa̠n a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu aro̠, ma̠ ola̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu u̠gala A̠zu bho̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. Odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ bho̠ na̠ akpari̠an aro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 7 Idi ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ idi Afarisi e̠ro̠ na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan e̠kal abar ola̠ odin ob̠ologiom A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ awa ikimeni na̠ egon o̠bi̠gh ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠koko ma̠ a̠likoko ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ akpari̠an bho̠ ma̠a̠, “B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠ru, ra̠ amara d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠.” Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ka̠ amara d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io bho̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠pura̠n inyin, oken abar wa̠ oloko bho̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ i̠yar ogir d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠: ogir ib̠eb̠i bo̠d̠o̠ ogir i̠karabh, otenemeni o̠ni̠ onigha̠ a̠ghud̠um bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ o̠pi̠e̠gi̠?”  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpon eb̠la̠ awa a̠kitineni̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom.” I̠na a̠gir o̠ku̠a, sa̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠selegha̠n.  
\v 11 Sa̠ a̠likoko bho̠ agamame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi ogbo Afarisi bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠. Sa̠ awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, oma̠ra̠nua̠n abar awa ta̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s aso̠n d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo-ogir 
\r (Amatiu 10:1-4; Amaki̠ 3:13-19) 
\p  
\v 12 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠ sa̠ A̠zizo̠s asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu bho̠ ma̠ osiseiny; sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin eb̠la̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n bho̠ a̠siseiny A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 13 A̠d̠io ra̠ ab̠al sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kokod̠i, sa̠ aso̠n d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal a̠mutiom, sa̠ a̠doni awa a̠guri ma̠ ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 14 I̠nye̠n a̠rid̠ien d̠awa: Asai̠mo̠n, wa̠ i̠na a̠ghol A̠pita̠ bho̠, na̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ Anduru, A̠zemsi̠ na̠ Azo̠n, A̠filip na̠ Abatolomio,  
\v 15 Amatiu na̠ Ato̠mo̠si̠, A̠zemsi̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ali̠fi̠o̠s na̠ Asai̠mo̠n, wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zilo̠t bho̠,  
\v 16 A̠zuda̠s o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zemsi̠ na̠ A̠zuda̠s I̠skari̠o̠t, wa̠ a̠wol i̠na ma̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠. 
\s1 Itutumeni na̠ Isugi 
\r (Amatiu 4:23-25) 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ I̠na na̠ awa isor ka̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ otutula̠n a̠de. O̠lo̠gh ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh A̠zudia̠ na̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, na̠ d̠a̠ rakagara Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n e̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 18 Awa iru ra̠ o̠nagha o̠yo̠ na̠ okokua̠n d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠awa. Ogbo ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ enyegi eka̠ eru ra̠ ekokua̠n.  
\v 19 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ iwia̠n okula̠n o̠yo̠, ezin bho̠ a̠limon na̠ emite d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ ekoko ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠. 
\s1 Ibo na̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ 
\r (Amatiu 5:1-12) 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin ronyigoiny bho̠, 
\q2 irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ola̠ inyin. 
\q1  
\v 21 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, 
\q2 inyin ta̠ od̠e olegha̠n. 
\q1 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ esorogi ma̠ izin i̠se̠n bho̠, 
\q2 inyin ta̠ o̠mo̠lo̠gh adi̠e̠l. 
\q1  
\v 22 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ a̠nwunom na̠ e̠su̠a inyin, 
\q2 na̠ obhel ola̠ awa na̠ eghirom inyin, sa̠ na̠ eduom inyin, 
\q2 sa̠ ighel a̠d̠ien d̠a̠ inyin ma̠a̠ i̠nyin i̠karabh, 
\q3 d̠a̠ ebula̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠. 
\p  
\v 23 “Ya̠a̠, ibo ma̠ epeleghu na̠ a̠libhon ologi, ezin bho̠ asu̠o̠ ya̠ i̠mar i̠bu̠gh na̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny; ya̠a̠ iloghome ma̠ igba̠iny ro̠we̠de̠ d̠awa igir o̠ku̠a egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 24 “Ya̠a̠ olo a̠leghe inyin ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠li̠la ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, 
\q2 ezin bho̠ inyin na̠ o̠te̠i̠ e̠no̠gho̠man d̠inyin. 
\q1  
\v 25 Olo a̠leghe inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠e na̠ elegha̠n i̠se̠n bho̠, 
\q2 ezin bho̠ inyin ta̠ o̠ri̠la ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠. 
\q1 Olo a̠leghe inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠mo̠lo̠gh adi̠e̠l i̠se̠n bho̠, 
\q2 ezin bho̠ inyin ta̠ od̠igh i̠ku̠nu̠ o̠gba ma̠ igbir. 
\q1  
\v 26 Olo a̠leghe inyin ka̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom na̠ esen inyin ib̠eb̠i, 
\q2 obha̠ agu̠o̠ igba̠iny ro̠we̠de̠ d̠awa igir igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠riwil igunugha̠ bho̠. 
\s1 Otula̠n ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠rid̠ien 
\r (Amatiu 5:38-48; 7:12) 
\p  
\v 27 “Ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nagha ami̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: Itula̠ne ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠rid̠ien d̠inyin, igire ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠su̠a inyin bho̠,  
\v 28 Itutumeni ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ghad̠i̠ inyin bho̠, ma̠ esiseiny enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠ighi inyin i̠karabh nyen.  
\v 29 Ka̠ o̠ni̠ ab̠abh anwa d̠a̠ odi ab̠akagba d̠oyom, tiba̠ra̠ ma̠ agba uwed̠i ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na nyen. Ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠ghum akapa-anyu̠\f + \fr 6:29 \fq Akapa-anyu̠: \ft Akapa ibura̠. Agu̠o̠ o̠tu̠o̠m, akapa okirika̠, akapa ogir, bo̠d̠o̠ akapa ola̠ u̠lagha d̠a̠ anyu̠ u̠gbam opa̠n\f* d̠oyom a̠bhin, ko okigima̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠b̠aram na̠ akapa-a̠de d̠oyom obhin.  
\v 30 Nigha̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠puru ma̠ anwa ma̠ abar; ya̠a̠ ka̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin abar oyom, ko opuru i̠na ma̠ omulumeni abar bho̠.  
\v 31 Gire ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh awa ma̠ ogir onigha̠ oyom bho̠. 
\p  
\v 32 “Ka̠ u̠gba ma̠ inyin otula̠n ogbo etula̠n d̠inyin ku̠ku̠m, ka̠ asu̠o̠ d̠inyin ka̠ ere? Id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ eka̠ na̠ etula̠n ogbo ya̠ itula̠n awa bho̠ nyen.  
\v 33 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ inyin ugir ib̠eb̠i unigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ egir ib̠eb̠i na̠ enigha̠ inyin bho̠, ka̠ asu̠o̠ d̠inyin ka̠ ere? Id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ eka̠ na̠ egir o̠ku̠a nyen.  
\v 34 Ka̠ inyin i̠wo̠lo̠ni̠an abar ogbo ya̠ ta̠ erue e̠kpe̠ inyin bho̠, ka̠ asu̠o̠ d̠inyin ka̠ ere? Onin agu̠o̠ rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom na̠ e̠wo̠lo̠ni̠an i̠di̠ar ma̠ rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, sa̠ awa na̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ egon a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ o̠kpe̠ awa ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠mu̠gh d̠awa.  
\v 35 Ya̠a̠ itula̠ne ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠inyin, igire ma̠ ib̠ebi̠ ma̠ enigha̠ awa, i̠wo̠lo̠ni̠ane̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ inyin ko ogon d̠o̠ ma̠ amu̠kpe̠. Sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ ibom alu̠kpe̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ oten anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ O̠ni̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠. Ezin bho̠, i̠na na̠ a̠gir ib̠eb̠i na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠bi̠gh ghan ib̠eb̠i ya̠ ugir ugir unigha̠ awa bho̠, na̠ rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 36 Ikpone ma̠ igbirigbir a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin na̠ a̠kpon igbirigbir bho̠. 
\s1 Osobh Ase̠ Onigha̠ Ipa̠n A̠nwunom 
\r (Amatiu 7:15) 
\p  
\v 37 “O̠ni̠ ko o̠nu̠r e̠bi̠gh o̠ni̠ ma̠ e̠pi̠e̠, b̠o̠ka̠ u̠nu̠r o̠bi̠gh inyin o̠pi̠e. O̠ni̠ ko obhin ib̠ologiom esobh ase̠ ma̠ ebhumeni ma̠ o̠ni̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ubhin ib̠ologiom osobh ase̠ obhumeni inyin. I̠we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom enigha̠ awa, b̠o̠ka̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠inyin onigha̠ inyin.  
\v 38 I̠ne̠ghe̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ enigha̠ inyin nyen. Ib̠eb̠i atu̠gi̠, ya̠ u̠mar u̠zo̠, sa̠ unyegi umuzoghod̠i sa̠ ipel na̠ ezugia̠n, sa̠ ubhin uzuom ru̠gbo̠ d̠inyin. Agu̠o̠ inyin ugir unigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ inyin. Ezin bho̠, i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin ubhin u̠to̠ unigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, i̠nye̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ obhin o̠to̠ onigha̠ inyin bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien ta̠ a̠rue a̠rileghom opa̠n o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien ke̠re̠? I̠wal awa ko omel d̠o̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ ogugua̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 40 O̠ni̠ atu̠ghan na̠ o̠bu̠gh d̠o̠ a̠pu ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠na wa̠ amar atu̠ghan aku̠ro̠m bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ ka̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 41 “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ anwa na̠ abi̠gh o̠taghatagh wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien umor d̠oyom bho̠, sa̠ anwa na̠ ologhoma̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ egum oriren wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠?  
\v 42 Anwa ta̠ a̠din ere a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠oyom ma̠a̠, ‘Umor, d̠ighi ami̠ ta̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠taghatagh d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien d̠oyom,’ ma̠ igiel anwa o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ egum oriren wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠? Anwa obhelebhel o̠ni̠! D̠ia̠ ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ egum oriren wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠; i̠se̠ kisa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠rue abi̠gh esi asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠taghatagh wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien umor d̠oyom bho̠. 
\s1 Oriren na̠ itu d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 7:16-20; 12:33-35) 
\p  
\v 43 “Ob̠eb̠i oriren ola̠ na̠ a̠mum o̠karabh otu bo̠. Onin agu̠o̠ o̠karabh oriren omum d̠o̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i otu.  
\v 44 Na̠ obhin otu oriren na̠ olelegi ma̠ a̠d̠ien oriren bho̠. A̠nwunom ikpokpo d̠o̠ ma̠ itu a̠fig\fig A̠grep ola̠ usuom|alt="Grape vine on trellis" src="Louise Basse" size="col" loc="Luke 6:44" copy="HK00112" ref="6:44" \fig* d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom; bo̠d̠o̠, sa̠ awa na̠ ekpokpo ma̠ itu oriren a̠grep d̠a̠ e̠ko̠ko̠ esi iriren i̠su̠ ya̠ od̠i ka̠ ib̠e na̠ id̠id̠igh na̠ i̠ze̠.  
\v 45 Ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠mutioghom ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i ya̠ i̠na a̠kokod̠i a̠guri d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. Onin agu̠o̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠mutioghom i̠karabh i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ i̠karabh ya̠ i̠na a̠kokod̠i a̠guri d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. A̠d̠ien i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠kokod̠i a̠muzoghod̠i d̠a̠ ologi o̠ni̠, i̠nye̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠nu̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠fugh na̠ a̠mutiom bho̠. 
\s1 I̠wal ilo ma̠ a̠rutu 
\p  
\v 46 “Anwa i̠tu̠n ere na̠ a̠bhelegi ami̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, Wa̠nwuna̠,’ ya̠a̠ anwa na̠ ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ na̠ agba bho̠?  
\v 47 Ami̠ ta̠ a̠leriom inyin o̠le̠m o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠ru d̠ami̠, sa̠ anagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠ami̠, sa̠ a̠kpon o̠ku̠a a̠rugh.  
\v 48 I̠na od̠i ka̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu, sa̠ a̠gbo ma̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠kud̠umeni sa̠ a̠bho ma̠ otu bho̠ agbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma. Igiel a̠d̠igho a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ obom amu̠m bho̠ aro̠bho̠m otu bho̠, ya̠a̠ otu bho̠ amara gigiribh, ezin bho̠ o̠mar olo ma̠ otu bho̠.  
\v 49 Ya̠a̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ amu̠gho̠n sa̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠, i̠na od̠i ka̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu o̠kpo̠kpo̠ o̠to̠. Sa̠ igiel obom amu̠m a̠d̠igho a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ a̠nu ma̠ otu bho̠ a̠teb̠eli a̠tutughud̠i. Abu̠gh emel!” 
\c 7  
\s1 Ologi ima̠ra̠ we̠mu̠ e̠gham bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 8:5-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agba ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ amado̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma Akapanu̠m.  
\v 2 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, odi we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham A̠rom, a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ogoni ola̠ i̠na a̠bhin atu̠o̠m abar ibom. Ogoni bho̠ na̠ anwe̠r na̠ a̠tua̠n omugh.  
\v 3 Igiel bho̠ o̠ni̠ we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ amu̠gho̠n a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom ikei a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s opuru agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠koko ma̠ ogoni d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 4 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ o̠kparakpar agu̠o̠, i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ onon akpe̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ d̠oyom.  
\v 5 Ezin bho̠, i̠na a̠tula̠n ebhugh d̠i̠yar, sa̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu u̠gala d̠i̠yar.”  
\v 6 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh na̠ awa agi̠. 
\p Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n otu bho̠ sa̠ o̠ni̠ we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ a̠ruom ra̠tologha̠n d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠gba onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠, ko onyegi ma̠ ozu d̠oyom, ezin bho̠ ami̠ ilei d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ od̠ighom oyom d̠a̠ ekpukpu i̠galaga otu d̠ami̠.  
\v 7 Odi abar eka̠, ami̠ na̠ aru̠ru̠an ma̠ ami̠ ilei d̠o̠ ma̠ oru ra̠ o̠bi̠ghan oyom nyen. Ya̠a̠, fughe ka̠ ma̠ abar a̠gboloma̠, sa̠ ogoni d̠ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠um.  
\v 8 Ami̠ eka̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de a̠limon, sa̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpukpu d̠ami̠ bho̠. Ka̠ ami̠ iruom o̠ni̠ onon ma̠a̠, ‘Gi̠e̠,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ agi̠; ka̠ ami̠ iruom opa̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Tue,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ru. Ka̠ ami̠ iruom ogoni d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Gire ma̠ abar onon,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠gir.” 
\p  
\v 9 Obhel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠igh i̠na ma̠ ilologia̠n, sa̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na bho̠ sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l eka̠, ami̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ abu̠gh o̠ko̠no̠n.”  
\v 10 Sa̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ uruom a̠duom bho̠ imula̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ otu, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ma̠ ogoni bho̠ na̠ a̠d̠um. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eton o̠nyi̠ odi ekpukele ani̠ d̠a̠ omugh 
\p  
\v 11 Obhel a̠ten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ odi e̠ma ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠nen, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom id̠igh na̠ i̠na i̠gi̠.  
\v 12 Agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n o̠nu̠ ogigo e̠ma bho̠, bha̠ a̠nwunom na̠ erol egua̠de na̠ emite d̠a̠ ogigo bho̠. O̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠mugh bho̠ ogini olobhiri o̠nyi̠ ta̠ odi ekpukele ani̠. Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ ekpon ani̠ bho̠.  
\v 13 Igiel bho̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ abi̠gh ani̠ bho̠, sa̠ igbirigbir ani̠ bho̠ id̠ighi i̠na. Sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ko oleghe mu.” 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erol egua̠de bho̠, sa̠ a̠kula̠n abar wa̠ awa na̠ ebhin na̠ erol egua̠de bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠mara kpom. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ bho̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠fugh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwa, b̠etina̠!”  
\v 15 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠mugh bho̠ asu̠ma aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ ake̠ ma̠ ofugh a̠fugh, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eton i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n, sa̠ awa itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “Obom owil na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠i̠yar. A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠.”  
\v 17 Sa̠ o̠du̠ ogir ilologia̠n ta̠ A̠zizo̠s onon asi̠saragi̠an d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ A̠zudia̠ sekina̠ d̠a̠ eghighira̠ ebhugh bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 11:2-19) 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n i̠gba ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠gir bho̠ inigha̠ i̠na. Sa̠ Azo̠n a̠bhelegi i̠wal o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa,  
\v 19 sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ opura̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Anwa Witenemeni wa̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠yar ogon opa̠n o̠ni̠?” 
\p  
\v 20 Igiel bho̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Azo̠n owurmamu̠m a̠ruom i̠yar oru ra̠ o̠te̠i̠ oyom opura̠n ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠yar ogon opa̠n o̠ni̠?’ ” 
\p  
\v 21 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom a̠d̠umeni d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠awa, sa̠ a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh, sa̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar na̠ e̠bi̠gh.  
\v 22 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Imula̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Azo̠n ma̠ ebhin i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠, sekina̠ ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: ogbo ya̠ a̠rid̠ien ib̠omia̠n bho̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh esi, a̠rukula̠ bho̠ na̠ erile, ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠ na̠ okoko o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠, remua̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n abar, imumugh a̠nwunom na̠ ob̠egion, sa̠ na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠.  
\v 23 Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ami̠, sa̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ odugh d̠o̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 24 Obhel bho̠ itileduom ta̠ Azo̠n na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Azo̠n onigha̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠: “Inyin u̠gi̠ d̠a̠ obom e̠sala ed̠um bho̠ ka̠ o̠bi̠gh ere? Ikpoko ya̠ na̠ eduka̠ d̠a̠ o̠fe̠gu̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 25 Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ku̠a d̠o̠, ka̠ inyin u̠gi̠ ka̠ u̠bi̠gh ere? O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bura̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ibura̠ ke̠re̠? E̠e̠nyi̠, a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠an rakapa ibom a̠b̠ua̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa ma̠ e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, od̠i d̠a̠ rogigo aru̠li̠le̠ma.  
\v 26 Ya̠a̠, inyin u̠gi̠ ka̠ u̠bi̠gh ere? Owil ke̠re̠? Yii, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠pu ma̠ owil.  
\v 27 Onon o̠ni̠ wa̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ bho̠, ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom o̠ni̠ a̠duom d̠ami̠ ma̠ od̠ia̠ o̠gi̠, 
\q2 ka̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man eten bho̠, kisa̠ anwa ta̠ ake̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠.’ 
\m  
\v 28 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ anwani̠ i̠maragi̠ bho̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ Azo̠n bo̠; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ abu̠gh a̠pu i̠na.” 
\p  
\v 29 Igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, na̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n a̠fugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ awa id̠igh ani̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ eten ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i, ezin bho̠ Azo̠n na̠ a̠wur awa ma̠ amu̠m.  
\v 30 Ya̠a̠, a̠nwunom Afarisi bho̠, sekina̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ oloko bho̠, ighel i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠awa bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ Azo̠n owur awa ma̠ amu̠m. 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ Azizo̠s a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ere atu̠o̠m a̠nwunom amu̠m onon? Awa i̠gu̠b̠an ere?  
\v 32 Awa od̠i ka̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ egbolom a̠b̠ua̠, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ odi na̠ e̠go̠ya ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘I̠yar upughe ma̠ od̠od̠ue onigha̠ inyin, 
\q2 ya̠a̠ inyin u̠ghe̠r d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠gba, 
\q1 i̠yar u̠mo̠r aso̠r ekulom onigha̠ inyin eka̠, 
\q2 inyin uleghe d̠o̠ osorogi ma̠ izin nyen.’ 
\m  
\v 33 Azo̠n owurmamu̠m a̠ru bho̠, i̠na na̠ od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i ed̠ia̠n, na̠ o̠d̠a d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠min, sa̠ inyin u̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘O̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ ab̠am i̠na.’  
\v 34 O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠ru, i̠na a̠d̠e na̠ ad̠a, sa̠ inyin u̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Onon o̠d̠o̠gho̠d̠o̠gh sekina̠ o̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min, na̠ a̠tologha̠n ta̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.’  
\v 35 Yaa̠, a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ eloghom abar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ erugh na̠ eleriom ma̠ eloghom abar a̠bhon.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s awe̠le̠man i̠karabh odi ani̠ a̠nigha̠ 
\p  
\v 36 Odi o̠ni̠ Afarisi a̠lebh A̠zizo̠s ma̠ oru ra̠ od̠igh na̠ o̠yo̠ od̠e abar, sa̠ i̠na a̠ten agi̠ d̠a̠ otu o̠ni̠ bho̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ma̠ o̠gho̠ d̠a̠ a̠de, d̠a̠ aka akpata od̠e bho̠.  
\v 37 Sa̠ odi ani̠ ola̠ e̠ma bho̠, ola̠ na̠ a̠rugh i̠karabh a̠ma̠rugh, amu̠gho̠n ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ abar d̠a̠ otu o̠ni̠ Afarisi bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ololo ola̠ ubhin ob̠eb̠i o̠gbe̠o̠ma ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ alabasta u̠le̠m, ola̠ elo ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ologi bho̠ agi̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 38 Sa̠ i̠na amara d̠a̠ aman ta̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ aka a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠leghe, sa̠ izin d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠b̠o̠ro̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠sike ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ a̠bhin asi̠ghal d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gbul izin bho̠ asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ a̠sike ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ api̠pi̠o̠bh a̠sike bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin elo ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ bho̠ a̠zugioghom. 
\p  
\v 39 Igiel bho̠ o̠ni̠ Afarisi wa̠ a̠lebh i̠na bho̠ abi̠gh abar onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ onon aro̠ ma̠ owil nab̠o̠, i̠na ka̠ iloghom o̠le̠m ani̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠kula̠n i̠na bho̠, ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.” 
\p  
\v 40 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠mutiom awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Asai̠mo̠n, ami̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠gba onigha̠ oyom.” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 41 “I̠wal a̠nwunom id̠ikighu ma̠ i̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ awo̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ikpoki. Odi o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠d̠igh o̠mu̠gh o̠ni̠r na̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (500) adi̠nari̠, uwed̠i sa̠ a̠d̠igh o̠mu̠gh eruba̠l na̠ d̠iobh (50) adi̠nari̠.\fig Ra̠misigh a̠dinari̠|alt="Faces of silver Roman denarius" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 7:41" copy="HK00166" ref="7:41" \fig* 
\v 42 O̠ni̠ awa ola̠ a̠rue ma̠ o̠kpe̠ o̠mu̠gh d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠man i̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. I̠se̠ ka̠, d̠a̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom i̠nye̠ ka̠ oken ta̠ a̠tula̠n i̠na a̠pu?” 
\p  
\v 43 Asai̠mo̠n awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ aru̠ru̠an ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ u̠we̠le̠man o̠mu̠gh wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ a̠sobh ase̠ bho̠ ma̠ iya̠ igielake̠.” 
\p  
\v 44 Sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ abi̠gh ani̠ onon? Ami̠ iru d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom, ya̠a̠ anwa na̠ onigha̠ d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ amu̠m ya̠ obhin otitola̠ a̠sike d̠ami̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠na na̠ a̠bhin izin d̠o̠yo̠ a̠b̠o̠ro̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠sike d̠ami̠ sa̠ a̠bhin asi̠ghal d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gbul asi̠ghe̠.  
\v 45 Anwa na̠ o̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh\f + \fr 7:45 \fq O̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh: \ft I̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh etula̠n. A̠nwunom Izre̠l na̠ e̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh o̠ni̠ (d̠a̠ ab̠akagba), na̠ e̠da ma̠ isuloma̠ na̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ otu d̠awa, na̠ eleriom etula̠n d̠awa.\f* d̠o̠ ami̠, ya̠a̠ ani̠ onon ka̠ obhel bho̠ ami̠ id̠igh iru ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, i̠na ta̠ o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh a̠sike d̠ami̠.  
\v 46 Anwa na̠ ozuom d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ amu̠nu̠, ya̠a̠ ani̠ onon na̠ a̠zugioghom a̠sike d̠ami̠ ma̠ elo ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠.  
\v 47 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwa ma̠a̠, na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ ib̠uiy opa̠n bho̠ onigha̠ i̠na, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠leriom ibom etula̠n bho̠. Ya̠a̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ u̠we̠le̠man o̠nyi̠ki̠kara i̠karabh unigha̠ bho̠, ta̠ a̠leriom o̠nyi̠ki̠kara etula̠n ku̠ku̠m.” 
\p  
\v 48 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠karabh d̠oyom na̠ o̠we̠le̠man onigha̠ ma̠ anwa.” 
\p  
\v 49 Sa̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i ya̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠na na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠, i̠ke̠ ma̠ ofugh d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa ma̠a̠, “Onon ka̠ a̠nyen, wa̠ na̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 50 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ologi ima̠ra̠\f + \fr 7:50 \fq Ologi ima̠ra̠: \ft Id̠umom ologi\f* d̠oyom na̠ etenemeni ma̠ anwa; gi̠e̠ na̠ ekima̠.” 
\c 8  
\s1 A̠sidogh ta̠ Ogbebhma̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Onon a̠ru a̠ten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ e̠ma a̠ten e̠ma, na̠ agba na̠ a̠mutiom ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ibom na̠ i̠gbara re̠ma bho̠. D̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo-ogir bho̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ i̠na,  
\v 2 na̠ idi anwani̠ ya̠ i̠na asi̠ghe̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ ozu na̠ iya̠ a̠koko d̠a̠ rasu̠nwe̠r a̠d̠umeni. A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ wa̠ u̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ od̠ua̠l i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ ozu bho̠,  
\v 3 A̠zoana ani̠ ta̠ A̠suza̠, okponom ma̠ otu ta̠ E̠ro̠d, na̠ A̠suzana, na̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom ya̠ ib̠uiy ibhin ghan i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa inwuna̠ bho̠ e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 4 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom na̠ e̠d̠u̠a ke̠ma ke̠ma eru ra̠ ed̠igh na̠ i̠na ekokod̠ia̠n onin esi bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh ma̠a̠:  
\v 5 “Ogbebhma̠ agi̠ ka̠ ogbebh ikpo ed̠ia̠n. Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠kpo asar bho̠, sa̠ idi imel d̠a̠ eten sa̠ u̠ze̠re̠gi̠, sa̠ i̠nu̠r iru ra̠ ikpokpoiny id̠e i̠mado̠n.  
\v 6 Idi imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma, i̠ke̠ aka ma̠ o̠su̠ sa̠ imugughu d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ amu̠m bho̠.  
\v 7 Idi imel d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom. Sa̠ iriren ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠ na̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n i̠nye̠ i̠su̠ imite, sa̠ iriren ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠ ikpegiom i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠ awa i̠ze̠gi̠.  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠ idi imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de, sa̠ i̠mar i̠su̠ imum imutiom i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh a̠bin o̠nu̠ ya̠ ubhin ugbebh bho̠.” 
\p A̠fugh i̠nye̠n awe̠le̠ sa̠ a̠mulughu a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “I̠na wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, amu̠gho̠n.” 
\s1 Ezin a̠sidogh bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 13:10-17; Amaki̠ 4:10-12) 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ipura̠n I̠na ma̠a̠, “Ezin a̠sidogh bho̠ ka̠ ere?”  
\v 10 Sa̠ I̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ inyin, na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ologhom i̠di̠ar e̠wo̠gi̠na irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠; ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i, urogh a̠sidogh onigha̠ b̠o̠ka̠, 
\q1 “ ‘awa ta̠ ekpon ya̠a̠ awa ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠, 
\q2 ta̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠a̠ awa ko o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠.’\x - \xo 8:10 \xt Azaya 6:9\x* 
\p  
\v 11 “Ezin a̠sidogh bho̠, bha̠ o̠ko̠no̠n: Ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠, bha̠ ikpo-a̠fugh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 12 Ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ eten bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n; sa̠ eru bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠ ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa, b̠o̠ka̠ awa id̠umom eten.  
\v 13 Ya̠a̠ ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n, sa̠ ibhin d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi i̠da ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh bho̠ ibhin; ya̠a̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠kaka, awa ima̠ra̠ ma̠ ekud̠i obhel sa̠ imel i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ obhel ad̠agi̠an.  
\v 14 Ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n, ya̠a̠ a̠tepa̠ sa̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh e̠mara̠nwunom, e̠li̠la na̠ e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom i̠vi̠mo̠m ola̠ irue d̠o̠ ma̠ omum itu ya̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ e̠kpo̠ e̠b̠am.  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, ikpo ya̠ imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ ibhin ob̠eb̠i ologi i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠, sa̠ i̠da ibhin i̠b̠ar na̠ a̠ma̠ne, sa̠ imum itu ya̠ i̠kpo̠ sa̠ i̠b̠am. 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ato̠di̠ Bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:21-25) 
\p  
\v 16 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ asu̠o̠m ato̠di̠, sa̠ ta̠ awo̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ekpukpu abafu̠ bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ekpukpu akpata bo̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠na ta̠ agbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ esi ola̠, ka̠ a̠nwunom ud̠igh esi bho̠ ta̠ e̠bi̠gh abar.\fig Ato̠di̠ ola̠ u̠gbam d̠a̠ esi agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ |alt="Lamp on bushel" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 8:16" copy="HK00152" ref="8:16" \fig* 
\v 17 Abar ola̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ola̠ ko omutiom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠bi̠gh bo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ abar ola̠ u̠wo̠gi̠ ola̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ obhin omutiom d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al bo̠.  
\v 18 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha ma̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n. O̠ni̠ ola̠ ate̠i̠ ta̠ onigha̠ ma̠ o̠gbam; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠, iya̠ i̠na na̠ aru̠ru̠an ma̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ bho̠ eka̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r obhin.” 
\s1 Onweni na̠ a̠rumor ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 12:46-50; Amaki̠ 3:31-35) 
\p  
\v 19 I̠se̠n onweni na̠ a̠rumor d̠o̠yo̠ iru ra̠ o̠bi̠ghan o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠yo̠.  
\v 20 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Onweni d̠oyom na̠ a̠rumor d̠oyom na̠ e̠mara d̠a̠ etire na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh o̠bi̠ghan onyom.” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Onweni d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠rumor d̠ami̠ bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ igir o̠ku̠a bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠okumeni ma̠ ogim na̠ abadi̠ ola̠ na̠ agam 
\r (Amatiu 8:23-27; Amaki̠ 4:35-41) 
\p  
\v 22 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ id̠igh oghugh. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Id̠ighi o̠b̠e̠i̠y d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko bho̠.” Sa̠ awa igim avala bho̠ imutiom oghugh bho̠ ma̠ o̠b̠e̠i̠y.  
\v 23 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠b̠e̠i̠y bho̠ sa̠ adi̠la ibhinom i̠na. Sa̠ ogim a̠gim awai̠ d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko bho̠ sa̠ abadi̠ bho̠ agam. Sa̠ amu̠m ipoka̠n na̠ ed̠igh na̠ emuzo d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠, sa̠ awa iloghoma̠n ma̠ obom a̠d̠ugh na̠ ate̠i̠ awa. 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠su̠me̠ni̠ i̠na, ifugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar na̠ owi-o!” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ ogim bho̠ na̠ abadi̠ wa̠ na̠ agam bho̠, sa̠ ogim bho̠ a̠b̠okum sa̠ ekima̠ a̠mite.  
\v 25 Ya̠a̠, i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin ka̠ od̠i d̠a̠ken?” 
\p Sa̠ id̠igh awa ma̠ a̠rugugu na̠ ilologia̠n, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠fugh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ma̠a̠, “Onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠? Ka̠ i̠na ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ ogim na̠ opoka̠n amu̠m eka̠, sa̠ awa na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n na̠ e̠ro̠ to̠i̠ny, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠fugh bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu odi o̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 8:28-34; Amaki̠ 5:1-20) 
\p  
\v 26 Awa i̠zo̠ghu̠ ka̠ isul d̠a̠ agba ebhugh Age̠rasa\f + \fr 8:26 \fq Age̠rasa: \ft Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire bho̠ ibhelegi ma̠ Agadara (Amat 8:28). Ipa̠n sa̠ ibhelegi ma̠ Age̠ge̠sa.\f*, d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ Agalili.  
\v 27 I̠na a̠pel a̠bhun d̠a̠ egbolom, sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ e̠ma bho̠ ola̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ ebia̠ ami̠nana i̠na. O̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an d̠o̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ma̠ owewegh obhel, na̠ orugh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ otu nyen; ya̠a̠ a̠rugh ka̠ d̠a̠ o̠karabh esi.  
\v 28 O̠ni̠ bho̠ abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ a̠mulughu, sa̠ a̠mel a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠bhin obom okoroko a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ ami̠ ka̠ unwuna̠ ma̠ ere, A̠zizo̠s, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Wagi̠manyu̠ A̠pu bho̠? Siseiny, ko ogbikimeni ami̠!”  
\v 29 Ezin bho̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ ma̠ omite o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ bho̠. A̠d̠izo robhel na̠ a̠guri ghan na̠ a̠b̠oroghom o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ ubhin i̠go̠ro̠go̠ro̠ na̠ ikoli u̠du̠o̠m ghan i̠na d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ na̠ a̠sike, sa̠ uguri ma̠ esi ukponom, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠gbugbo ma̠ i̠go̠ro̠go̠ro̠ na̠ ikoli\f + \fr 8:29 \fq Ikoli: \ft Abar ola̠ na̠ obhin na̠ o̠du̠o̠m a̠wel o̠ni̠, bo̠d̠o̠ agu̠o̠.\f* ya̠ ubhin ghan u̠du̠o̠m i̠na bho̠, sa̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠b̠or i̠na a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ e̠ghana. 
\p  
\v 30 A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠d̠ien d̠oyom ka̠ ubhelegi eka̠?” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “A̠d̠izo,” ezin bho̠ a̠d̠izo i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ erugh d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 31 Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠, i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ i̠na oze d̠o̠ awa a̠d̠ighom, d̠a̠ ogugua̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠. 
\p  
\v 32 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, obom o̠lo̠gh roporopo i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ d̠a̠ a̠gbo bho̠ na̠ eb̠u na̠ ed̠e. Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠ awa ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ rozu roporopo bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ imite i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ka̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ roporopo bho̠. Sa̠ roporopo bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠gbo bho̠ ighil isor d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y-eko bho̠ i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠an. 
\p  
\v 34 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom roporopo bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, sa̠ awa ighil i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ i̠gba d̠a̠ ibom na̠ i̠gbara re̠ma bho̠.  
\v 35 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠. Sa̠ awa iru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s ra̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ a̠loghoma̠n ozu, a̠bura̠ ma̠ ibura̠, ari̠la ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka a̠sike ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa.  
\v 36 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, i̠gba ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠um.  
\v 37 O̠ku̠a sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom d̠a̠ ebhugh Age̠rasa ize ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ebhugh d̠awa, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ ibom a̠rugugu na̠ esibh awa bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh a̠mula̠. 
\p  
\v 38 O̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu bho̠ ale̠gh A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Ma̠ra̠ ami̠ id̠igh na̠ anwa i̠ro̠.” Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin o̠kparakpar okoroko a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠,  
\v 39 “Mula̠ ma̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom, ma̠ agba ma̠ a̠mutiom ibom i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwa bho̠.” Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh eten agba asasaragi̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠ma bho̠ ma̠ ibom i̠di̠ar ya̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠gir a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eton o̠nyani̠ ta̠ Azari̠o̠s d̠a̠ omugh,  //  sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ ani̠ ola̠ a̠kula̠n akapa d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 9:18-26; Amaki̠ 5:21-43) 
\p  
\v 40 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ A̠zizo̠s ab̠e̠i̠ a̠mula̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ uwed̠i bho̠, sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠da i̠na ibhin, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠ro̠ na̠ egon i̠na.  
\v 41 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Azai̠ru̠s, we̠mu̠ u̠gala A̠zu a̠ru, sa̠ a̠mel a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ale̠gh i̠na ma̠ oru d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠,  
\v 42 ezin bho̠ onin ekpo o̠nyani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠lei agu̠o̠ a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal rala, na̠ anwe̠r na̠ a̠ru ra̠ omugh. 
\p I̠na a̠b̠etina̠ na̠ agi̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iko i̠na ikiton na̠ e̠ni̠r i̠na.  
\v 43 Odi ani̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠, ma̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rughom eb̠la̠ ikpoki d̠o̠yo̠, ad̠u̠a ma̠ owil a̠ten owil ma̠ okokua̠n asu̠nwe̠r anwani̠ ola̠ asi̠ na̠ e̠gbo̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ala, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠rue ma̠ okoko o̠yo̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 44 Ani̠ bho̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ aman a̠ru, sa̠ ra̠ a̠kula̠n akapa ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, ma̠ esi bho̠ u̠labh d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠. D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠ sa̠ asi̠ bho̠ isobha̠n. 
\p  
\v 45 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen a̠kula̠n ami̠?” 
\p Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠ku̠a, sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ e̠ni̠ran na̠ ekulugha̠n anwa.” 
\p  
\v 46 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ a̠kula̠n ami̠, ezin bho̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠loghoma̠n ma̠ a̠limon na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu d̠ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 47 Igiel bho̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠loghoma̠n ma̠ i̠na ko orue d̠o̠ awo̠gi̠na ad̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠rugugu a̠mutuma̠, a̠mel a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. Sa̠ i̠na agba d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, ma̠ ezin wa̠ i̠na atu̠n a̠kula̠n i̠na bho̠, sekina̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠d̠um d̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠ bho̠.  
\v 48 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠nyani̠ bho̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠umeni nyam. Gi̠e̠ na̠ ekima̠.” 
\p  
\v 49 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Azari̠o̠s, we̠mu̠ u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, a̠ru ra̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠nyani̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠mugh. Ko onyegi mu ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.”  
\v 50 Ya̠a̠, obhel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Azari̠o̠s ma̠a̠, “Ko oghil a̠rugugu; d̠umome ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠um.”  
\v 51 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠misi d̠a̠ otu bho̠, i̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ ologi, a̠ten A̠pita̠, Azo̠n na̠ A̠zemsi, na̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠.  
\v 52 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ na̠ a̠sorogi ma̠ izin na̠ e̠ku̠nu̠. Ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko oleghe mu, o̠nyani̠ bho̠ na̠ omugh d̠o̠, na̠ a̠kod̠u a̠kod̠ua̠.”  
\v 53 Sa̠ awa i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na, d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ awa iloghom ma̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠mugh bho̠.  
\v 54 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠sibh o̠nyani̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “O̠nyani̠ bho̠, b̠etina̠!”  
\v 55 Sa̠ e̠mu̠gh o̠nyani̠ bho̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ egbo. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom awa ma̠ onigha̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n.\fig O̠nyani̠ ta̠ Azari̠o̠s na̠ ogbo i̠ku̠nu̠|alt="Jarius daughter with mourners" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 8:55" copy="LB00311" ref="8:55" \fig* 
\v 56 Sa̠ id̠igh ilologia̠n ma̠ oweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠. Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s anyagh ra̠to d̠awa a̠fugh ma̠ awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠ enigha̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠. 
\c 9  
\s1 A̠duom wa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 10:5-15; Amaki̠ 6:7-13) 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s a̠kokod̠i ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ a̠limon na̠ a̠dila̠de obhin oze eb̠la̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh o̠sighe̠gi̠ na̠ okoko rasu̠nwe̠r.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom awa ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠gba ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ omutiom, na̠ okoko ogbo asu̠nwe̠r.  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko obhin bebina̠ abar eb̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠: a̠d̠igh okpeti, a̠d̠igh e̠kpa e̠gi̠, a̠d̠igh ed̠ia̠n, a̠d̠igh okpoki; ukpe onwegina̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ nyen.  
\v 4 E̠ma ola̠ inyin ud̠igh, ikpone ma̠ onin otu ma̠ esul e̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠, tu̠tu̠n inyin ta̠ ob̠etina̠ o̠d̠u̠a.  
\v 5 E̠ma ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ o̠d̠a d̠o̠ inyin ebhin, ikpukpu ma̠ ibhugh e̠b̠ab̠a a̠sike d̠inyin ma̠ esorogi, ma̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a. Obha̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh ma̠a̠ awa na̠ e̠so̠n ebhum ase̠ ebhin.”  
\v 6 Sa̠ awa ib̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ e̠ma iten e̠ma, i̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ ikoko ma̠ a̠nwunom kesikesi. 
\s1 Asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an ta̠ E̠ro̠d 
\r (Amatiu 14:1-12; Amaki̠ 6:14-29) 
\p  
\v 7 Igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d o̠li̠la ebhugh Agalili amu̠gho̠n a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ emite bho̠, sa̠ asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an. Ezin bho̠ idi a̠nwunom na̠ e̠gba ma̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.  
\v 8 Idi ogbo sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ owil I̠lai̠za a̠mula̠ a̠ru, ya̠a̠ ipa̠n ogbo sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ odi opa̠n owil igied̠i a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.  
\v 9 E̠ro̠d sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Azo̠n, sa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠sobh e̠mu̠ bho̠. Ya̠a̠ onon ka̠ a̠nyen wa̠ ami̠ na̠ amu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ a̠gboloma̠ bho̠?” Sa̠ i̠na a̠wia̠n ibom o̠bi̠gh A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ni̠gha̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala o̠ni̠ 
\r (Amatiu 14:13-21; Amaki̠ 6:30-44; Azo̠n 6:1-14) 
\p  
\v 10 Igiel bho̠ ogbo ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s imula̠ iru bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa ibhin irile d̠a̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin awa ab̠o̠i̠ny ad̠u̠a agi̠ d̠a̠ aka e̠ma Abe̠tsai̠da.  
\v 11 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ iloghom agba wa̠ awa iten bho̠, sa̠ i̠tu̠ ma̠ e̠b̠a i̠gi̠ ani̠ ma̠ esi bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na ada awa a̠bhin, agba ma̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠nigha̠ awa, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan a̠li̠kokua̠n. 
\p  
\v 12 D̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n a̠dule, sa̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na, sa̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠ “Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ eten e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma na̠ a̠risi ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ eghighira̠ bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awa e̠bho̠ro̠gh e̠te̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n na̠ a̠risi ya̠ okod̠u. Ezin bho̠ onon esi ola̠ a̠nwunom orugh d̠o̠.” 
\p  
\v 13 Ya̠a̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Inigha̠ awa ma̠ abar od̠e.” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠yar unwuna̠ ogho ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠ ku̠ku̠m; a̠ten ka̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ ogho ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ ta̠ elei eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n.”  
\v 14 (O̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom\f + \fr 9:14 \ft I̠gbara-anwi̠i̠ny na̠ anwani̠ id̠igh ani̠ d̠o̠.\f* bho̠ ta̠ elei agu̠o̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala (5,000) i̠ro̠.) 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Gba ma̠ awa e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ebu ebu; ebu i̠se̠ eruba̠l na̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠.”  
\v 15 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ igir agu̠o̠ i̠na ato̠ bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de.  
\v 16 I̠na a̠bhin ogho ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠pupugion a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠gi̠ onigha̠ a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 17 Eb̠la̠ awa id̠e ilegha̠n sa̠ idi ed̠ia̠n bho̠ isugho. Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ikpokpo ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ya̠ imuzo ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal a̠rukpuom. 
\s1 A̠pita̠ agba ma̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutiom 
\p  
\v 18 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ esi na̠ a̠siseiny, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na. Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “A̠nwunom na̠ e̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ka̠ a̠nyen?” 
\p  
\v 19 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Idi ogbo na̠ e̠gba ma̠ anwa Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠; idi sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ anwa I̠lai̠za; ya̠a̠ ipa̠n sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ odi owil igied̠i a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.” 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin u̠bi̠gh ani̠ eka̠. Inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ka̠ a̠nyen?” Sa̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st\f + \fr 9:20 \fq Akrai̠st: \ft O̠ni̠ Wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠doni bho̠. Ame̠saya d̠a̠ Iburu na̠ Akrai̠st d̠a̠ A̠griki ima̠ra̠ onin abar.\f* wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ afi̠ri̠ma bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ omugh  //  na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s anyagh ra̠to d̠awa ma̠ awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ abar onon enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.  
\v 22 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Na̠ o̠to̠ oguri ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ abi̠gh a̠d̠izo ali̠gam a̠ruzu, sa̠ ikei bho̠ na̠ aru̠li̠la bho̠, na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo-atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, ta̠ eghel i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ egigh i̠na. Sa̠, oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.”  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ ebhir o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ami̠, o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠gineni ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar, a̠b̠eton e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠.  
\v 24 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh otenemeni a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠, ko o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul. Ya̠a̠, ka̠ i̠na atu̠n ami̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠, i̠na ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul.  
\v 25 Ere ma̠ asu̠o̠ bho̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ate̠i̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom, sa̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ a̠dinom?  
\v 26 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠din ami̠ na̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠ami̠ a̠ghil ari̠ghe̠l, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ obha̠, ma̠ igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ ita̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ ita̠ itileduom e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 27 “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, idi inyin ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, ko omugh d̠o̠ tu̠tu̠n awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\s1 I̠sar ogbo-ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s i̠bi̠gh isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ 
\p  
\v 28 D̠a̠ a̠bin o̠bhabhanya a̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin A̠pita̠ na̠ A̠zemsi̠ na̠ Azo̠n asi̠n igu ka̠ a̠d̠igh a̠siseiny.  
\v 29 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠siseiny bho̠, sa̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nwegia̠n, sa̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ i̠mu̠ isosorogia̠n e̠b̠alab̠al.  
\v 30 Sa̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom, A̠mozizi na̠ I̠lai̠za imite ma̠ awai̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠na i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an.\fig Onwegina̠ ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s|alt="Jesus transfigured" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 9:30" copy="LB00317" ref="9:30" \fig* 
\v 31 A̠mozizi na̠ I̠lai̠za esosorogia̠n o̠bi̠gh, sa̠ i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an igboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s ta̠ a̠bhin a̠muzoghod̠iom i̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ma̠ obhel ola̠ ko obia̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 32 Adi̠la ibhinom A̠pita̠ na̠ i̠wal ogbo-ogir iyed̠i ma̠ igiel bho̠; ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ awa i̠su̠ma iloghoma̠n ozu bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh isosorogia̠n ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom na̠ ed̠igh na̠ i̠na e̠mara.  
\v 33 Igiel bho̠ A̠mozizi na̠ I̠lai̠za ib̠etina̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “E Wa̠nwuna̠, ya̠ a̠bhon i̠yar o̠ro̠ i̠se̠n! D̠ighi i̠yar ta̠ ogim i̠sar a̠rutu akpu̠ru̠; odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ oyom, odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠mozizi, sa̠ odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ I̠lai̠za.” (I̠na na̠ o̠da d̠o̠ a̠loghom abar wa̠ i̠na a̠fugh bho̠ nyen.) 
\p  
\v 34 I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh sa̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh a̠mite a̠kpegiom eb̠la̠ awa; sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh A̠pita̠, A̠zemsi̠ na̠ Azo̠n d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ a̠kpegiom awa bho̠.  
\v 35 Sa̠ okoroko a̠si a̠mite d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Onon O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ Ami̠ na̠ aso̠n bho̠. I̠nagha i̠na!”  
\v 36 Igiel bho̠ okoroko bho̠ na̠ a̠fugh awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m a̠sughonom esi bho̠. Ogbo-ogir bho̠ iguri ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa i̠bi̠gh bho̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa; bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ obhel obha̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ola̠  //  o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh aro̠ d̠a̠ ozu 
\p  
\v 37 I̠b̠ala bho̠ sa̠ awa isor d̠a̠ igu bho̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 38 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ologi o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠kele i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠! Siseiny, kpone ma̠ ogini o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir.  
\v 39 O̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ a̠puom gha̠n i̠na, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠kpogion na̠ a̠mulughu ma̠ izul. Sa̠ i̠na na̠ asalaghu̠ na̠ a̠mutioghom ofuko d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠. Na̠ a̠guri gha̠n na̠ a̠gbikimeni i̠na ma̠ o̠ku̠a na̠ alo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ i̠ne̠m, sa̠ na̠ o̠nu̠r ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠we̠le̠man o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠.  
\v 40 Ami̠ i̠le̠gh ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom ma̠ oze o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠, ya̠a̠ irue d̠o̠.” 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “E! Amu̠m ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠to̠, ya̠ ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ i̠kpe̠! Ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ inyin aro̠ a̠bia̠ eka̠? Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ne ma̠ ado̠l d̠inyin a̠bia̠ eka̠?” Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Bhine ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠oyom a̠ru ma̠ enen.”  
\v 42 Igiel bho̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠rile na̠ a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ agu̠ro̠m i̠na, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ asasalaghu̠ a̠mutiom ofuko d̠a̠ o̠nu̠. Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠mulumeni i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 43 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ ilologia̠n o̠bi̠gh ibom e̠mi̠ a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mula̠ a̠wa̠ ma̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 17:22,23; Amaki̠ 9:30-32) 
\p Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ awa od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ ema̠gha̠, na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠,  
\v 44 “I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠ru ro̠ o̠gba a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠, ma̠ e̠kpabh e̠bham: ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom.”  
\v 45 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ i̠na agba bho̠. U̠wo̠gi̠o̠m awa, sa̠ awa o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ awa ighil opura̠n o̠yo̠ ma̠ ezin bho̠. 
\s1 A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠? 
\r (Amatiu 18:1-5; Amaki̠ 9:33-37) 
\p  
\v 46 Sa̠ aku̠anan a̠sor d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa bho̠.  
\v 47 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa, sa̠ a̠bhin o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ amarame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ aka d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 48 Sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ola̠ atu̠n a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ ada ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ onon a̠bhin, bha̠ ada ami̠ a̠bhin. O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a ab̠aram na̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ruom ami̠ ma̠ oru bho̠ ada a̠bhin. O̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu a̠pu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, abu̠gh a̠pu.” 
\s1 O̠ni̠ ola̠ owia̠n d̠o̠ inyin od̠i na̠ inyin 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:38-40) 
\p  
\v 49 Sa̠ Azo̠n agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar u̠bi̠gh odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh sa̠ i̠yar u̠ghaghana i̠na, ezin bho̠ i̠na bo̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠i̠yar.”  
\v 50 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko o̠ghaghana i̠na; ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ owia̠n d̠o̠ inyin od̠i na̠ inyin.” 
\s1 Odi o̠gbara e̠ma Asameria̠ igin A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 51 Igiel bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n A̠zizo̠s obhun d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ato̠ d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m.  
\v 52 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom a̠nwunom od̠ia̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ odi e̠ma Asameria̠, okokod̠ia̠n ob̠a̠ra̠ o̠yo̠;  
\v 53 Ya̠a̠ a̠nwunom e̠ma bho̠ i̠da d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ebhin, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ ada na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m be̠le̠ni̠.  
\v 54 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n i̠bi̠gh o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ awa ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar okele ma̠ anya ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠sor abhu̠gi̠ awa ke̠re̠?”  
\v 55 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠tiba̠ra̠ agamam awa. (Inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien e̠mu̠gh wa̠ inyin u̠te̠i̠ bho̠. O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ oru d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ze̠ a̠nwunom; ya̠a̠ i̠na atu̠n otenemeni a̠nwunom a̠ru)\f + \fr 9:55 \ft Idi i̠pu̠r ra̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ ya̠ ubhin agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ i̠lo̠gh ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠nye̠n.\f*.  
\v 56 Sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n o̠gbara e̠ma. 
\s1 Ado̠l O̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 57 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ erile d̠a̠ eten na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ atu̠o̠no̠m anwa agi̠ kesikesi ola̠ anwa na̠ agi̠.” 
\p  
\v 58 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Rududu enwuna̠ ma̠ iyol ya̠ awa na̠ erugh, i̠nu̠r eka̠ enwuna̠ ma̠ a̠rutu; ya̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ od̠igh ob̠enegiom e̠mu̠.” 
\p  
\v 59 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, “Tu̠o̠no̠me̠ ami̠.” 
\p Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, d̠ighi ami̠ id̠ia̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ id̠i ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 60 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “We̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gh bho̠ ma̠ od̠i imumugh d̠awa. Ya̠a̠, anwa gi̠e̠ ka̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\p  
\v 61 Sa̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ ta̠ atu̠o̠no̠m anwa, ya̠a̠ d̠ighi ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ eghun otu d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠ awa e̠mar e̠ro̠.” 
\p  
\v 62 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠sibh e̠su̠a\f + \fr 9:62 \ft E̠su̠a: Onon e̠su̠a ola̠ u̠kpu̠o̠m d̠a̠ e̠nam, sa̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠sibh na̠ a̠rileghom na̠ a̠b̠u ma̠ a̠de.\f* ola̠ u̠kpu̠o̠m d̠a̠ i̠nam na̠ ob̠u ma̠ a̠de, sa̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ aman, na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir ogir irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”\fig O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠sibh e̠su̠a ola̠ u̠kpu̠o̠m d̠a̠ i̠nam|alt="Man ploughing yoke oxen" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 9:62" copy="LB00018" ref="9:62" \fig* 
\c 10  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom a̠duom  //  e̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ 
\p  
\v 1 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ aso̠n ipa̠n e̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire i̠gba ma̠ i̠na aso̠n e̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh ogbo atu̠ghan.\f* ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ato̠to̠gi̠ awa, ma̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠ ma̠ ebu, ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma na̠ a̠risi ya̠ i̠na na̠ ato̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ed̠ia̠n ob̠u eb̠uiy, ya̠a̠, ogbo od̠ighi bho̠ e̠ki̠r; ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, isiseinye ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ib̠ua̠ bho̠ ma̠ i̠na a̠ruom ogbo od̠ighi a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 3 I̠gi̠e̠! Ami̠ na̠ a̠ruom inyin agu̠o̠ ro̠nana d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io o̠lo̠gh i̠gagaman i̠nam.\fig Ro̠nana na̠ i̠gagaman i̠nam|alt="Sheep and wolves" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 10:3" copy="LB00011" ref="10:3" \fig* 
\v 4 O̠ni̠ ko obhin e̠kpa ola̠ ikpoki, bo̠d̠o̠ e̠kpa e̠gi̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ragbaka. O̠ni̠ ko obhelegima̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ eten nyen. 
\p  
\v 5 “Kotukotu ola̠ inyin ud̠igh id̠ia̠ ma̠ efugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ekima̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ otu onon!’  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ekima̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ ekima̠ d̠inyin ta̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ awa. Ya̠a̠ o̠ku̠a bo̠, ekima̠ d̠inyin ta̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin.  
\v 7 Ka̠ inyin ud̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma, o̠ni̠ o̠d̠u̠a ma̠ otu ma̠ eten otu. I̠ri̠la d̠a̠ onin otu bho̠. Id̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, ma̠ e̠d̠a ma̠ amu̠m ya̠ awa ta̠ enigha̠ inyin bho̠. Ezin bho̠, o̠ni̠ ogir bho̠ a̠sora̠n o̠te̠i̠ alu̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 8 “Ka̠ inyin ud̠i̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ma i̠se̠, sa̠ awa i̠da inyin ibhin, id̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ awa ta̠ enigha̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 9 Ikoko ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r bho̠, ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, ‘Irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, od̠i d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠a agu̠o̠.’  
\v 10 Ka̠ inyin ud̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma, sa̠ o̠da d̠o̠ inyin ebhin, bha̠ i̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ reten ma̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠,  
\v 11 ‘Ibhugh a̠de e̠ma d̠inyin ya̠ i̠kpabh d̠a̠ a̠sike d̠i̠yar bho̠ eka̠, i̠yar na̠ okpukpu osoroni onigha̠ inyin. Obha̠ elegh ola̠ ta̠ a̠leriom ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠bhumeni inyin. Ya̠a̠ iloghome ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n.’  
\v 12 Ami̠ na̠ amar na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠leriom okpon igbirigbir Aso̠do̠m a̠pu ma̠ a̠nwunom e̠ma obha̠. 
\s1 Re̠ma ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 11:20-24) 
\p  
\v 13 “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ anwa, A̠kora̠zin! Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ anwa, Abe̠tsai̠da! Ezin bho̠, ilologia̠n ya̠ ugir unigha̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠ ugir onigha̠ ma̠ Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n nab̠o̠, awa na̠ etiba̠ra̠ ka̠ obom igiel, sa̠ awa ka̠ izum e̠ro̠ na̠ akapa i̠ku̠nu̠ na̠ i̠ru̠ru̠.  
\v 14 Okpon igbirigbir ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n epu inyin d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠.  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, inyin a̠nwunom Akapanu̠m, ta̠ obhuneni inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ke̠re̠? E̠nyi̠, ta̠ orobh inyin osoroni d̠a̠ imumugh bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan do̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ada ma̠ a̠duom d̠inyin a̠bhin ada ami̠ a̠bhin. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠ghel inyin a̠ghel ami̠. O̠ku̠a a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠ghel ami̠ ab̠aram na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠ruom ami̠ ma̠ a̠duom bho̠ a̠ghel.” 
\p  
\v 17 E̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ya̠ i̠na aso̠n bho̠ imula̠ iru na̠ a̠libhon ologi sa̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh eka̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien d̠oyom.” 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Yii, ami̠ i̠bi̠gh ka̠ Eru bho̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠mel a̠sor, ka̠ i̠me̠me̠gi̠na agbararan.  
\v 19 Ikpone! Ami̠ na̠ a̠ni̠gha̠ inyin a̠limon ya̠ obhin o̠ze̠re̠gi̠ i̠karabh-i̠di̠ar na̠ id̠ekebi, na̠ a̠limon ya̠ i̠kpo̠luzu ipel eb̠la̠ a̠li̠mon ta̠ Eru; bebina̠ abar ola̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ od̠ighia̠nma̠ bo̠.  
\v 20 Na̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a bho̠ eka̠, o̠ni̠ ko obhon ologi d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ a̠ruru bho̠ na̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi na̠ enigha̠ inyin bho̠, ya̠a̠ ibhone ma̠ ologi ma̠ na̠ o̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny.” 
\p  
\v 21 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠muzo na̠ a̠li̠bhon ologi ta̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ ase̠bh anwa O̠we̠de̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠de ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa i̠wo̠gi̠o̠m i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n iloghom ma̠ i̠di̠ar sekina̠ iloghom ma̠ a̠d̠ire bho̠, ya̠a̠ anwa ileriom ka̠ ma̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n. Yii, o̠we̠de̠, a̠d̠igh anwa ma̠ ologi ma̠ ogir o̠ku̠a. 
\p  
\v 22 “O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom O̠nyi̠ bho̠ bo̠, a̠ten O̠we̠de̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ a̠ten O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠ aso̠n oleriom o̠yo̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ma̠a̠, “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠rid̠ien ya̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠.  
\v 24 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ ebhir a̠d̠izo a̠riwil na̠ aru̠li̠le̠ma ma̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠ ya̠a̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠, na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠ ya̠a̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ob̠eb̠i O̠ni̠ Asameria̠ 
\p  
\v 25 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ aku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ad̠a ma̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kpon. Sa̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul?” 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “U̠ge̠ ma̠ ere d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire oloko bho̠? Anwa isen i̠mu̠gho̠nyan eka̠?” 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Anwa ta̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠limon d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠oyom a̠tula̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom; sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠tula̠n i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ aka d̠oyom bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ozu d̠oyom.” 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa̠ amar awo̠ran. Gire ma̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠d̠um.” 
\p  
\v 29 D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ abho̠ro̠gh oleriom ma̠ i̠na ab̠ab̠ala bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ aka d̠a̠ ami̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 30 A̠zizo̠s a̠mulumeni agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m na̠ a̠sor na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Aze̠riko. Sa̠ i̠na a̠mel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ a̠b̠igh. Sa̠ i̠fo̠i̠ny i̠na i̠ke̠gi̠o̠n ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠, id̠ul i̠na i̠fu̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ iten i̠d̠u̠a.  
\v 31 A̠mite ma̠ ola̠ odi okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ awo̠l ani̠ d̠a̠ onin eten bho̠. Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ab̠e̠i̠ eten bho̠ agbal ad̠u̠a.  
\v 32 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ eghun ta̠ A̠livai̠, o̠lo̠ghmagu̠o̠ d̠a̠ Otu-a̠siseiny bho̠, a̠ru ra̠ abi̠gh i̠na, sa̠ i̠na ab̠e̠i̠ eten bho̠ agbal ad̠u̠a.  
\v 33 Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ Asameria̠ na̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ eten bho̠ sa̠ abi̠gh i̠na, sa̠ igbirigbir o̠ni̠ bho̠ isibh i̠na.  
\v 34 I̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin amu̠nu̠ na̠ a̠min a̠zuom i̠ne̠m bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin ukpe a̠bhurugi ma̠ i̠ne̠m o̠ni̠ bho̠. Sa̠ a̠bhin i̠na agbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ e̠nam d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠igh gha̠n na̠ a̠rile bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ otu-esul, sa̠ a̠kponom i̠na.  
\v 35 I̠b̠ala bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠mutiom i̠wal adi̠nari̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ okponom ma̠ otu-esul bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ okponom ma̠ otu-esul bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Kponome ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon a̠nigha̠ ami̠. Ami̠ na̠ agi̠ na̠ a̠ru. Ka̠ anwa irughom ipa̠n ikpoki i̠b̠aram, ami̠ ta̠ a̠mulumeni ma̠ anwa.’ ” 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ i̠sar a̠nwunom bho̠, ka̠ a̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠mel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ib̠igh ma̠ a̠b̠igh bho̠, ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ aka d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ aku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠na wa̠ a̠kpon o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠ igbirigbir bho̠.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠gir ani̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠zua̠n wa̠ A̠meri na̠ Amata 
\p  
\v 38 D̠a̠ erile ta̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠te̠i̠ odi e̠ma ola̠ odi ani̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Amata ada awa a̠bhin a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 39 I̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ u̠marani̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠meri, ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ anagha ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 40 Ya̠a̠ a̠d̠izo rogir i̠ki̠o̠m bho̠ na̠ e̠vi̠mo̠m Amata. Sa̠ Amata agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ i̠na sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, a̠bhon agu̠o̠ u̠marani̠ d̠ami̠ awe̠le̠man eb̠la̠ ogir i̠ki̠o̠m bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠? Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na a̠ru ra̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Amata, O Amata, anwa na̠ anyo̠gho̠ghan na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar.  
\v 42 Onin ob̠eb̠i abar ku̠ku̠m ola̠ akpe̠ ma̠ o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan ogboloma̠. A̠meri na̠ aso̠n abar bho̠ a̠bhin, o̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ awo̠r i̠na a̠bhin.” 
\c 11  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ Osiseiny A̠siseiny 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠siseiny odi esi, sa̠ obhel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠siseiny awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠yar agu̠o̠ o̠sisieny a̠sisieny, ma̠ agu̠o̠ Azo̠n a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 2 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Igiel inyin na̠ osiseiny, ifughe ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘O̠we̠de̠, 
\q1 a̠d̠ien d̠oyom aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ e̠tu̠tu̠. 
\q1 Irileghom d̠oyom eru. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ed̠ia̠n ya̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, nigha̠ i̠yar ya̠ a̠didon. 
\q1  
\v 4 We̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠i̠yar, 
\q1 agu̠o̠ bho̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh ya̠ ipa̠n ogbo na̠ ed̠ighi i̠yar bho̠. 
\q1 Ya̠a̠, ko oma̠ra̠ i̠yar omel d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an.’ ” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ a̠wa̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen inyin ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠tologha̠n, sa̠ agi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ egum a̠d̠io ka̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘O̠mo̠lo̠l, wo̠lo̠ni̠ane̠ ami̠ ma̠ i̠sar ikpokpogh abe̠re̠di̠.  
\v 6 Ezin bho̠, a̠tologha̠n olami̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ e̠gi̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠suloma̠ ami̠, ya̠a̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ obhi̠n o̠ki̠o̠m o̠yo̠.’  
\v 7 Ku̠gba ma̠ i̠na wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ologi otu bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Ko onyegi ami̠, na̠ o̠du̠ ma̠ otu bho̠, anwi̠i̠ny d̠ami̠ na̠ ami̠ na̠ od̠igh o̠managhan. Ami̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam abar.’  
\v 8 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠na ko o̠tu̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ awa ra̠tologha̠n be̠le̠ni̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na; ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ i̠na od̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ ari̠ghe̠l sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ okpukpu okpukpu\f + \fr 11:8 \fq Aro̠ ma̠ okpukpu okpukpu: \ft D̠a̠ od̠ud̠ul Iburu, ob̠a̠na̠ otu bho̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ka̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠puru bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na na̠ od̠igh ari̠ghe̠l. Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire bho̠ irughom abe̠re̠di̠ na̠ o̠gbaki̠ghe̠\f* bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ka̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na kabar kabar ola̠ i̠na na̠ a̠puru. 
\p  
\v 9 “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠: ipuru sa̠ ta̠ onigha̠ inyin, i̠bho̠ro̠ghane̠ sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh, ikpukpu sa̠ ta̠ a̠guron.  
\v 10 Ezin bho̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠puru ta̠ onigha̠; ola̠ abho̠ro̠ghan ta̠ abi̠gh; ola̠ a̠kpukpu ta̠ oguron onigha̠. 
\p  
\v 11 “D̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin, ka̠ oken o̠we̠de̠ ola̠ ka̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠puru ma̠ ena̠ sa̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠karabh abar?  
\v 12 Bo̠d̠o̠, ka̠ a̠puru ma̠ aga e̠nu̠r, sa̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ id̠ekebi?  
\v 13 Ku̠gba ma̠ inyin rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠, ologhom agu̠o̠ onigha̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin, a̠dina̠mu ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠! I̠na ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ka̠ inyin upuru i̠na.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ A̠belzibul 
\p  
\v 14 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh emua̠ asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ ozu odi o̠ni̠. Igiel bho̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ ad̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ emua̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ake̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, idi awa d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ Abe̠lzi̠bu̠l, we̠mu̠ a̠ruru na̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh, na̠ a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠.”  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, ipa̠n ogbo, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠d̠a o̠yo̠ okpon, sa̠ i̠bho̠ro̠ghan i̠na ma̠ omutiom elegh ola̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny oleriom awa. 
\p  
\v 17 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom rologi d̠awa, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Irileghom ola̠ aru̠gi̠an na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ ago̠gu̠an a̠mel. Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, eghun ola̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu ta̠ a̠mel.  
\v 18 Ku̠gba ma̠ Eru bho̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠, ka̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ amara? Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ Abe̠lzi̠bu̠l na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru.  
\v 19 Ku̠gba ma̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ Abe̠lzi̠bu̠l na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru, ka̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin na̠ e̠bhin ere na̠ eze na̠ e̠se̠ghe̠gi̠? O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbo osobh ase̠ d̠inyin.  
\v 20 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru bho̠, bha̠ iloghome ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ inyin. 
\p  
\v 21 “Ku̠gba ma̠ omoma̠na̠n o̠ni̠ amar a̠kokod̠ia̠n o̠kpo̠ erorobhi\f + \fr 11:21 \fq O̠kpo̠ erorobhi: \ft O̠kpo̠ ya̠ na̠ obhin na̠ owe ma̠ e̠gham\f* d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠kponom otu d̠o̠yo̠; i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ekima̠.  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠mon a̠pu i̠na a̠wia̠n i̠na, sa̠ ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ i̠na, o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ghumi ma̠ eb̠la̠ o̠kpo̠ erorobhi d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠b̠em ologi bho̠ a̠bhin. Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠ghumi bho̠. 
\p  
\v 23 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ri̠la d̠o̠ na̠ ami̠ bha̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n ami̠; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠igh d̠o̠ na̠ ami̠ a̠kokod̠i bha̠ na̠ asasaragi̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s anyagh a̠to a̠gboloma̠ ma̠  //  omula̠ oru ta̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ 
\p  
\v 24 “Igiel o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠, ta̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ esi a̠ten esi abho̠ro̠gh esi ola̠ a̠sora̠n od̠igh o̠ro̠. Ya̠a̠, ka̠ i̠na o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi o̠ro̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ otu wa̠ ami̠ i̠d̠u̠a bho̠.’  
\v 25 Igiel i̠na a̠misi sa̠ abi̠gh ma̠ otu bho̠ na̠ o̠mar ogber o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠, oselegi ma̠ i̠di̠ar,  
\v 26 sa̠ i̠na ta̠ ka̠ a̠bhin od̠ua̠l ipa̠n i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh ya̠ i̠bho̠ru̠ ipu i̠na, sa̠ awa ta̠ ka̠ ed̠igh erugh d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ bho̠. Sa̠ e̠do̠lo̠ghu̠ma o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠gurom a̠pu ma̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r igiel bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠ga̠i Itutumeni 
\p  
\v 27 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ odi ani̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠, a̠b̠eton okoroko ma̠a̠, “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ otu-i̠mara wa̠ a̠rol anwa bho̠ na̠ amu̠mam ya̠ anwa i̠mam bho̠.”  
\v 28 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Itutumeni ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ kuma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ igir o̠ku̠a bho̠.” 
\s1 Elegh ta̠ A̠zona̠ 
\p  
\v 29 Agu̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ na̠ abu̠gh bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Onon amu̠m rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh. Na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠gh elegh; ya̠a̠, elegh ola̠ ta̠ oleriom awa bo̠, a̠ten elegh ta̠ A̠zona̠.  
\v 30 Agu̠o̠ A̠zona̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom A̠ninive bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ amu̠m onon.  
\v 31 D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, ani̠ebhom O̠li̠la ebhugh Ase̠ba ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ agba ma̠ a̠nwunom amu̠m onon e̠mar egir e̠pi̠e̠; ezin bho̠, i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom\f + \fr 11:31 \fq Ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom: \ft esi ola̠ a̠gbeiny opa̠n\f* a̠ru ra̠ atu̠ghan eloghom abar ta̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n!  
\v 32 D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, a̠nwunom A̠ninive ta̠ e̠mara, sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ a̠nwunom amu̠m onon e̠mar egir e̠pi̠e̠; ezin bho̠, awa e̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba ta̠ A̠zona̠ sa̠ awa itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ A̠zona̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n! 
\s1 Ato̠di̠ ozu bho̠ 
\p  
\v 33 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ asu̠o̠m ato̠di̠ sa̠ ta̠ alo̠gh esi awo̠gi̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ ekpukpu abo̠di̠ bo̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠na ta̠ agbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ abar, b̠o̠ka̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh esi bho̠ e̠bi̠gh e̠b̠alab̠al.  
\v 34 Ekpo-a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bha̠ ato̠di̠ ozu d̠oyom. Ku̠gba ma̠ ekpo-a̠d̠ien d̠oyom a̠bhon, bha̠ eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom ta̠ a̠muzo na̠ e̠b̠alab̠al. Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ekpo-a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ obhon d̠o̠, bha̠ eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom ta̠ a̠muzo na̠ azi̠m.  
\v 35 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, mare̠ ma̠ a̠kpona̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ e̠b̠alab̠al wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ozu d̠oyom bho̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ azi̠m.  
\v 36 Ku̠gba ma̠ eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom a̠muzo na̠ e̠b̠alab̠al, sa̠ azi̠m o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ esi, bha̠ ta̠ a̠muzo na̠ e̠b̠alab̠al kesikesi woma̠ ato̠di̠ na̠ awar e̠b̠alab̠al na̠ a̠zuom anwa.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s ali̠o̠m Rafarisi na̠ ogbo oloko bho̠ 
\p  
\v 37 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ odi Afarisi ale̠gh i̠na ma̠ oru ra̠ od̠igh na̠ o̠yo̠ od̠e abar. Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ab̠e̠d̠i̠an d̠a̠ akpata od̠e bho̠.\fig Ibura̠ a̠siseiny Afarisi|alt="Pharisee and phylactery" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 11:37" copy="LB00276" ref="11:37" \fig* 
\v 38 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n o̠ni̠ Afarisi bho̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ a̠tita̠la̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ kisa̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ma̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n bho̠.  
\v 39 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Inyin Rafarisi bho̠, inyin na̠ otitol aman okpa̠ko bho̠ na̠ e̠kpa bho̠; ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin bha̠ o̠ku̠ku̠ na̠ i̠karabh imuzo!  
\v 40 Sa̠ rema̠! Wale̠m aman bho̠ na̠ o̠b̠aram d̠o̠ na̠ ologi bho̠ ale̠m ke̠re̠?  
\v 41 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ibhine ma̠ onyen ologi ma̠ ebhin i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin unwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala enigha̠ inyin. 
\p  
\v 42 “Ekulom inyin Rafarisi! Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ obhin aghan-od̠od̠ua̠ na̠ u̠ki̠a na̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠gho̠gho̠ a̠mubobh, na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ odi a̠bin d̠a̠ a̠d̠iobh, sa̠ inyin ugin a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ na̠ etula̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. I̠nye̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ inyin ogir, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ onigha̠ a̠bin a̠d̠iobh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\p  
\v 43 “Ekulom inyin Rafarisi bho̠! Ezin bho̠ inyin uba̠ra̠ ma̠ ra̠dila̠de idoni d̠a̠ ru̠gala A̠zu, na̠ ipelegima̠ d̠a̠ regbolom a̠b̠ua̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 44 “Ekulom inyin Rafarisi bho̠! Ezin bho̠, inyin od̠i ka̠ ranyu̠od̠i ya̠ elegh o̠to̠, ya̠ a̠nwunom ologhom d̠o̠ sa̠ na̠ erile d̠a̠ anyu̠ na̠ eten.” 
\p  
\v 45 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ awa ola̠ na̠ aku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, anwa i̠b̠aram na̠ i̠yar a̠rogi d̠a̠ a̠fugh i̠nye̠n.” 
\p  
\v 46 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ekulom inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ roloko bho̠! Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ obhin a̠dol ya̠ i̠mu̠mo̠r na̠ o̠gbam d̠a̠ aru̠mu̠ a̠nwonom orol; ya̠a̠, inyin ub̠eton d̠o̠ ma̠ ad̠u̠nu̠ agu̠o̠ okula̠n a̠dol bho̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠. 
\p  
\v 47 “Ekulom inyin! Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ ob̠olob̠ol na̠ oburi ma̠ ranyu̠od̠i a̠riwil ya̠ ro̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin igigh bho̠.  
\v 48 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ inyin na̠ oleriom ma̠a̠, inyin oma̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ro̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin igir bho̠. Awa i̠ze̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ ob̠olob̠ol ranyu̠od̠i d̠awa.  
\v 49 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, d̠a̠ ibom eloghom abar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ afi̠ri̠ma ma̠ a̠riwil sekina̠ ogbo ogir agi̠o̠m a̠wa̠. Idi sa̠ a̠wa̠ ta̠ egigh, ipa̠n sa̠ a̠wa̠ ta̠ egbikimeni.’  
\v 50 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ta̠ osibh a̠nwunom a̠mu̠m onon odinom ebula̠ asi̠ ta̠ eb̠la̠ a̠riwil ya̠ u̠ze̠gi̠ bho̠, d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ i̠se̠n;  
\v 51 ob̠eton d̠a̠ asi̠ ta̠ Ebe̠l ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ asi̠ ta̠ Azakaraya wa̠ ugigh d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io enwen i̠ko̠l bho̠ na̠ a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ta̠ opuru ma̠ amu̠m onon ma̠ asi̠ i̠nye̠n. 
\p  
\v 52 “Ekulom inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ roloko A̠zu bho̠! Ezi̠n bho̠, inyin na̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ i̠sabi̠ eloghom abar bho̠. Inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ ud̠igh d̠o̠ ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ okigima̠ ma̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom od̠i̠gh.” 
\p  
\v 53 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ad̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ ogbo a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ owia̠n o̠yo̠, opupura̠n o̠yo̠ a̠d̠i̠zo i̠di̠ar,  
\v 54 opoiny o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠ ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh abar ola̠ awa ta̠ edin esibh i̠na. 
\c 12  
\s1 I̠kparakpar a̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ado̠l ibhelebhel 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ ipel a̠d̠usubh o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala, id̠u iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ odi na̠ aze̠r odi. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠ia̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ a̠yist Rafarisi bho̠, ya̠ awa na̠ e̠gba ma̠ ipa̠n na̠ egir ipa̠n bho̠.  
\v 2 Abar ola̠ ukpegiom ola̠ ko omite d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma bo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ola̠ odi d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ola̠ ko ologhom d̠o̠ bo̠.  
\v 3 Abar ola̠ inyin ufugh d̠a̠ a̠d̠io azi̠m, ola̠ a̠nwunom ka̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ etita̠n a̠d̠io bo̠, abar ola̠ inyin ubhobhula̠ d̠a̠ re̠bhai̠, ta̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ a̠rutu\f + \fr 12:3 \fq Anyu̠ a̠rutu: \ft Anyu̠ a̠rutu a̠nwunom A̠zu d̠a̠ obhel bho̠ otutula̠n, ola̠ na̠ orue na̠ o̠si̠n na̠ o̠ro̠.\f* o̠gba o̠sasaragi̠. 
\s1 O̠ni̠ wa̠ oghil bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 10:28-31) 
\p  
\v 4 “Ra̠tologha̠n d̠ami̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ko oghil ogbo ya̠ na̠ egigh ozu bho̠ sa̠ ko orue mu egir opa̠n abar e̠lo̠gho̠m.  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin o̠kparakpar okoroko na̠ a̠kikiom inyin o̠ni̠ wa̠ akpe̠ inyin oghil bho̠: ighile i̠na wa̠, ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gigh ozu bho̠ awe̠le̠, sa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon orobh inyin o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠banya bho̠. Yii, ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠na wa̠ oghil bho̠.  
\v 6 Uwol d̠o̠ ma̠ ogho ikpo ro̠gi̠e̠ ta̠ egule ma̠ i̠wal ape̠ni̠ ke̠re̠? Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, bebina̠ onin awa ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠weleta̠n bo̠.  
\v 7 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, eb̠la̠ ikpo asi̠ghal aru̠mu̠ d̠inyin eka̠ na̠ o̠wal. O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu; inyin ulei abar opu ma̠ o̠lo̠gh ro̠gi̠e̠ ta̠ egule. 
\s1 O̠gba Akrai̠st omutiom na̠ oghel o̠yo̠  //  d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom 
\r (Amatiu 10:32-33; 12:32; 10:19-20) 
\p  
\v 8 “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ agba ami̠ a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ agba ani̠ i̠na a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠misigh itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ aku̠a ami̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom, ta̠ o̠ku̠a ani̠ i̠na d̠a̠ a̠misigh itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 10 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠, ta̠ okpon o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ko okpon d̠o̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien. 
\p  
\v 11 “Igiel uler inyin iku d̠a̠ u̠gala A̠zu, sa̠ u̠marame̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo ya̠ na̠ erileghom ebhugh bho̠ na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ bho̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠wo̠yo̠ghan awa, bo̠d̠o̠ agu̠o̠ obhin o̠gba o̠nu̠.  
\v 12 Ezin bho̠, E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ta̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ o̠ku̠a, ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ isora̠n o̠gba omutiom bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh ema̠ o̠li̠la bho̠ 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, fughe ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠ami̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na na̠ ami̠ ta̠ o̠ru̠gi̠an ad̠i̠a o̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar.”  
\v 14 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ bho̠, a̠nyen aso̠n ami̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ osobh ma̠ ase̠, bo̠d̠o̠ wi̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠inyin?”  
\v 15 Sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠! I̠we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere ado̠l o̠ku̠ku̠; a̠ga̠i a̠ghud̠um o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ bo̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠ e̠li̠la ya̠ i̠na a̠gbo bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “O̠si̠ odi o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ a̠mite ma̠ opa̠n.  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na aru̠ru̠an d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠se̠n ka̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠? Ami̠ inwuna̠ mu ma̠ esi okpol ed̠ia̠n d̠ami̠ oguri ya̠ eko.’ 
\p  
\v 18 “Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ogion re̠kpe̠ okoko ed̠ia̠n d̠ami̠ a̠lo ma̠ ipa̠n ya̠ i̠bu̠gh ipu ma̠ i̠nye̠n. Sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighoghom eb̠la̠ ed̠ia̠n ib̠ua̠ d̠ami̠ a̠kpol d̠a̠ ologi.  
\v 19 Sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ a̠kpol ed̠ia̠n a̠guri ma̠ iya̠ eko ya̠ ta̠ elei od̠e a̠d̠izo rala d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ri̠la ti̠to̠i̠ny ma̠ a̠d̠e, ma̠ ad̠a, ma̠ ad̠e̠ ma̠ o̠d̠e̠.” ’ 
\p  
\v 20 “Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Sa̠ ema̠! A̠d̠uga̠la̠n onon, ta̠ opuru nyam a̠ghud̠um d̠oyom. Sa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa ikokod̠i iguri bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠nyen?’ 
\p  
\v 21 “Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠kpol i̠di̠ar a̠guri a̠sisa̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man ogbo e̠li̠la d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\s1 I̠ku̠nu̠ na̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh ologi 
\r (Amatiu 6:25-34) 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan ologi ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠inyin, a̠d̠igh abar ola̠ inyin ta̠ od̠e; bo̠d̠o̠ abar ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠lagha.  
\v 23 Ezin bho̠, a̠ghud̠um a̠lei abar a̠pu ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, sa̠ ozu o̠ni̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu ma̠ ibura̠.  
\v 24 Ikpone ma̠ ed̠ighom a̠ghud̠um i̠nu̠r ya̠ od̠i ka̠ e̠gbar bho̠: Awa igbebh d̠o̠, awa ib̠u d̠o̠, inwuna̠ d̠o̠ nyen e̠bhai̠, bo̠d̠o̠ e̠kpe̠ ola̠ okpol ed̠ia̠n. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠koko awa. Ya̠a̠, inyin ulei abar opu ma̠ i̠nu̠r ya̠ na̠ e̠bhe̠bh d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠!  
\v 25 O̠ni̠ inyin ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan ologi alo̠gho̠m ekud̠i obhel d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ od̠i ke̠re̠?  
\v 26 Ku̠gba ma̠ inyin ko orue d̠o̠ ogir o̠gbara abar ola̠ o̠ku̠a, ka̠ inyin ta̠ odin ere o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan ologi ogboloma̠ ma̠ ipa̠n i̠di̠ar? 
\p  
\v 27 “Ikpone ma̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um ra̠lele bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ ebhin na̠ e̠su̠ bho̠. Awa igir d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠kparakpar ogir, awa ilo d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠lo nyen. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ a̠ga̠i Aso̠lo̠mo̠n eka̠, d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ obura̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ya̠ ibhon ile̠i ita̠ odi a̠lele i̠se̠.  
\v 28 Ku̠gba ma̠ obha̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠buri ma̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠, ya̠ a̠didon od̠i sa̠ elegien ta̠ orobh o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ anya bho̠, o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠buri inyin a̠peleni ma̠ o̠ku̠a-inyin ogbo ya̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠ bho̠!  
\v 29 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, o̠ni̠ ko onigha̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin ma̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ od̠e, bo̠d̠o̠ ya̠ o̠d̠a; o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan egboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 30 Ezin bho̠, a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom onon, na̠ ewia̠n o̠te̠i̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠, ya̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin a̠loghom ma̠ a̠bhon inyin o̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠.  
\v 31 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠bho̠ro̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ta̠ o̠b̠ar na̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n onigha̠ inyin. 
\s1 E̠li̠la d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny 
\r (Amatiu 6:19-21) 
\p  
\v 32 “Inyin o̠gbara o̠lo̠gh, o̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu. Ezin bho̠, a̠d̠igh ologi ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin onigha̠ inyin irileghom bho̠.  
\v 33 Iwole ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin unwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ ebhin e̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠. Iguri ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ eko d̠inyin d̠a̠ e̠kpa ola̠ ko o̠ghu̠r d̠o̠, i̠di̠ar ya̠ ilei abar d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ya̠ ko omunia̠n d̠o̠; d̠a̠ esi ola̠ aru̠gba ko otua̠n d̠o̠, sa̠ afi̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠d̠e api̠e̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 34 Esi wa̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ilei abar d̠inyin od̠i bho̠, i̠se̠ esi rologi d̠inyin ta̠ e̠ro̠ nyen. 
\s1 Okokod̠ia̠n ogon eruoma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:45-51) 
\p  
\v 35 “I̠kpaki̠ane̠ ma̠ e̠kpo̠a ma̠ ro̠kara, ma̠ e̠su̠o̠m rato̠di̠ d̠inyin e̠ro̠ ma̠ omumor omumor,  
\v 36 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ib̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ na̠ egon wa̠nwuna̠ d̠awa ma̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ erogh omula̠ oru, b̠o̠ka̠ obhel i̠na ra̠ a̠kpukpu awa e̠nu̠r eguron enigha̠.  
\v 37 Ta̠ ebhon enigha̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠awa ta̠ ra̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa i̠ro̠ na̠ egon i̠na, ma̠ igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ a̠bura̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ogir iyo̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh awa ma̠ o̠ro̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 38 Ta̠ ebhon enigha̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠awa ta̠ ra̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa i̠ro̠ na̠ egon i̠na; i̠na a̠ru ka̠ ma̠ egum a̠d̠io, bo̠d̠o̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠ eka̠.  
\v 39 Ya̠a̠, i̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar onon: Ku̠gba ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ amar a̠loghom obhel wa̠ o̠gba bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠b̠om otu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠d̠igh.  
\v 40 Inyin eka̠ ikokod̠ia̠ne ma̠ eb̠a̠ra̠, ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ inyin o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠ na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an.” 
\s1 Ob̠eb̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu na̠ o̠karabh ob̠a̠ra̠motu 
\r (Amatiu 24:45-51) 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, anwa na̠ a̠rogh a̠sidogh onon na̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar ku̠ku̠m ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo?”  
\v 42 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ a̠nyen ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ wa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ aso̠n o̠ro̠ we̠mu̠ okponom rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, onigha̠ gha̠n awa ra̠bin ed̠ia̠n d̠awa ma̠ obhel wa̠ akpe̠ bho̠?  
\v 43 Ta̠ ebhon enigha̠ ma̠ ogoni bho̠, ka̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru sa̠ ta̠ abi̠gh ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ u̠to̠ bho̠.  
\v 44 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton eb̠la̠ i̠d̠i̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ okponom.  
\v 45 Ya̠a̠ ta̠ aro̠ eka̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠fugh d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ ma̠ oru,’ sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ od̠ulogh rob̠a̠ra̠motu iyed̠i, anwani̠ na̠ ilobhiri, sa̠ a̠d̠e ad̠a ka̠ ate̠i̠ esi ola̠ a̠min bho̠ na̠ epuru i̠na?  
\v 46 Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu obha̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ i̠na o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ i̠na ologhom d̠o̠ nyen. Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠gbikimeni i̠na ma̠ egbika̠ ya̠ igurom ipu bho̠, a̠d̠ighom i̠na ma̠ esi wa̠ ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ bho̠.  
\v 47 Ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ a̠loghom abar wa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ i̠na na̠ a̠puru i̠na ma̠ ogir bho̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man okokod̠ia̠n ob̠a̠ra̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ogir agu̠o̠ bho̠ akpe̠ i̠na ma̠ ogir bho̠, ta̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh ibom.  
\v 48 Ya̠a̠, i̠na wa̠ ologhom d̠o̠, sa̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ o̠gu̠r o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh o̠nyi̠ki̠kara ku̠ku̠m. O̠ni̠ ola̠ unigha̠ ma̠ ya̠ ib̠uiy, ta̠ opuru i̠na ma̠ iya̠ ib̠uiy. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ unigha̠ ma̠ ya̠ ib̠uiy ibom, ta̠ opuru i̠na ma̠ iya̠ ib̠uiy ibom. 
\s1 A̠nwunom ta̠ edin A̠zizo̠s e̠bagi̠na 
\r (Amatiu 10:34-36) 
\p  
\v 49 “Ami̠ iru ma̠ ra̠ o̠lo̠gh anya d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon. Ya̠ i̠se̠n anya bho̠ na̠ e̠ke̠ na̠ emumor na̠ ab̠o̠, ka̠ id̠igh ami̠ ma̠ ologi!  
\v 50 Ami̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ owura̠ amu̠m ali̠gam a̠luzu d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ola̠ agu̠o̠ omiza̠n o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ na̠ ane̠mu̠o̠m ami̠ a̠guri tu̠tu̠n ta̠ a̠ten!  
\v 51 Inyin u̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ ami̠ iru ra̠ omutiom ekima̠ d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon d̠u̠ko̠? E̠nyi̠, ami̠ iru ra̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n a̠nwunom.  
\v 52 Ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, eghun otu ogho o̠ni̠ ta̠ abagi̠na; i̠sar ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ agba, sa̠ i̠wal ta̠ ewia̠n awa, bo̠d̠o̠, i̠wal ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ agba, sa̠ i̠sar ta̠ ewia̠n awa.  
\v 53 Awa ta̠ e̠bagi̠na, o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠nyi̠, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠we̠de̠; onweni ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠nyani̠, sa̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n onweni; o̠yo̠go̠-onweni ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠yo̠go̠-o̠nyani̠, sa̠ o̠yo̠go̠-o̠nyani̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠yo̠go̠-onweni.” 
\s1 O̠mu̠gho̠nyan obhel bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 16:2-3) 
\p  
\v 54 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ka̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ na̠ a̠lo na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ agba wa̠ ogogo bho̠ na̠ a̠sor bho̠, onin obhel bho̠ sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘A̠d̠io ta̠ alo̠bh,’ sa̠ na̠ a̠mite ma̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 55 Ya̠a̠, igiel o̠fe̠gu̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ esoroma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ a̠ru, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘A̠d̠io ta̠ asi̠so̠,’ sa̠ na̠ a̠mite ma̠ o̠ku̠a.  
\v 56 Sa̠ ribhelebhel! Inyin na̠ orue na̠ okpon a̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan agu̠o̠ a̠d̠io na̠ a̠bhin na̠ a̠lologia̠n; ya̠a̠, ezin ka̠ ere ma̠ wa̠ inyin orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ emite d̠a̠ obhel onon bho̠? 
\s1 Itulugia̠ne na̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠inyin 
\r (Amatiu 5:25-26) 
\p  
\v 57 “Ya̠a̠, ezin ka̠ ere wa̠ inyin orue ani̠ d̠o̠, ma̠ o̠wal ologho̠m abar wa̠ a̠bhon bho̠?  
\v 58 Igiel anwa na̠ agi̠ ka̠ o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an o̠kpe̠ na̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ler anwa ma̠ iku bho̠, wia̠ne ma̠ a̠tulugia̠n na̠ i̠na d̠a̠ eten, kisa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ esi osobh ase̠ bho̠. Bo̠d̠o̠ bha̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin anwa agi̠o̠m osobh ma̠ ase̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠nu nyam agi̠o̠m o̠ni̠-oloko bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠-oloko bho̠ ta̠ a̠sibh anwa alo̠gh d̠a̠ ikoli.  
\v 59 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, anwa ko orue d̠o̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ikoli bho̠ a̠ten ka̠ anwa na̠ akpe̠ kabar kabar amado̠n, ma̠ ola̠ bebina̠ ape̠ni̠ eka̠ ko osugho d̠o̠.” 
\c 13  
\s1 Itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin,  //  bo̠d̠o̠ inyin ta̠ omugh obhe 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ idi a̠nwunom iru ra̠ i̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, Apai̠let aze̠ ma̠ idi a̠nwunom Agalili d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ awa na̠ e̠ko̠l i̠ko̠l, ma̠ ola̠ asi̠ d̠awa i̠gu̠a na̠ asi̠ i̠nam i̠ko̠l bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, ezin wa̠ a̠nwunom Agalili i̠nye̠n ya̠ i̠mu̠gh o̠ko̠no̠n bho̠, ma̠a̠ awa igir i̠karabh epu ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom Agalili iyed̠i ke̠re̠?  
\v 3 E̠e̠nyi̠! Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠ten ka̠ inyin utiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin, eb̠la̠ inyin eka̠ ta̠ omugh obhe.  
\v 4 Bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠, d̠iobh na̠ o̠bhabhanya o̠ni̠ ya̠ owewegh otu-ipoiny d̠a̠ Asi̠lo̠m a̠mel a̠bhum bho̠, ka̠ awa igir i̠karabh epu ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erugh d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 5 E̠e̠nyi̠! Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ ka̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠ten ka̠ inyin utiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin, eb̠la̠ inyin eka̠ ta̠ omugh obhe.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh a̠fig wa̠ omum d̠o̠ ma̠ itu bho̠ 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh onon: “Odi o̠ni̠ a̠gbebh a̠fig d̠a̠ a̠lei d̠o̠yo̠; sa̠ agi̠gha̠n ka̠ a̠kpon ka̠ i̠na ta̠ abi̠gh itu aku̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ bebina̠ onin otu.  
\v 7 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠kponom a̠lei bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Onon sa̠ i̠sar ala ami̠ na̠ a̠guri gha̠n na̠ a̠ru ma̠ i̠se̠n ra̠ okpon ka̠ ami̠ ta̠ abi̠gh otu d̠a̠ a̠fig onon, ya̠a̠ ami̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ bebina̠ onin otu. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, gue ma̠ oriren bho̠ ma̠ a̠teb̠eli! Ta̠ atu̠n ere aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠robh a̠b̠uruko a̠de bho̠?’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠kponom a̠lei bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ a̠guri ma̠ opa̠n ala, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠gbo ma̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠gir esin oriren bho̠ a̠bhin a̠b̠uruko a̠b̠ologhom.  
\v 9 Ku̠gba ma̠ a̠fig bho̠ a̠mum otu ma̠ ala wa̠ na̠ a̠ru, bha̠ ob̠eb̠i; bo̠d̠o̠ bha̠ gue ma̠ a̠teb̠eli.’ ” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ ani̠ e̠gha-aman  //  ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh 
\p  
\v 10 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh, A̠zizo̠s na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ odi otu u̠gala A̠zu,  
\v 11 ya̠a̠ odi ani̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh alo̠gh e̠gha-aman d̠iobh na̠ o̠bhabhanya ala aro̠. Ani̠ bho̠ akpu̠lan ola̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mara oselegha̠n.  
\v 12 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh ani̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhelegi a̠mutiom a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ani̠ bho̠, na̠ okoko ma̠ anwa od̠umeni d̠a̠ asu̠nwe̠r d̠oyom.”  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agbam aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ozu ani̠ bho̠. D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠nwe amara a̠selegha̠n sa̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\p  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠ ologi ta̠ we̠mu̠ u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, a̠gurom ma̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ a̠likoko d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Odin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esi-a̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠i̠yar ma̠ obhin ogir ogir. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, itue d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠ ma̠ ra̠ ekokua̠n; o̠ni̠ ko oru ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Inyin ibhelebhel! O̠ni̠ inyin ola̠ o̠ko̠to̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ anam d̠o̠yo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠su̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mutiom d̠a̠ otu i̠nam bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ amu̠m, ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠, od̠i ke̠re̠?  
\v 16 O̠ku̠a ka̠, na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ Ebraham onon wa̠ Eru bho̠ abhad̠i̠ a̠guri ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ o̠bhabhanya ala bho̠, ma̠ omiza̠n d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠, ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 17 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠fugh o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ ari̠ghe̠l isibh eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠dama i̠na bho̠; ya̠a̠, o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ebhon ologi d̠a̠ ebula̠ rogir ilologia̠n ya̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠gir bho̠. 
\s1 A̠sidogh ekpo Amu̠stad 
\r (Amatiu 13:31-32; Amaki̠ 4:30-32) 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ od̠i eka̠? Ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ere atu̠o̠m?  
\v 19 Od̠i ka̠ ekpo amu̠stad\f + \fr 13:19 \fq Ekpo Amu̠stad: \ft Ekpo ola̠ aki̠r opa̠n d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l; od̠i ka̠ ekpo obom o̠nyi̠ o̠kai̠ ola̠, ka̠ ugbebh sa̠ na̠ asu̠ na̠ a̠ten oriren.\f* ola̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin a̠gbebh d̠a̠ a̠lei d̠o̠yo̠; sa̠ asu̠ a̠mite a̠ten oriren, sa̠ i̠nu̠r iru ra̠ ilo ma̠ a̠rutu d̠a̠ i̠gha bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh A̠yist bho̠ 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ere atu̠o̠m irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠?  
\v 21 Od̠i ka̠ o̠nyi̠ki̠kara a̠yist ya̠ ani̠ebhom a̠bhin alo̠gh d̠a̠ o̠to̠ma̠ i̠sar-abafu̠ ed̠ia̠n ibhugh sa̠ iwubhmeni ma̠ eb̠la̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.” 
\s1 O̠nu̠-otu wa̠ a̠kporia̠n bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 7:13-14; 7:21-23) 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠l d̠a̠ ibom na̠ i̠gbara re̠ma a̠ten, na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom kesikesi d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ten na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠.  
\v 23 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, o̠nyi̠ki̠kara a̠nwunom ku̠ku̠m ta̠ eten ke̠re̠?” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 24 “Iwia̠ne ma̠ ibom ma̠ o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ o̠nu̠-otu wa̠ a̠kporia̠n bho̠; ezin bho̠, a̠d̠izo ogbo ta̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠wo̠l i̠se̠ od̠igh, ya̠a̠ ko orue d̠o̠.  
\v 25 Ku̠gba ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ adu̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠-otu bho̠, sa̠ inyin uru ra̠ u̠mara d̠a̠ etire u̠kpukpu ma̠ egugh bho̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, gurone ma̠ otu bho̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar.’ 
\p “I̠na ta̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ inyin, esi inyin na̠ o̠d̠u̠a na̠ oru eka̠ ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠.’ 
\p  
\v 26 “Sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠go̠ya ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar od̠igh na̠ anwa od̠e, o̠d̠a; sa̠ anwa i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ reten d̠i̠yar nyen.’ 
\p  
\v 27 “Yaa̠, i̠na ta̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ inyin, na̠ esi inyin na̠ o̠d̠u̠a na̠ oru. Itene ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠n, eb̠la̠ inyin rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.’ 
\p  
\v 28 “A̠nwunom ta̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir, e̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠, ma̠ igiel inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh Ebraham, na̠ Azi̠ki̠, na̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠, na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠riwil d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ya̠a̠ inyin sa̠ ta̠ orobh omutiom d̠a̠ etire.  
\v 29 A̠nwunom ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ agba wa̠ ogogo na̠ a̠pu na̠ a̠mite bho̠, na̠ agba wa̠ ogogo na̠ a̠sor bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ eb̠o na̠ d̠a̠ esoroma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom eru ra̠ ebhin ra̠dila̠de d̠awa, d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠sor d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.  
\v 30 Ya̠ga̠i, ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ idi ogbo ya̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ ta̠ eten i̠pu̠r, sa̠ idi i̠pu̠r bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ u̠man.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠ igbir a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m 
\r (Amatiu 23:37-39) 
\p  
\v 31 D̠a̠ obhel wa̠ i̠na na̠ agba ma̠ o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ idi ogbo Afarisi iru ra̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “D̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠ten agi̠ ma̠ opa̠n esi. E̠ro̠d na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ogigh oyom.” 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ududu\f + \fr 13:32 \fq Ududu: \ft A̠nwunom A̠zu ibhin ma̠ ududu e̠nam ola̠ na̠ a̠koiny ikoiny. \f* obha̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ozegi ozegi i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ okoko okoko a̠nwunom od̠umeni, ma̠ a̠didon na̠ elegien a̠ru; oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠muzoghod̠iom ogir d̠ami̠.’  
\v 33 O̠ku̠a eka̠, ami̠ ta̠ agi̠o̠m d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ma̠ erile d̠ami̠ ma̠ a̠didon, na̠ elegien a̠ru, na̠ a̠melegien. Ezin bho̠, ugigh gha̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ owil opa̠n esi, a̠ten d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m! 
\p  
\v 34 “A̠zeruse̠le̠m, E A̠zeruse̠le̠m, e̠ma wa̠ na̠ a̠guri gha̠n na̠ a̠robhod̠i\f + \fr 13:34 \ft A̠robhod̠i: Obhin ikputu orobhod̠i o̠ni̠ ogigh\f* na̠ aze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠riwil na̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin a̠dila̠de-i̠to̠ a̠ruom oru d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠! Ya̠a̠ i̠ni̠ igiel ma̠ iya̠, na̠ ebhir ami̠ ma̠ okokod̠i eb̠la̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠oyom oguri onin esi, ma̠ agu̠o̠ e̠nu̠r-e̠ma na̠ a̠bhin rapu̠ba d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠ghughuom anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ anwa na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 35 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, nagha ma̠ abar wa̠ ta̠ a̠mite bho̠! Ta̠ ogin otu d̠inyin oguri ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠. Sa̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, inyin ko o̠bi̠gh mu ami̠ tu̠tu̠n ta̠ ate̠i̠ igiel inyin ta̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ i̠na wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.’\x - \xo 13:35 \xt Raso̠r 118:26\x* ” 
\c 14  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠  //  ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ otu odi we̠mu̠ ogbo Afarisi, ka̠ od̠igh na̠ awa od̠e ed̠ia̠n, sa̠ a̠nwunom i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ epoiny  
\v 2 na̠ e̠nagha i̠na! I̠se̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ bha̠ odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ na̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r wa̠nopelbho̠\f + \fr 14:2 \fq Wa̠nopelbho̠: \ft Asu̠nwe̠r wa̠ na̠ opel bho̠; asu̠nwe̠r ola̠ eb̠la̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ a̠wubh\f*.  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ ogbo Afarisi bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Oloko bho̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ okoko o̠ni̠ od̠umeni ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠?”  
\v 4 Ya̠a̠ awa inima̠ i̠ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠sibh o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠b̠eton, sa̠ a̠koko i̠na a̠d̠umeni, sa̠ a̠ruom i̠na ma̠ oten oyel. 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ inyin a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠, bo̠d̠o̠ anam ola̠ a̠mel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ogugua̠-amu̠m ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh, i̠na ko o̠nu̠r d̠o̠ agi̠ ka̠ ato̠ro̠n ke̠re̠?”  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠ awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠wo̠ran a̠pura̠n onon. 
\s1 O̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu na̠ o̠ki̠o̠m i̠ki̠o̠m 
\p  
\v 7 Igiel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ iru d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠so̠n ra̠dila̠de edim na̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ akpata-od̠e bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh onon a̠nigha̠ awa:  
\v 8 “Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠lebh anwa ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ erogh, ko o̠so̠n a̠dila̠de edim aro̠; ka̠din olebh ani̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh e̠mi̠ a̠pu nyam.  
\v 9 Ku̠gba ma̠ oku̠a, sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lebh inyin bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ anwa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘B̠etina̠ d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de d̠oyom ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon.’ Obhel o̠ku̠a, sa̠ ari̠ghe̠l ta̠ esibh anwa, sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠kpon bo̠ agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ aki̠r edim.  
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠lebh anwa, gi̠e̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ esi wa̠ aki̠r edim a̠pu bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ igiel o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lebh anwa bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru, i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, ‘A̠tologha̠n, b̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠bhun ka̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de ola̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ onon.’ Sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠d̠igh edim d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i ya̠ ulebh bho̠.  
\v 11 Ezin bho̠, ogbo ya̠ i̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠, ta̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠; ya̠a̠, ogbo ya̠ i̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠, ta̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠, wa̠ a̠lebh i̠na bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Igiel anwa na̠ a̠soroni ma̠ o̠d̠e̠, a̠d̠igh etita̠n bo̠d̠o̠ a̠dule, ko olebh ra̠tologha̠n d̠oyom, na̠ a̠rumor d̠oyom, bo̠d̠o̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠oyom, na̠ ogbo a̠ghisia̠n, bo̠d̠o̠ aru̠li̠la eghighira̠ d̠oyom. Ka̠ anwa igir o̠ku̠a, awa ta̠ emula̠ elebh ani̠ nyam e̠kpe̠, sa̠ obha̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠oyom.  
\v 13 Yaa̠, igiel anwa na̠ a̠soroni ma̠ o̠d̠e̠, lebhe ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ a̠risisi ozu na̠ e̠kpari̠an bho̠, na̠ a̠rukula̠ bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ a̠rid̠ien na̠ eb̠omia̠n bho̠,  
\v 14 sa̠ anwa ta̠ ate̠i̠ itutumeni. Awa ko orue d̠o̠ e̠kpe̠ nyam emulumeni; ya̠a̠, ta̠ o̠kpe̠ nyam d̠a̠ igiel ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh i̠b̠ab̠alab̠ab̠ala bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh Obom E̠yal bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 22:1-10) 
\p  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ aro̠ ani̠ d̠a̠ akpata-od̠e bho̠ amu̠gho̠n abar onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Itutumeni od̠i na̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ ad̠e̠ ma̠ o̠d̠e̠ d̠a̠ esi irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Odi o̠ni̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n osoroni obom o̠d̠e̠ sa̠ a̠lebh a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom.  
\v 17 Ate̠i̠ obhel o̠d̠e̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gba onigha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na a̠lebh bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Itue, ezin bho̠ na̠ okokod̠i̠an kabarkabar ola̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠ oguri.’ 
\p  
\v 18 “Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ awa sa̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ omutioghom reb̠ologuma̠ ya̠ awa ko orue d̠o̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ bho̠. O̠pu̠r bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠se̠n kisa̠ ami̠ igho ma̠ egbolom, sa̠ a̠bhon ami̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠bi̠gh esi bho̠. Ko o̠gam, ami̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠ru.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “Wa̠leghemeni i̠wal bho̠ sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠se̠n kisa̠ ami̠ igho ma̠ o̠gho̠ etire anam-ogir, ami̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ ad̠a awa a̠kpon. Ko o̠gam, ami̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠ru.’ 
\p  
\v 20 “Wa̠leghemeni i̠sar bho̠ sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠se̠n kisa̠ ami̠ ibhin ani̠, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠ru.’ 
\p  
\v 21 “Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mula̠ agi̠ ka̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ i̠na bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠wo̠ran bho̠. Sa̠ ologi ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ a̠gurom, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ i̠gam bho̠ a̠ruom ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Nu̠re̠ ma̠ a̠ten agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ reten bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ reten-a̠kposi bho̠, ma̠ a̠gun ronyigoiny bho̠, ogbo ya̠ a̠risisi ozu na̠ e̠kpari̠an bho̠, a̠nwunom ya̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠, na̠ a̠rukula̠ bho̠ ma̠ a̠ru.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ anwa iruom ami̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ esi bho̠ ta̠ omuzo d̠o̠.’ 
\p  
\v 23 “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Tene ma̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ibom reten bho̠, na̠ reten d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ eghighira̠ bho̠, ma̠ a̠wia̠n a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ ed̠igh eru, b̠o̠ka̠ otu d̠ami̠ a̠muzo.  
\v 24 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, bebina̠ o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ ulebh bho̠ ko od̠igh d̠o̠ ad̠e̠d̠i̠ma ma̠ o̠d̠e̠ d̠ami̠.’ ” 
\s1 Ibhioma̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 10:37-38) 
\p  
\v 25 I̠se̠n obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom id̠igh na̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ e̠gi̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠,  
\v 26 “Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠ru d̠ami̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ otula̠n d̠o̠ ami̠ a̠pu ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠, a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a ko orue d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠ami̠.  
\v 27 O̠ni̠ ola̠ ko orue d̠o̠ a̠rol e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren d̠o̠yo̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠, ko orue d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠ami̠. 
\p  
\v 28 “Obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ma̠ na̠ ebhir odi o̠ni̠ inyin ma̠ olo owewegh otu-ipoiny, o̠ni̠ bho̠ ko od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de awal a̠b̠ua̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ a̠kpon, ma̠ ologhom ka̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ ikpoki ya̠ ta̠ elei obhin omunieni ogir bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 29 Ezin bho̠, ka̠ anwa i̠ke̠ ma̠ ozu o̠de̠-otu bho̠, sa̠ anwa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ omunieni, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ abi̠gh o̠ku̠a ta̠ aki̠ri̠ nyam,  
\v 30 a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ onon ake̠ ma̠ olo otu, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ omunieni.’ 
\p  
\v 31 “Bo̠d̠o̠, obhin o̠tu̠o̠m o̠li̠la ebhugh ola̠ na̠ agi̠ ka̠ owe e̠gham ma̠ o̠li̠la opa̠n ebhugh. I̠na ko od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de awal a̠kpon ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin o̠lo̠gh e̠gham a̠d̠usubh na̠ ogho o̠ni̠r (10,000) o̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠, adama ma̠ i̠na wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin o̠lo̠gh e̠gham eruba̠l na̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r (20,000) o̠ni̠, na̠ a̠ru ra̠ owe o̠yo̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 32 Ku̠gba ma̠ i̠na ko orue d̠o̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ ato̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠li̠la ebhugh uwed̠i ma̠ obhel ola̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham d̠o̠yo̠ od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ esi egbeiny. Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠puru ma̠ o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an omutiom ekima̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa.  
\v 33 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, o̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠ami̠, a̠ten ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue awe̠le̠man eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠. 
\s1 Ub̠on obhobho i̠kpo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 5:13; Amaki̠ 9:50) 
\p  
\v 34 “Ub̠on ob̠eb̠i abar, ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ub̠on bho̠ na̠ a̠robh a̠lisibh d̠o̠yo̠, ka̠ ub̠on bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠mula̠ ate̠i̠ a̠lisibh d̠o̠yo̠?  
\v 35 Ub̠on ya̠ o̠ku̠a ibhon d̠o̠ ma̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠de, bo̠d̠o̠ oguri d̠a̠ esi ola̠ na̠ okpol a̠b̠uruko nyen; ya̠a̠ ta̠ ozu orobh. 
\p “Wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n, i̠na amu̠gho̠n.” 
\c 15  
\s1 A̠sidogh o̠nana wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠, igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom na̠ ekokod̠ia̠n na̠ ekin A̠zizo̠s ma̠ o̠nagha atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 2 Ya̠a̠ a̠nwunom Afarisi bho̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi bho̠, i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ eghunuma̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ onon na̠ ada ma̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh na̠ a̠bhin, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ awa na̠ a̠d̠ed̠ia̠n.” 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh onon a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠:  
\v 4 “Obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ inyin a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh ro̠nana ya̠ ilei i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100), sa̠ odi o̠nana bho̠ a̠bhe, i̠na ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ d̠iobh na̠ esugho (99) ro̠nana iyed̠i d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠, agi̠ ka̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠nana wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 5 Igiel i̠na abi̠gh o̠nana bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin a̠libhon ologi a̠b̠eton o̠nana bho̠ ale̠ti̠an d̠a̠ o̠kpalu̠ma d̠o̠yo̠ a̠rol a̠bhin a̠yel.  
\v 6 Igiel i̠na na̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ otu, i̠na ta̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ ra̠tologha̠n d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh na̠ etua̠n i̠na bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Id̠ighe na̠ ami̠ ma̠ ebhon ologi, ezin bho̠, ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh o̠nana d̠ami̠ wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠.’  
\v 7 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ibo d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny d̠a̠ ebula̠ onin od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠, ta̠ epu ma̠ ibo d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ d̠iobh na̠ esugho (99) a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠. 
\s1 A̠sidogh okpoki wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ 
\p  
\v 8 “Bo̠d̠o̠, ani̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ d̠iobh adrakma\f + \fr 15:8 \fq Adrakma: \ft Okpoki a̠nwunom A̠rom\f* sa̠ odi a̠bhe. I̠na ko o̠su̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ ato̠di̠, a̠gber otu bho̠, a̠bhin obhel abho̠ro̠ghan tu̠tu̠n i̠na ta̠ abi̠gh ke̠re̠?  
\v 9 Igiel i̠na abi̠gh okpoki bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ ra̠tologha̠n d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh na̠ etua̠n i̠na bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Id̠ighe na̠ ami̠ ma̠ ebhon ologi, ezin bho̠ ami̠ na̠ abi̠gh okpoki d̠ami̠ wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠.’  
\v 10 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ibo od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ka̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh o̠ni̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh obhebhia̠n o̠nyi̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh opa̠n a̠sidogh amar agba a̠mutiom ma̠a̠, “Odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny.  
\v 12 Sa̠ o̠gbara bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa ma̠a̠, ‘O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠, ru̠gi̠ ma̠ ad̠i̠a d̠oyom ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ a̠bin d̠ami̠.’ Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ bho̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ i̠wal awa. 
\p  
\v 13 “Na̠ obia̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ o̠gbara bho̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠bhin a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n ebhugh ola̠ a̠gbeiny, sa̠ a̠rugh ado̠l i̠te̠i̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ eb̠la̠ e̠li̠la d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ iyobh.  
\v 14 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ eb̠la̠ ikpoki d̠o̠yo̠ amado̠n bho̠, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n a̠sor d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ e̠kparama ado̠l ate̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 15 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ odi o̠nyi̠ eghun ebhugh bho̠, ma̠ onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠ ogir. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠ruom i̠na ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ okponom roporopo d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 16 Sa̠, o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na ate̠i̠ esi ola̠, i̠na ra̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ e̠d̠o̠gh od̠e ani̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ roporopo bho̠ na̠ ed̠e bho̠, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na bebina̠ abar od̠e na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\p  
\v 17 “Igiel bho̠ i̠na ra̠ a̠loghoma̠n ozu bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘I̠ni̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ ako̠ ma̠ ogir ogir onigha̠ o̠yo̠, ya̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ed̠e esughieni bho̠? Ya̠a̠ ami̠ od̠i ma̠ enen na̠ a̠mugh o̠ko̠i̠!  
\v 18 Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ten a̠yel ka̠ ate̠i̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: O̠we̠de̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ anwa na̠ ote̠nai̠ny.  
\v 19 Ami̠ i̠kpe̠ mu̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠oyom. Bhine ami̠ ma̠ a̠guri ma̠ agu̠o̠ odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu ola̠ anwa i̠ko̠.’  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p “I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ esi egbeiny sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ abi̠gh ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ru, sa̠ igbirigbir na̠ etula̠n o̠nyi̠ bho̠ isibh i̠na, sa̠ i̠na a̠ghil agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ sa̠ a̠b̠ola̠n i̠na. 
\p  
\v 21 “Sa̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘O̠we̠de̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ anwa na̠ ote̠nai̠ny. Ami̠ i̠kpe̠ mu̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠oyom.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Sa̠, o̠we̠de̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠nu̠re̠! Ibhine ma̠ akapa wa̠ a̠bhon a̠pu bho̠ ma̠ eburi i̠na, ma̠ e̠lo̠gh a̠gulu d̠a̠ ad̠u̠nu̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ e̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ ragbaka.  
\v 23 Ibhine ma̠ e̠nam e̠nu̠m bho̠ ma̠ eru ra̠ egigh, sa̠ ta̠ od̠e ma̠ e̠yal obhon ologi.  
\v 24 Ezin bho̠, o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ onon a̠mugh a̠mugha̠ sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um i̠se̠n; i̠na a̠bhe a̠bha̠ sa̠ na̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠na ma̠ i̠se̠n.’ Sa̠ awa i̠ke̠ ma̠ od̠e e̠yal bho̠. 
\p  
\v 25 “D̠a̠ onin obhel wa̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ emite bho̠, okei o̠nyi̠ bho̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠um na̠ a̠gir ogir. Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mula̠ na̠ a̠yel na̠ a̠tua̠n otu d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n okoroko a̠ma̠ti na̠ aso̠r na̠ i̠gba.  
\v 26 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠pura̠n abar wa̠ na̠ a̠mite bho̠.  
\v 27 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Umor d̠oyom na̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom a̠gigh e̠nam e̠nu̠m bho̠ sa̠ na̠ o̠ghe̠re̠ghu̠o̠m. Ezin bho̠, i̠na na̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um na̠ alu̠kpo̠ a̠luzu.’ 
\p  
\v 28 “Sa̠ ologi ta̠ okei umor bho̠ a̠gurom sa̠ i̠na a̠gin od̠igh d̠a̠ ologi otu. Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠mite agi̠ ka̠ ale̠gh i̠na.  
\v 29 Sa̠, i̠na awo̠ran o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Kpone! Eb̠la̠ rala i̠nye̠n ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwa ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogoni bho̠, a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ i̠pi̠o̠m i̠to̠to̠gi̠ d̠oyom na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. O̠ku̠a eka̠, a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ anwa inigha̠ ami̠ bebina̠ o̠nyi̠ ewel ola̠ obhin od̠igh na̠ ra̠tologha̠n d̠ami̠ od̠e e̠yal na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 30 Ya̠a̠, o̠nyi̠ d̠oyom onon wa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠li̠la d̠oyom iyobh na̠ id̠eme̠ma a̠mula̠ a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ anwa igigh e̠nam e̠nu̠m bho̠ inigha̠ i̠na!’ 
\p  
\v 31 “Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, anwa od̠i na̠ ami̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ igiel. Kabarkabar ola̠ ami̠ inwuna̠, oloyom.  
\v 32 Akpe̠ i̠yar od̠e e̠yal obhon ologi. Ezin bho̠, umor d̠oyom onon a̠mugh a̠mugha̠ sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um, i̠na a̠bhe a̠bha̠ sa̠ na̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠na.’ ” 
\c 16  
\s1 A̠sidogh ikoiny we̠mu̠ ogir bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Odi o̠li̠la aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠guri ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ we̠mu̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ u̠gba unigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠ we̠mu̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠rughom i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ya̠ i̠te̠i̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘I̠gho̠r i̠nye̠n ya̠ ami̠ na̠ amu̠gho̠n na̠ a̠gboloma̠ nyam bho̠, ka̠ imite eka̠? Gba ma̠ a̠mutiom ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ a̠bhin na̠ a̠rileghom ogir d̠ami̠, ezin bho̠, anwa ko orileghom mu ma̠ ogir bho̠.’ 
\p  
\v 3 “Sa̠ we̠mu̠ ogir bho̠ aru̠ru̠an d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n wa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ ogir bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠? Ami̠ i̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠limon\f + \fr 16:3 \fq A̠limon: \ft Ali̠ke̠le̠ke̠l\f* ogbo a̠de, sa̠ ari̠ghe̠l na̠ esibh ami̠ ma̠ opuru ipupuru.  
\v 4 Ami̠ na̠ a̠loghom abar ami̠ ta̠ a̠gir, b̠o̠ka̠ igiel uze ami̠ d̠a̠ ogir bho̠, a̠nwunom e̠da ami̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ a̠rutu d̠awa.’ 
\p  
\v 5 “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠lebh eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ id̠ikighu i̠mu̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ma̠ oru. Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n o̠pu̠r bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠mu̠gh ya̠ anwa id̠igh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠ ka̠ i̠ni̠?’ 
\p  
\v 6 “Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘I̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh a̠tini amu̠nu̠ oliv.’ 
\p “Sa̠ we̠mu̠ ogir bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Bhine ma̠ a̠d̠ire o̠mu̠gh d̠oyom, ma̠ anu̠r aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, ma̠ a̠nwe ma̠ age̠ ma̠ eruba̠l na̠ d̠iobh.’ 
\p  
\v 7 “Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n oleghemeni i̠wal o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa ka̠ o̠mu̠gh d̠oyom ka̠ i̠ni̠?’ 
\p “Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘I̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala re̠kpa i̠bu̠kpa\f + \fr 16:7 \fq I̠bu̠kpa: \ft A̠d̠ien i̠bu̠kpa i̠nye̠n bo̠ d̠a̠ A̠b̠ureni. I̠nye̠n i̠gbara ikpo.\f*.’ 
\p “Sa̠ we̠mu̠ ogir bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Bhine ma̠ a̠d̠ire o̠mu̠gh d̠oyom, ma̠ a̠nwe ma̠ age̠ ma̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r.’ 
\p  
\v 8 “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ogir bho̠ ase̠bh oniniom ma̠ a̠niniom we̠mu̠ ogir bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠koiny ikoiny bho̠. Ezin bho̠, a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom onon na̠ ekoiny na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom amu̠m d̠awa na̠ epu ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny e̠b̠alab̠al na̠ erughom e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠awa bho̠.  
\v 9 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ibhine ma̠ e̠li̠la e̠mara̠nwunom e̠te̠i̠ ra̠tologha̠n iya̠ inyin, b̠o̠ka̠ igiel e̠li̠la d̠inyin na̠ ekun, od̠ighom inyin d̠a̠ a̠rutu esul ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠. 
\p  
\v 10 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rugh ya̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ i̠gbara i̠di̠ar, ta̠ a̠rugh ya̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ ibom i̠di̠ar. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ a̠niniom d̠a̠ i̠gbara i̠di̠ar, ta̠ a̠niniom d̠a̠ ibom i̠di̠ar nyen.  
\v 11 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni, ku̠gba ma̠ inyin ta̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ obhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ orileghom e̠li̠la e̠mara̠nwunom, ka̠ a̠nyen ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠ga̠i e̠li̠la ma̠ okponom?  
\v 12 Sa̠, ku̠gba ma̠ inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ obhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ okponom i̠di̠ar opa̠n o̠ni̠, ka̠ a̠nyen ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin i̠di̠ar iya̠ inyin? 
\p  
\v 13 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu a̠nigha̠ ma̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ i̠na bo̠. O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a ta̠ alo̠gh a̠d̠ien odi sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠tula̠n uwed̠i, bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, sa̠ ta̠ a̠kpon uwed̠i ado̠ti̠me̠ni̠. O̠ni̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ okpoki.” 
\s1 Oloko bho̠ na̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\r (Amatiu 11:12-13; 5:31-32; Amaki̠ 10:11-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Igiel bho̠ Rafarisi ya̠ iba̠ra̠ ma̠ okpoki i̠mu̠gho̠n eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠ki̠ri̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 15 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ oleriom a̠ruzu d̠inyin ma̠ inyin ib̠eb̠i d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom, ya̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠loghom rologi d̠inyin. I̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠nwunom na̠ ebhin na̠ e̠tu̠o̠m abar ibom bho̠, i̠nye̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\p  
\v 16 “Oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi na̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ i̠ge̠ bho̠ e̠ro̠ erileghom i̠to̠to̠gi̠ bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ igiel bho̠ Azo̠n a̠ru bho̠. Ob̠eton obhel obha̠, na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom, sa̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ na̠ alo̠gh e̠mi̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n od̠igh d̠a̠ ologi ma̠ onyen.  
\v 17 A̠b̠ur a̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny o̠mai̠ny o̠d̠u̠a a̠pu, ma̠ ekpo abar ola̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ ma̠ o̠pe̠ti̠na omel obhe. 
\p  
\v 18 “O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gbogina̠ ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin opa̠n ani̠ a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma, sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin ani̠ wa̠ owolom a̠gbogina̠ bho̠ eka̠, a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ Alazaro̠s 
\p  
\v 19 “Odi o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠bhin ib̠eb̠i a̠rukpe ododo na̠ asi̠ni̠ni̠n a̠bura̠ gha̠n ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠duduga̠na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠li̠la ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠.  
\v 20 Odi onyigoiny o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Alazaro̠s eka̠ aro̠, ola̠ re̠b̠e̠ imuzo d̠a̠ ozu bho̠, ola̠ ubhin gha̠n uru d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo o̠li̠la bho̠.  
\v 21 Sa̠ ibhir i̠na ma̠ okpokpo i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ed̠ia̠n ya̠ na̠ emeleghu d̠a̠ akpata-od̠e o̠li̠la bho̠ od̠e. A̠sib̠ogho eka̠ e̠gi̠ ghan ka̠ e̠lai̠ re̠b̠e̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 22 “Ekunuguma̠ bho̠, sa̠ onyigoiny bho̠ a̠mugh, sa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ irileghom i̠na ka̠ id̠ighom d̠a̠ agba ta̠ Ebraham. O̠li̠la bho̠ eka̠ sa̠ a̠mugh, sa̠ ud̠i i̠na,  
\v 23 sa̠ e̠mu̠gh d̠o̠yo̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma imumugh. D̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ibom ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kpon d̠a̠ anyu̠ abi̠gh Ebraham esi egbeiny na̠ Alazaro̠s d̠a̠ aka d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 24 Sa̠ o̠li̠la bho̠ a̠kele ma̠ Ebraham ma̠a̠, ‘E O̠we̠de̠ Ebraham, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir, ma̠ a̠ruom Alazaro̠s ato̠ri̠ ma̠ ad̠u̠nu̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m ra̠ a̠b̠okumeni ma̠ a̠nem d̠ami̠. Ezin bho̠, ami̠ od̠i d̠a̠ obom ali̠gam a̠luzu d̠a̠ ologi e̠banya onon.’ 
\p  
\v 25 “Ya̠a̠ Ebraham awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘O̠nyi̠ ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠oyom d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom, anwa i̠te̠i̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar, ya̠a̠ Alazaro̠s ate̠i̠ i̠karabh sa̠ a̠gbika̠ ma̠ egbika̠. Ya̠a̠ i̠se̠n, i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ e̠no̠gho̠man enen, ya̠a̠ anwa od̠i d̠a̠ ali̠gam a̠luzu na̠ a̠gbika̠.  
\v 26 O̠ku̠a ku̠ku̠m d̠o̠, obom okud̠umkud̠um oghololo od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin na̠ d̠i̠yar, b̠o̠ka̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebhir o̠d̠u̠a d̠inyin o̠b̠e̠i̠y oru d̠i̠yar irue; o̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ ebha̠ d̠inyin ab̠e̠i̠ a̠ru ma̠ enen d̠i̠yar.’ 
\p  
\v 27 “Sa̠ o̠li̠la bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Siseiny O̠we̠de̠ Ebraham, ruome ma̠ Alazaro̠s agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ eghun-otu o̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠,  
\v 28 ezin bho̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ ogho a̠rumor. I̠na agi̠ ka̠ anyagh ra̠to d̠awa, b̠o̠ka̠ awa eka̠ iru d̠a̠ esi onon wa̠ ibom ali̠gam a̠ruzu od̠i bho̠.’ 
\p  
\v 29 “Sa̠ Ebraham awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘A̠mozizi na̠ a̠riwil bho̠ od̠i na̠ awa. Awa e̠nagha ma̠ a̠kikiom d̠awa.’ 
\p  
\v 30 “Sa̠ o̠li̠la bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘E̠nyi̠, E o̠we̠de̠ Ebraham! Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ enen d̠a̠ e̠ma imumugh agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa, awa ta̠ ed̠umom etiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh.’ 
\p  
\v 31 “Sa̠ Ebraham awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Ku̠gba ma̠ awa i̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠mozizi na̠ a̠riwil bho̠, o̠ni̠ a̠b̠etina̠ eka̠ d̠a̠ omugh agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa, awa ko od̠umom d̠o̠.’ ” 
\c 17  
\s1 O̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh 
\r (Amatiu 18:6-7; Amatiu 18:21-22; Amaki̠ 9:42) 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ad̠agi̠an ya̠ ta̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ omel od̠igh d̠a̠ i̠karabh ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ omite; ya̠a̠, itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠nye̠ ta̠ e̠wo̠l emite bho̠.  
\v 2 O̠gho̠ro̠gi̠o̠m obom o̠gbe̠o̠ma d̠a̠ orum o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a orobh o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ abadi̠, ta̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠ od̠ighi ola̠ odi o̠gbara o̠nyi̠\f + \fr 17:2 \fq O̠gbara o̠nyi̠: \ft O̠ni̠ ola̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an bho̠ ta̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar, ka̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠.\f* i̠se̠ ta̠ a̠mel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ i̠karabh.  
\v 3 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin. 
\p “Ku̠gba ma̠ umor d̠oyom, bo̠d̠o̠ u̠marani̠ d̠oyom a̠d̠ighi nyam ma̠ i̠karabh, kikiome̠ i̠na; ka̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠, kpone i̠na ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien.  
\v 4 Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ obha̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam i̠karabh ma̠ od̠ua̠l igiel d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ eka̠, sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠siseiny anwa ma̠ od̠ua̠l igiel sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ na̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠ami̠,’ kpone i̠na ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien.” 
\s1 Ologi ima̠ra̠ 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ ifugh inigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠i̠yar!” 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ I̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ inyin u̠te̠i̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ aki̠r ka̠ ekpo amu̠stad\f + \fr 17:6 \fq Ekpo amu̠stad: \ft Na̠ asu̠ na̠ a̠ten oriren.\f*, inyin ta̠ orue ofugh onigha̠ ma̠ obom oriren onon ma̠a̠, ‘B̠uruna̠ ma̠ ka̠ a̠gbebha̠n d̠a̠ abadi̠,’ sa̠ oriren bho̠ ta̠ anagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠inyin. 
\s1 Ogir ob̠a̠ra̠motu 
\p  
\v 7 “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ inyin ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ola̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ari̠si̠, bo̠d̠o̠ na̠ a̠kponom ro̠nana, sa̠ ka̠ i̠na a̠mutiom a̠ru, wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Dighe ma̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ abar ke̠re̠’?  
\v 8 E̠nyi̠, i̠na ko ofugh d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a. I̠na ta̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘D̠ighi ma̠ ed̠ia̠n a̠dule d̠ami̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠; ma̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n aro̠ ma̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠e ad̠a. Igiel ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠e awe̠le̠ ka̠ ma̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ad̠a ma̠ itoyom’?  
\v 9 Ta̠ a̠sora̠n wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ ma̠ o̠se̠bh o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ rogir ya̠ uruom i̠na ma̠ ogir bho̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 10 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, igiel inyin ugir eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ uruom inyin ogir bho̠, inyin ta̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar ibhobho i̠kpo̠ ib̠a̠ra̠motu; i̠yar ugir i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ i̠yar ogir bho̠ ku̠ku̠m.’ ” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko d̠iobh a̠nwunom  //  ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh 
\p  
\v 11 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠ten na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠, i̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ o̠gbaki̠ Asameria̠ na̠ Agalili.  
\v 12 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n od̠igh d̠a̠ odi o̠gbara e̠ma bho̠, sa̠ d̠iobh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na. Awa i̠mara ma̠ esi ola̠ a̠sigima̠ i̠na,  
\v 13 sa̠ awa ibhin obom okoroko ikele i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s, Wa̠nwuna̠, kpone i̠yar igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 14 Igiel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh awa bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠gi̠e̠, ka̠ eleriom a̠ruzu d̠inyin rokur bho̠.”\x - \xo 17:14 \xt I̠to̠t 14:2-32\x* Sa̠ igiel bho̠ awa iten na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa id̠um i̠b̠ab̠ala. 
\p  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ odi o̠ni̠ awa abi̠gh ma̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠um bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ obom okoroko.  
\v 16 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mel a̠b̠obhia̠n d̠a̠ a̠sike ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ase̠bh i̠na. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ onon ola̠ Asameria̠. 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ukoko d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠iobh a̠nwunom o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ke̠re̠? Ya̠a̠, iken esugho a̠nwunom iyed̠i?  
\v 18 Ka̠ na̠ a̠ten isuloma̠ onon, o̠ni̠ awa ola̠ na̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru ma̠ ra̠ onigha̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ itutumeni bo̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠yel, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠koko nyam a̠d̠umeni.” 
\s1 Eruoma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:23-28; Amatiu 24:37-41) 
\p  
\v 20 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ Rafarisi bho̠ ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠ ologhom igiel irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠ru, sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Eruoma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bo̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ obhin elegh olelegi,  
\v 21 bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n,’ bo̠d̠o̠, ‘Od̠i ma̠ ebha̠,’ ezin bho̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io inyin.” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Obhel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ ebhir inyin o̠bi̠gh odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ inyin ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠.  
\v 23 A̠nwunom ta̠ e̠gba enigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ‘Ikpone, i̠na od̠i ma̠ ebha̠,’ bo̠d̠o̠, ‘Ikpone, i̠na od̠i ma̠ enen,’ ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠tu̠o̠no̠m awa.  
\v 24 A̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ i̠me̠me̠gi̠na agbararan na̠ ame̠me̠gi̠na na̠ a̠mutiom e̠b̠alab̠al d̠a̠ odi e̠ku̠l o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠, sa̠ na̠ ame̠me̠gi̠na na̠ ab̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n e̠ku̠l bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru bho̠.  
\v 25 Ya̠a̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ amar abi̠gh a̠d̠izo ali̠gam a̠ruzu, sa̠ a̠nwunom amu̠m onon ta̠ eghel i̠na. 
\p  
\v 26 “A̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ A̠nua̠ bho̠, onin agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠.  
\v 27 A̠nwunom i̠ro̠ na̠ ed̠e na̠ e̠d̠a, na̠ ebhinogh anwani̠, na̠ enigha̠nom anwi̠nyan d̠awa tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ A̠nua̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ obom oghugh bho̠. Sa̠ obom amu̠m a̠d̠igho a̠ru ra̠ a̠kunugi ma̠ eb̠la̠ awa. 
\p  
\v 28 “Obha̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ Alo̠t nyen. A̠nwunom i̠ro̠ na̠ ed̠e na̠ e̠d̠a, na̠ egho na̠ ewod̠i ma̠ i̠di̠ar, na̠ egbebhegh ed̠ia̠n, na̠ eloyogh a̠rutu,  
\v 29 tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ Alo̠t ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Aso̠do̠m bho̠. Sa̠ anya na̠ aso̠lfo̠\f + \fr 17:29 \fq Aso̠lfo̠: \ft O̠gagaman abar ola̠ od̠i ka̠ i̠ru̠ru̠, ola̠ ka̠ u̠gu̠a d̠a̠ amu̠m, sa̠ na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ozu o̠ni̠ bo̠d̠o̠ ozu abar na̠ api̠e̠, ka̠ ate̠i̠ abar bho̠.\f*, i̠lo̠bh d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny isor ra̠ ikunugi ma̠ eb̠la̠ awa. 
\p  
\v 30 “Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru bho̠.  
\v 31 D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu, osor d̠o̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin abar d̠a̠ ologi otu. Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠sala bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ omula̠ d̠o̠ a̠yel d̠a̠ otu.  
\v 32 I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ ani̠ ta̠ Alo̠t bho̠!  
\v 33 O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠wia̠n otenemeni a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠, ta̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 34 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠d̠uga̠la̠n obha̠, i̠wal a̠nwunom ta̠ ekod̠u d̠a̠ onin akpata; odi ta̠ obhin, uwed̠i sa̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠se̠.  
\v 35 I̠wal anwani̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ onin esi e̠gbe̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar; odi ta̠ obhin, uwed̠i sa̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠se̠.”  
\v 36 [I̠wal a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ egir ogir, odi ta̠ obhin, uwed̠i sa̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠se̠.]\f + \fr 17:36 \ft Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire bho̠ i̠ge̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n. Bhine ma̠ atu̠o̠m ya̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ Amatiu 24:40 bho̠.\f* 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite d̠a̠ken?” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Esi ola̠ omumugh ozu od̠i, bha̠ esi ola̠ ro̠de̠le̠ ta̠ ekokod̠ia̠n.” 
\c 18  
\s1 A̠sidogh ekpukele ani̠ wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ okpukpu okpukpu bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kikiom ma̠a̠, awa e̠ro̠ ma̠ osiseiny osiseiny A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ o̠tabh d̠o̠ awa.  
\v 2 I̠na agba ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ odi e̠ma, odi osobh ma̠ ase̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ oghila̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ atu̠o̠m abar nyen.  
\v 3 Sa̠ odi ekpukele ani̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ o̠yo̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ali̠gam a̠luzu ola̠ ate̠i̠ i̠na, sa̠ ale̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Sobhe ma̠ ase̠ igielake̠ ma̠ a̠tenemeni ami̠, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠.’ 
\p  
\v 4 “I̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir abar ogboloma̠ ani̠ bho̠ ma̠ owewegh obhel; ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ a̠loghom ma̠ ami̠ ighila̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ami̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ atu̠o̠m abar nyen.  
\v 5 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ebula̠ agu̠o̠ ekpukele ani̠ onon na̠ a̠guri na̠ a̠nyegi ami̠ bho̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ bho̠ ma̠ ya̠ igielake̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awe̠le̠man ami̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠!’ ” 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “I̠nagha ma̠ abar wa̠ o̠karabh osobh ma̠ ase̠ onon a̠fugh bho̠.  
\v 7 A̠zib̠a̠ ko osobh d̠o̠ ma̠ ase̠ igielake̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n bho̠, ya̠ na̠ eleghe na̠ enigha̠ i̠na ma̠ etita̠n na̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n bho̠ ke̠re̠? I̠na ta̠ a̠bhogia̠n awa a̠guri ma̠ esi egbeiny ke̠re̠?  
\v 8 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin onyen a̠sobh ase̠ bho̠ ma̠ ya̠ igielake̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. Aro̠ eka̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a, igiel O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, i̠na ta̠ abi̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠de onon ke̠re̠?” 
\s1 A̠sidogh o̠ni̠ Afarisi bho̠  //  na̠ ogun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠ 
\p  
\v 9 A̠zizo̠s ab̠ar na̠ a̠sidogh onon a̠rogh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ id̠umom d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠ awa na̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠, sa̠ na̠ ekpon ipa̠n a̠nwunom na̠ e̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠:  
\v 10 “I̠wal a̠nwunom iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ osiseiny a̠siseiny. Odi, Afarisi; ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ uwed̠i, ogun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh.  
\v 11 Afarisi bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ amara sa̠ a̠siseiny o̠ko̠no̠n: ‘A̠zib̠a̠, anwa a̠d̠ighi ami̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom. Ami̠ bo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ a̠b̠igh, na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, na̠ id̠e ma̠ e̠ma, bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh onon nyen.  
\v 12 Ami̠ na̠ a̠ne ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ i̠wal igiel d̠a̠ ologi od̠ua̠l ra̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ gha̠n A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ odi a̠bin atu̠gi̠-a̠d̠iobh bho̠, d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ bho̠.’ 
\p  
\v 13 “Ya̠a̠, ogun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠ amara ma̠ esi egbeiny. I̠na na̠ one d̠o̠ ma̠ ob̠eka̠ okpon d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny nyen; Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ i̠na a̠bhuma̠ ma̠ ekpa̠kpa̠gh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘E A̠zib̠a̠! Kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir, ezin bho̠ ami̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.’ 
\p  
\v 14 “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ada ma̠ a̠siseiny od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh onon a̠bhin, sa̠ i̠na a̠yel agu̠o̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠, ya̠a̠ Afarisi bho̠ d̠o̠. Ezin bho̠, eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠ ta̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠; sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠awa bho̠ sa̠ ta̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠tutumeni ma̠ i̠gbara-anwi̠i̠ny 
\r (Amatiu 19:13-15; Amaki̠ 10:13-16) 
\p  
\v 15 A̠nwunom i̠b̠aram na̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny ebhin eru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s, ma̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠gbam agu̠o̠ otutumeni. Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠bi̠gh oku̠a bho̠, sa̠ ikigima̠ awa.  
\v 16 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhelegi ma̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ima̠ra̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ eru d̠ami̠. O̠ni̠ ko okigima̠ awa, ezin bho̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n.  
\v 17 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠da d̠o̠ ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhin ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠, ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ologi.” 
\s1 O̠li̠la Bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 19:16-30; Amaki̠ 10:17-31) 
\p  
\v 18 Odi o̠li̠la ebhugh A̠zu a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠-atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠?” 
\p  
\v 19 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ere a̠d̠ighi ka̠ anwa na̠ a̠bhelegi ami̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠? Ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ bo̠, usigimeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m.  
\v 20 Anwa a̠loghom oloko wa̠ agba ma̠a̠: ‘Anwa ko od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma. Anwa ko ogigh d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠. Anwa ko ob̠igh d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠b̠igh. Anwa ko o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠. Zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ d̠oyom.’\x - \xo 18:20 \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:12-16\x* ” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Eb̠la̠ roloko i̠nye̠n ami̠ na̠ a̠koko ka̠ d̠a̠ i̠gbara d̠ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 22 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Odi abar od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ anwa ma̠ ogir. Wole ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa inwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ ma̠ inyigoiny bho̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ ate̠i̠ e̠li̠la d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny. Igiel anwa na̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a awe̠le̠, ma̠ a̠mula̠ ma̠ a̠ru ra̠ ato̠no̠m ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 23 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n e̠kal onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na aku̠ru̠ru̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠gbo ma̠ e̠li̠la ma̠ ibom.  
\v 24 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠bhin aku̠ru̠ru̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Amar akpar ogbo ya̠ igbo ma̠ e̠li̠la ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ ologi irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!  
\v 25 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, e̠nam-a̠dol o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ oyol anu̠ga oten ta̠ a̠b̠ur a̠pu, ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gbo ma̠ e̠li̠la ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ ologi irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”\fig E̠nam-a̠dol|alt="Carmel" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 18:25" copy="HK00038" ref="18:25" \fig* 
\p  
\v 26 A̠nwunom ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠ sa̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ a̠nyen ta̠ a̠rue a̠ten?” 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Abar ola̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ na̠ orue a̠gir, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir.” 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar na̠ o̠we̠le̠man eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar unwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m anwa.” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ awe̠le̠man otu, bo̠d̠o̠ ani̠, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠rumor, bo̠d̠o̠ aru̠marani̠, bo̠d̠o̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠, bo̠d̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny, ma̠ ebula̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 30 o̠ni̠ bho̠ ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ipel o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ amu̠m onon, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ bho̠.” 
\s1 Oleghemeni i̠sar igiel  //  A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠  //  omugh na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 20:17-19; Amaki̠ 10:32-34) 
\p  
\v 31 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ a̠d̠ukun, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠nagha, i̠yar ta̠ obhun o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, esi bho̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom eb̠la̠ iwowa̠ ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ i̠ge̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 32 Ta̠ ob̠eton i̠na o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠. A̠nwunom ta̠ e̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na, sa̠ awa ta̠ erogi i̠na ekpon e̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠si̠ro̠gho̠m i̠na ma̠ i̠gho̠r.  
\v 33 Awa ta̠ e̠gu̠ro̠gh i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ egigh i̠na. Sa̠ oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.” 
\p  
\v 34 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ bebina̠ abar d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ya̠ i̠na agba bho̠. U̠wo̠gi̠o̠m awa ma̠ ezin i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na agba bho̠, sa̠ awa ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na na̠ agba na̠ a̠gboloma̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ opuru ma̠ ipupuru o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien 
\r (Amatiu 20:29-34; Amaki̠ 10:46-52) 
\p  
\v 35 I̠se̠n a̠mite ma̠ ola̠, agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠tua̠n Aze̠riko bho̠, bha̠ odi o̠ni̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka eten bho̠ na̠ a̠puru ma̠ ipupuru.  
\v 36 Igiel bho̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n oghoroghor o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ eten bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n ologhom abar wa̠ na̠ a̠mite bho̠.  
\v 37 Sa̠ awa i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t bho̠ na̠ a̠ten.” 
\p  
\v 38 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mulughu a̠kele ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s, o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠, imulughuom i̠na ma̠ i̠na aro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m. Ya̠a̠, i̠na aro̠ ma̠ omulughu omulughu izul d̠o̠yo̠ o̠gi̠o̠m anyu̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 40 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s amara kpom, sa̠ a̠bhin okparakpar okoroko a̠ruom agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ obhin o̠ni̠ bho̠ oru d̠o̠yo̠. Igiel bho̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠,  
\v 41 “Ere ma̠ abar wa̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ami̠ ma̠ ogir onigha̠ oyom bho̠?” Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠. 
\p “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠bi̠gh abar\f + \fr 18:41 \fq O̠bi̠gh abar: \ft O̠bi̠gh esi; a̠rid̠ien bho̠ ma̠ o̠kpakpagi̠na\f*.” 
\p  
\v 42 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠rid̠ien d̠oyom e̠kpagi̠na! Ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠koko nyam a̠d̠umeni.”  
\v 43 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh abar, sa̠ atu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s, na̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠bi̠gh o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ awa itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\c 19  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ Azaki̠o̠s 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ Aze̠riko sa̠ awo̠l na̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠.  
\v 2 Odi o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Azaki̠o̠s aro̠. I̠na we̠mu̠ igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠.\f + \fr 19:2 \fq Otua̠-ebhugh: \ft Otua̠ oloko, ola̠ a̠nwunom na̠ e̠kpe̠ na̠ e̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠kpa ebhugh\f* 
\v 3 I̠na a̠wia̠n o̠bi̠gh ani̠ A̠zizo̠s, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠lukper d̠o̠yo̠ i̠na na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ okpon opeleni o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠yo̠.  
\v 4 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠ghil a̠ten o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, sa̠ asi̠n oriren ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ a̠sikamo̠; b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na a̠rue abi̠gh i̠na, ezin bho̠ A̠zizo̠s ta̠ awo̠l i̠se̠ a̠ten. 
\p  
\v 5 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s ate̠i̠ esi bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ anyu̠ a̠bhelegi i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Azaki̠o̠s! Nu̠re̠ ma̠ a̠sor a̠ru; ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh aro̠ d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom a̠didon.”  
\v 6 Onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na anu̠r a̠sor agi̠ ka̠ ada i̠na a̠bhin na̠ a̠libhon ologi. 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠bi̠gh o̠ku̠a bho̠, i̠ke̠ ma̠ oghunuma̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠suloma̠ ma̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.” 
\p  
\v 8 Sa̠ Azaki̠o̠s a̠b̠etina̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Kpone, E Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ ta̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ e̠li̠la d̠ami̠ i̠wal a̠bin a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi a̠bin ronyigoiny bho̠; ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ami̠ ininiom abar, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ akpe̠\f + \fr 19:8 \fq Ami̠ ta̠ akpe̠: \ft Oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi, d̠a̠ E̠d̠u̠a 22:1-9, u̠to̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ omulumeni abar a̠niniom, bo̠d̠o̠ abar a̠b̠igh, bo̠d̠o̠ abar ola̠ o̠ni̠ ale̠ge̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ a̠bhin na̠ ikoiny.\f* ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠ inya̠ a̠bin abar i̠se̠.” 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠didon, itenemeni na̠ eru d̠a̠ otu onon, ezin bho̠, o̠ni̠ onon eka̠ o̠nyi̠ ola̠ Ebraham\f + \fr 19:9 \fq O̠nyi̠ ola̠ Ebraham: \ft Azaki̠o̠s a̠d̠umom A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ Ebraham o̠we̠de̠ od̠ud̠ul d̠o̠yo̠ a̠d̠umom A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠. Itenemeni bho̠ i̠gbo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ e̠te̠i̠ Azaki̠o̠s na̠ eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠.\f*.  
\v 10 Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ atu̠n o̠bho̠ro̠gh, na̠ otenemeni ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebhe bho̠ a̠ru.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh a̠d̠iobh rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 25:14-30) 
\p  
\v 11 Agu̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ e̠nagha ma̠ iya̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agba bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh ab̠aram. Ezin bho̠, awa na̠ e̠walama ma̠a̠, agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠ ma̠a̠, irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ omite i̠se̠ onin obhel obha̠.  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, “Odi obom o̠ni̠ ola̠ amar agbi̠r a̠mitia̠n, a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ esi egbeiny d̠a̠ opa̠n ebhugh, ola̠ ta̠ o̠lo̠gh i̠na ma̠ O̠li̠le̠ma sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru.  
\v 13 Kisa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ d̠iobh rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ami̠na, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ibhine ma̠ ikpoki i̠nye̠n ma̠ eb̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n ami̠ na̠ agi̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠.’ 
\p  
\v 14 “Ya̠a̠, a̠nwunom ebhugh d̠o̠yo̠ e̠su̠a i̠na, sa̠ awa i̠to̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom obha̠ra̠nom o̠yo̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠go̠ya d̠a̠ esi bho̠ i̠na na̠ agi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar u̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon o̠ro̠ o̠li̠le̠ma d̠i̠yar.’ 
\p  
\v 15 “A̠mite ma̠ ola̠ u̠lo̠gh i̠na ma̠ o̠li̠la ebhugh d̠awa, sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠yel. Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom obhelegi rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ikpoki bho̠, ma̠ opura̠n ologhom asu̠o̠ ya̠ awa igir imutiom bho̠. 
\p  
\v 16 “O̠pu̠r bho̠ a̠ru sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, okpoki d̠oyom amar ipa̠n a̠d̠iobh ami̠na a̠mutiom.’ 
\p  
\v 17 “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa amar a̠gir. Anwa ob̠eb̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu! Ebula̠ agu̠o̠ anwa ileriom ma̠a̠, ta̠ orue obhin anwa ob̠em ologi d̠a̠ o̠nyo̠gbara abar bho̠, anwa ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ola̠ orileghom a̠d̠iobh ibom re̠ma.’ 
\p  
\v 18 “O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ sa̠ oleghemeni i̠wal ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, okpoki d̠oyom amar ipa̠n ogho ami̠na a̠mutiom.’ 
\p  
\v 19 “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ola̠ orileghom ogho ibom re̠ma.’ 
\p  
\v 20 “O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ sa̠ oleghemeni i̠sar ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, onon okpoki d̠oyom; ami̠ i̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ukpe a̠guri a̠sisa̠n anwa.  
\v 21 Ami̠ ighil anwa, ezin bho̠ anwa o̠kparakpar o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin abar o̠la o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ oloyom, sa̠ anwa na̠ a̠b̠u ma̠ esi ola̠ anwa ogbebh d̠o̠.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa o̠karabh ob̠a̠ra̠motu onon, Ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin okoroko d̠oyom a̠sobh ase̠ a̠bhumeni nyam. Anwa amar a̠loghom ma̠a̠, ami̠ o̠kparakpar o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin abar ola̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ olami̠, sa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠u ma̠ esi ola̠ ami̠ ogbebh d̠o̠.  
\v 23 O̠ku̠a ka̠ a̠mite eka̠, ma̠ ola̠ anwa oguri d̠o̠ ma̠ okpoki d̠ami̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ ta̠ amar ipa̠n a̠mutiom, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠se̠n ami̠ imula̠ iru bho̠ ami̠ ate̠i̠ okpoki d̠ami̠ na̠ asu̠o̠ bho̠?’ 
\p  
\v 24 “Sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ibhine ma̠ okpoki wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ d̠iobh ami̠na bho̠.’ 
\p  
\v 25 “Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, o̠ni̠ obha̠ na̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ d̠iobh ami̠na d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠.’ 
\p  
\v 26 “Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Yii, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ ate̠i̠ bho̠, ta̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m ipa̠n ya̠ ib̠uiy ipu ma̠ o̠ku̠a onigha̠ i̠na; ya̠a̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, bebina̠ o̠nyi̠ki̠kara ya̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ bho̠ eka̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r obhin.  
\v 27 Ya̠a̠, ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ i̠nye̠n ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ka̠ ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ oli̠le̠ma d̠awa bho̠, ibhine awa ma̠ eru ma̠ i̠se̠n ma̠ e̠ze̠gi̠ awa d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠ami̠.’ ” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ka̠ O̠li̠le̠ma 
\r (Amatiu 21:1-11; Amaki̠ 11:1-11; Azo̠n 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agba ma̠ i̠nye̠n awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ten d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠awa a̠rile adama ma̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m.  
\v 29 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n e̠ma Abe̠ti̠fagi̠ na̠ e̠ma Abe̠tani̠ bho̠, ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ igu Oliv bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom a̠duom i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠,  
\v 30 “Itene ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠inyin bho̠, sa̠ ka̠ inyin ud̠igh a̠d̠igha̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh okubh ado̠ki̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ a̠d̠igh a̠rile.  
\v 31 Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠pura̠n inyin ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin na̠ o̠tu̠n ere na̠ o̠ko̠to̠n okubh ado̠ki̠ bho̠?’ I̠wo̠rane̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh orughom.’ ” 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ya̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom a̠duom bho̠ iten i̠gi̠, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠.  
\v 33 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠ko̠to̠n okubh ado̠ki̠ bho̠, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ bho̠ ipura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ o̠tu̠n ere na̠ o̠ko̠to̠n okubh ado̠ki̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh orughom.” 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ awa ibhin ado̠ki̠ bho̠ iruom A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ awa i̠ke̠gi̠na ma̠ ibom rakapa\f + \fr 19:35 \fq Ibom rakapa: \ft Ilobhiri a̠nwunom Izre̠l na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠an ibom rakapa ya̠ awa na̠ ebhin na̠ ezuom ipa̠n d̠a̠ ekpukpu.\f* d̠awa ibhin i̠de̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠ri̠lo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠.  
\v 36 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rile na̠ agi̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom i̠ke̠gi̠na ma̠ ibom rakapa d̠awa ibhin i̠de̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠d̠ia̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 37 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n esi bho̠ eten bho̠ ake̠ ma̠ okubh d̠a̠ igu Oliv osor bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠, ibhin d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi i̠ke̠ ma̠ o̠mo̠r aso̠r otutumeni A̠zib̠a̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogir ilologia̠n ya̠ awa na̠ e̠bi̠gh bho̠, ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 38 “Itutumeni ta̠ A̠zib̠a e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ O̠li̠le̠ma wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠!” 
\q1 “Ekima̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny na̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠pu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 39 Idi ogbo Afarisi ya̠ i̠ro̠ ani̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ sa̠ ifugh inigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ghi̠ghana ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom ma̠ ofugh i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a!” 
\p  
\v 40 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ka̠ awa inima̠ i̠ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m, ikpokpogh i̠gbaki̠ghe̠ bho̠ ta̠ ekpogion izul emulughu etutumeni ami̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠leghe ma̠ ekulom A̠zeruse̠le̠m 
\p  
\v 41 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tua̠n abi̠gh e̠ma bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠leghe ma̠ ekulom e̠ma bho̠  
\v 42 a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “A̠didon ma̠ inyin na̠ ologhom i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emutiom ekima̠ enigha̠ inyin bho̠ nab̠o̠! Ya̠a̠, na̠ o̠wo̠gi̠o̠m inyin amu̠gho̠nyan i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠.  
\v 43 Ya̠ a̠ga̠i, ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ eru d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ma̠ iya̠, ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom ta̠ elo ma̠ e̠b̠agh ekitineni ma̠ anwa, e̠du̠o̠m a̠nwunom d̠oyom eguri awa d̠a̠ ologi d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ragba bho̠.  
\v 44 Awa ta̠ e̠kpi̠ghi̠d̠i̠ nyam d̠a̠ a̠de, erobhom anwa na̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠oyom d̠a̠ re̠b̠agh d̠oyom e̠ze̠gi̠ inyin. Ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom ko oguri d̠o̠ bebina̠ ekpo o̠gbaki̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ ta̠ odi, ezin bho̠ anwa na̠ olelegi d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠zua̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ada i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ obhel bho̠ i̠na a̠ru d̠oyom bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ otu-a̠siseiny bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 21:12-17; Amaki̠ 11:15-19; Azo̠n 2:3-22) 
\p  
\v 45 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ozegi ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ eb̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠ bho̠.  
\v 46 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Otu d̠ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ otu-a̠siseiny,’ ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ obhin otenemeni ma̠ ‘e̠fe̠m i̠bi̠gh ma̠ a̠b̠igh.’ ”\fig A̠zizo̠s a̠kogion rakpata inwegi ma̠ ikpoki|alt="Jesus overturning tables of money changers" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 19:46" copy="LB000316" ref="19:46" \fig* 
\p  
\v 47 Ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ sa̠ i̠na aro̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ghan atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. Ya̠a̠, ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ ikei bho̠, sa̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ omimia̠n agu̠o̠ obhin ogigh o̠yo̠.  
\v 48 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh abar ola̠ odin ogigh o̠yo̠, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠, na̠ ebhin obhel na̠ e̠nagha ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠da na̠ ebhin. 
\c 20  
\s1 Ipura̠n esi a̠limon ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a a̠ru 
\r (Amatiu 21:23-27; Amaki̠ 11:27-33) 
\p  
\v 1 Odi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ ikei bho̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 2 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, anwa na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠limon ta̠ a̠nyen na̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n? A̠nyen a̠nigha̠ nyam a̠limon bho̠?”  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠pura̠n ani̠ inyin odi a̠pura̠n:  
\v 4 Owur amu̠m ta̠ Azo̠n ka̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ a̠ru?”  
\v 5 Sa̠ awa ibhin i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ i̠yar o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin udin ere na̠ o̠we̠le̠man od̠umom o̠yo̠?’  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, ka̠ i̠yar u̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ a̠ru,’ sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ erobhod̠i i̠yar egigh; ezin bho̠, a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠ Azo̠n owil.” 
\p  
\v 7 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ owur amu̠m ta̠ Azo̠n a̠bhin a̠mite.”  
\v 8 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ eka̠, ami̠ ko o̠gba d̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ a̠limon obhin ogir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠sidogh ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei irughom bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 21:33-46; Amaki̠ 12:1-12) 
\pi1  
\v 9 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei a̠grep\f + \fr 20:9 \fq A̠grep: \ft Otu oriren onon agu̠b̠an otu ololo ya̠ na̠ o̠b̠am d̠o̠ a̠ka̠ka̠ka̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ololo; oriren bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠ bo̠ d̠a̠ A̠b̠ureni.\f*, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ esi bho̠ ma̠ igbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n o̠ko̠ orughom, sa̠ a̠b̠etina̠ agi̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n ebhugh aro̠ ma̠ owewegh obhel.  
\v 10 Ate̠i̠ obhel o̠ku̠ imuma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ awa, obhin a̠bin imuma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ awa i̠ku̠ d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠. Ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ id̠ul i̠na, sa̠ imulumeni i̠na ma̠ i̠kpo̠.  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom opa̠n ob̠a̠ra̠motu. Obha̠ eka̠ sa̠ awa id̠ul, ikpon i̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ imulumeni ma̠ i̠kpo̠.  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom epa̠ ma̠ oleghemeni i̠sar ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠; onon eka̠ sa̠ awa id̠ul i̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠ne̠m, ize imutiom. 
\p  
\v 13 “Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ aru̠ru̠an opa̠n agu̠o̠ ogir, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠? Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ ami̠ itula̠n ibom bho̠; ka̠din awa ta̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ i̠na.’ 
\p  
\v 14 “Igiel bho̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erughom a̠lei bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ awa ima̠ra̠nua̠n ma̠a̠, ‘Onon ta̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a a̠lei bho̠, id̠ighi ogigh i̠na b̠o̠ka̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar o̠ni̠ bho̠ eten iyiyar.’  
\v 15 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ awa inu i̠na imutiom d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ igigh i̠na.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠, wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ta̠ a̠gir ere a̠gboloma̠ awa?  
\v 16 I̠na ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ aze̠gi̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ igbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ esi bho̠ i̠ro̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠eton a̠lei bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo.” 
\p Igiel bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa ifugh ma̠a̠, “A̠zib̠a̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ e̠tu̠tu̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ omite!” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kpon awa d̠a̠ a̠misigh sa̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Abar wa̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire-E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘Ikputu wa̠ ilo ma̠ a̠rutu bho̠ ighel bho̠ na̠ a̠ten e̠ko̠ otu bho̠,’\x - \xo 20:17\xt Raso̠r 118:22\x* ka̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ ere? 
\m  
\v 18 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠melema̠ ma̠ ikputu bho̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ob̠omia̠n; sa̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ ikputu bho̠ a̠mel a̠bhum eka̠ ta̠ a̠tutughud̠ia̠n.” 
\p  
\v 19 Ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ sa̠ i̠bho̠ro̠gh e̠ti̠ti̠gha o̠wo̠l ob̠ol o̠yo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ d̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa iloghoma̠n ma̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh bho̠ a̠gboloma̠ awa. Ya̠a̠, awa ighil a̠nwunom bho̠. 
\s1 Ipura̠n otua̠ ebhugh 
\r (Amatiu 22:15-22; Amaki̠ 12:13-17) 
\p  
\v 20 Awa i̠ro̠ igon o̠bi̠gh e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ ob̠ol A̠zizo̠s, obhin o̠gi̠o̠m ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ na̠ a̠limon d̠a̠ ebhugh bho̠. Sa̠ awa iruom ogbo ipoiny ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠ro̠ agu̠o̠ a̠ga̠i a̠nwunom, o̠nagha abar i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh a̠rima̠.  
\v 21 Sa̠ ogbo ipoiny bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar ologhom ma̠ anwa na̠ amar na̠ a̠gir d̠a̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠oyom, sa̠ anwa na̠ okpon d̠o̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠gurumeni, abhe̠l opa̠n, sa̠ anwa na̠ a̠bhin iya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar eten ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 22 A̠bhon otua̠ otua̠-ebhugh onigha̠ A̠siza̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ na̠ obhon d̠o̠?”  
\v 23 Ya̠a̠, i̠na abi̠gho̠m ipesi d̠awa sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 24 “Ileriome ami̠ ma̠ adi̠nari̠. U̠le̠m a̠misigh ta̠ a̠nyen, sa̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ a̠nyen d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠?” Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “A̠misigh ta̠ A̠siza̠.”  
\v 25 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a bha̠, imulumeni ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠siza̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ A̠siza̠, ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ita̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”  
\v 26 Awa i̠kpati̠ i̠na ma̠ osor, ya̠a̠ awo̠ran d̠o̠yo̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ awa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ osibh o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom bho̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ awo̠ran d̠o̠yo̠ a̠d̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n o̠mu̠gho̠n, sa̠ awa inima̠ i̠ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m. 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh na̠ ilom 
\r (Amatiu 22:13-33; Amaki̠ 12:18-27) 
\p  
\v 27 Idi Rasadusi, ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh odi bho̠, i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s epura̠n ma̠a̠,  
\v 28 “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, A̠mozizi age̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ umor o̠ni̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ad̠u̠a, ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠, ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ani̠ umor bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ ate̠i̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 29 I̠se̠n bha̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor e̠ro̠; sa̠ o̠pu̠r bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ sa̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ani̠ bho̠ ad̠u̠a.  
\v 30 Sa̠ oleghemeni i̠wal umor bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ bho̠, i̠na eka̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ sa̠ a̠mugh.  
\v 31 Sa̠ oleghemeni i̠sar umor bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ bho̠. O̠ku̠a oku̠a tu̠tu̠n eb̠la̠ a̠rumor bho̠ ibhin ani̠ bho̠ sa̠ imugughu, i̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny eguri.  
\v 32 Ekunuguma̠ bho̠ sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠mugh nyen.  
\v 33 Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, igiel ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ ka̠, ani̠ bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ani̠ ta̠ a̠nyen, d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ ani̠ bho̠ na̠ awal eb̠la̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “A̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ amu̠m onon bho̠ ta̠ ebhinogh anwani̠, sa̠ ta̠ onigha̠nom anwi̠nyan anwi̠i̠ny bho̠.  
\v 35 Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ada a̠bhin, ma̠ awa e̠kpe̠ ma̠ ob̠egina̠ d̠a̠ omugh od̠igh d̠a̠ amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠, ilom bo̠;  
\v 36 awa ko omugh mu, ezin bho̠ awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ka̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. Awa anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ezin bho̠ awa anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ na̠ eb̠egina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠.  
\v 37 Ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠, A̠mozizi eka̠ agba a̠mutiom d̠a̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠, wa̠ ed̠um bho̠ a̠mumor ya̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠ bho̠. A̠mozizi a̠bhelegi ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Ebraham, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Azi̠ki̠, na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠.’  
\v 38 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠na A̠zib̠a̠ imumugh d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na ola̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um; ezin bho̠, d̠o̠yo̠ eb̠la̠ awa od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.” 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ idi ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, anwa amar agba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠.”  
\v 40 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ne ma̠ o̠kpato̠n o̠nu̠ opura̠n abar na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\s1 A̠pura̠n wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Wa̠ uzuom amu̠nu̠ udoni bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 22:41-46; Amaki̠ 12:35-37) 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere wa̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠, Akrai̠st wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aso̠n a̠doni bho̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi bho̠?  
\v 42 Ezin bho̠, A̠devidi na̠ agu̠o̠ agba a̠mutiom d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire Raso̠r bho̠ ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “ ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q2 “Ri̠la d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠, 
\q1  
\v 43 tu̠tu̠n ami̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom ma̠ 
\q2 okpokpolom ola̠ o̠gbam a̠sike d̠oyom.” ’\x - \xo 20:43 \xt Raso̠r 110:1\x* 
\m  
\v 44 A̠devidi a̠bhelegi gha̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠.’ O̠ku̠a ka̠ i̠na a̠ten eka̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠?” 
\s1 I̠kparakpar a̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Ogbo Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ Oloko bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 23:1-36; Amaki̠ 12:38-40) 
\p  
\v 45 Igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ e̠nagha i̠na bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠,  
\v 46 “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠. Awa iba̠ra̠ ma̠ opa̠n obura̠ ibom rakapa isosor, sa̠ iba̠ra̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin d̠a̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi ebheleguma̠ awa d̠a̠ regbolom a̠b̠ua̠, sekina̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ra̠dila̠de edim d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala A̠zu, na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ rakpata o̠d̠e̠ ya̠ edim.  
\v 47 Awa na̠ eponoma̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠ na̠ e̠wo̠ro̠gh i̠di̠ar, sa̠ awa na̠ esiseiny iwewegh a̠siseiny b̠o̠ka̠ olelegi awa. Ta̠ o̠gu̠r awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠zagba ola̠ abu̠gh ibom.” 
\c 21  
\s1 Okpoki wa̠ ekpukele ani̠ bho̠ a̠bhin ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:41-44) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ aru̠li̠la bho̠ na̠ ebhin na̠ e̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ ikpoki ali̠se̠bh d̠awa d̠a̠ igba̠ o̠da ikpoki bho̠.  
\v 2 I̠na abi̠gh nyen ka̠ odi onyigoiny ekpukele ani̠\f + \fr 21:2 \fq Ekpukele ani̠: \ft Ani̠ ola̠ owolom na̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ad̠u̠a\f*, agi̠ ka̠ alo̠gh i̠wal i̠gbara ikpoki ako̠pa\f + \fr 21:2 \fq Ako̠pa: \ft Abar ola̠ akpar ka̠ okurogh, ola̠ a̠nwunom obhel bho̠, ibhin gha̠n i̠le̠m ikpoki na̠ ipa̠n i̠di̠ar o̠le̠m\f* d̠a̠ ologi igba̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mutiom okoroko ma̠a̠: “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ igba̠ bho̠, onyigoiny ekpukele ani̠ onon alo̠gh a̠pu.  
\v 4 Ezin bho̠, eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n na̠ ibom e̠li̠la d̠awa, wa̠ a̠ru, ape̠to̠n o̠nyi̠ esi d̠a̠ e̠li̠la d̠o̠yo̠ alo̠gh. Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ologi igoiny d̠o̠yo̠, i̠na a̠kpukpu ma̠ eb̠la̠ ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠ alo̠gh.” 
\s1 Ib̠ogion otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠  //  na̠ relegh ekunuguma̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 24:1-35; Amaki̠ 13:1-31) 
\p  
\v 5 Idi ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠libhon Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, d̠a̠ e̠mi̠ agu̠o̠ ubhin ib̠eb̠i i̠gbaki̠ghe̠, na̠ i̠d̠i̠ar e̠ne̠ghe̠ ya̠ ub̠eton u̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ uburi ma̠ otu bho̠. Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠a̠,  
\v 6 “I̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠se̠n bho̠, obhel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ bebina̠ ekpo o̠gbaki̠ghe̠ ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ ta̠ odi; ta̠ ob̠ogion eb̠la̠yi osoroni.”  
\v 7 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ka̠ ta̠ emite ma̠ a̠kere igiel? Sa̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin a̠kere a̠d̠ien elegh eloghom ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ etua̠n omite?”  
\v 8 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ b̠o̠ka̠ ugelemeni inyin; ezin bho̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ eru, sa̠ awa ta̠ ekue inyin e̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ Witenemeni bho̠, obhel bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n!’ Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ko od̠umom e̠tu̠o̠no̠m awa.  
\v 9 Igiel inyin umugho̠n i̠mu̠mu̠gho̠n e̠gham na̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere a̠d̠ugh e̠mu̠, o̠ni̠ ko okpa̠ra̠noma̠. Ezin bho̠, i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ ed̠ia̠ emite; ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ekunuguma̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ onin obhel bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ebhugh ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠wia̠n ebhugh, sa̠ a̠de e̠ma ta̠ a̠wia̠n a̠de e̠ma.  
\v 11 Sa̠ a̠d̠izo ibom ib̠ob̠omia̠n a̠de ta̠ emite, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n na̠ i̠karabh asu̠nwe̠r ta̠ esor a̠d̠izo a̠risisi; sa̠ ra̠d̠ugh ibom a̠rugugu na̠ ibom ilologia̠n ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny emite. 
\p  
\v 12 “Ya̠a̠, kisa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite, ta̠ ogbikimeni inyin ibom. Ta̠ ob̠ologh inyin, sa̠ ta̠ obhin inyin ka̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ ru̠gala A̠zu na̠ a̠rutu ikoli, sa̠ ta̠ obhin inyin ka̠ o̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh aru̠li̠le̠ma na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rebhugh, d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠.  
\v 13 Sa̠ onon ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ obhin o̠gba ami̠ omutiom.  
\v 14 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan egboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ obhin o̠gba o̠nu̠ o̠bhe̠la, d̠a̠ riku ya̠ awa ta̠ eleregi inyin bho̠.  
\v 15 Ezin bho̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠ga̠i o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ na̠ eloghom abar ya̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠rid̠ien d̠inyin ko orue d̠o̠ e̠damaghan, bo̠d̠o̠ e̠gba e̠ne̠gi̠me̠ni̠ nyen.  
\v 16 Ogbo ya̠ i̠mar itua̠n inyin eka̠-roweni na̠ rowede d̠inyin, a̠rumor na̠ a̠ghisia̠n, na̠ ra̠tologha̠n ta̠ ewol inyin. Sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ idi inyin.  
\v 17 Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠din ami̠ alo̠gh inyin a̠d̠ien.  
\v 18 Ya̠a̠, ekpo asi̠ghal e̠mu̠ d̠inyin ola̠ ta̠ akadi̠na a̠bhe ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 19 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠ ine ma̠ e̠ro̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ otenemeni ma̠ aru̠mu̠gh d̠inyin. 
\p  
\v 20 “Igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ka̠ ro̠lo̠gh ogbo-e̠gham na̠ eko ma̠ e̠ma A̠zeruse̠le̠m ekiton, bha̠ iloghome ma̠ obhel okunugi o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n.  
\v 21 Obhel o̠ku̠a, ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠ ekpo ma̠ eghil e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ rigu bho̠, ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io e̠ma bho̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a, ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ re̠sala aka e̠ma bho̠, ya̠ od̠i ma̠ ipa̠n a̠risisi bho̠ eka̠, omula̠ d̠o̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠.  
\v 22 Ezin bho̠ i̠nye̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ od̠e olo ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ma̠ omuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ya̠ u̠ge̠ uguri bho̠.  
\v 23 Ekulom anwani̠ a̠rughun na̠ anwani̠ amu̠gbo̠\f + \fr 21:23 \fq Anwani̠ amu̠gbo̠: \ft Anwani̠ ya̠ anwi̠i̠ny od̠i d̠a̠ agu̠o̠, sa̠ anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠mam amu̠mam.\f* d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠! Ezin bho̠ ibom i̠kparama ado̠l ta̠ emuzo d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠ na̠ ibom i̠gam ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ agam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n.  
\v 24 Idi awa ta̠ emugughu d̠a̠ alapa ogidi, sa̠ ta̠ obhin idi awa od̠ighom ikoli d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ rebhugh e̠mara̠nwunom. Sa̠ ogbo o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠ ta̠ ebhin a̠de ma̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, tu̠tu̠n ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom obhel ta̠ ogbo o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠. 
\p  
\v 25 “Relegh ta̠ emite d̠a̠ ogogo bho̠, na̠ uwetire bho̠ na̠ i̠ni̠nai̠ny bho̠. D̠a̠ a̠de onon sa̠ a̠d̠ugh ta̠ a̠bhin rebhugh bho̠, sa̠ e̠mi̠ oghur rabadi̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠gi̠o̠m anyu̠ ropoka̠n amu̠m bho̠, na̠ irorua̠ amu̠m o̠bhaghan na̠ okeleghel bho̠ ta̠ ed̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n.  
\v 26 A̠nwunom ta̠ e̠fu̠mu̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠rugugu i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emite d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Ezin bho̠ ra̠limon e̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ enyegia̠n.  
\v 27 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠, ya̠ na̠ a̠ru na̠ a̠limon na̠ ibom isosorogia̠n.  
\v 28 Igiel i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ e̠ke̠ na̠ emite, bha̠ ib̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠mara, ma̠ eb̠eka̠ ma̠ ekpon d̠a̠ anyu̠; ezin bho̠ oten\f + \fr 21:28 \fq Oten: \ft O̠wo̠l oten d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st omiza̠n i̠karabh, otenemeni e̠mu̠gh o̠ni̠\f* d̠inyin na̠ a̠tua̠n.” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: “Ikpone ma̠ oriren wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ a̠fig\f + \fr 21:29 \fq A̠fig: \ft Odi ad̠ien oriren d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l, ola̠ na̠ a̠guna̠ ma̠ a̠d̠igho, sa̠ i̠mu̠n na̠ ra̠lele d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠mu̠r na̠ emite ma̠ igiel a̠kozogh na̠ a̠ru.\f* bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ iriren bho̠.\fig O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ aku̠ ma̠ itu a̠fig|alt="Man picking figs" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 21:29" copy="LB00085" ref="21:29" \fig* 
\v 30 Igiel i̠mu̠nu̠mu̠n d̠awa na̠ e̠mu̠r na̠ emite, bha̠ inyin na̠ ologhom ma̠ a̠d̠io a̠kozogh na̠ a̠tua̠n.  
\v 31 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ka̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n na̠ emite, bha̠ iloghome ma̠a̠, irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n. 
\p  
\v 32 “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ amu̠m onon bho̠, ko omugughu d̠o̠ e̠man, kisa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite e̠man.  
\v 33 A̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny na̠ ta̠ eten emunia̠n, ya̠a̠ o̠nu̠-o̠kpe̠ d̠ami̠ ta̠ e̠ri̠la tu̠tu̠n ka̠ id̠ud̠ul.  
\v 34 I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠! O̠ni̠ ko oma̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠karabh i̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ i̠ku̠nu̠, na̠ e̠ye̠gha ogir o̠d̠a a̠min, na̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh a̠ghud̠um ma̠ odughumeni rologi d̠inyin, ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠bhin inyin awai̠  
\v 35 ma̠ agu̠o̠ abar ola̠ u̠kpati̠. I̠di̠ar i̠nye̠ ta̠ emutuma̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ a̠de no̠.  
\v 36 Igone ma̠ esiseiny kigiel kigiel, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin o̠te̠i̠ e̠mi̠ omiza̠n eb̠la̠ ra̠d̠ugh ya̠ ta̠ emite bho̠, na̠ orue o̠mara d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 37 Ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠, A̠zizo̠s atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ghan a̠nwunom d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠gha̠n ka̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ igu wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Oliv bho̠ ma̠ a̠d̠uga̠la̠n.  
\v 38 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠on gha̠n ib̠etina̠ ma̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠nagha i̠na d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. 
\c 22  
\s1 A̠ma̠ra̠nua̠n ogigh A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:1-5; Amaki̠ 14:1-2; Azo̠n 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n E̠yal Abe̠re̠di̠ Ya̠ Owubh D̠o̠ bho̠, wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠,  
\v 2 sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ku̠ro̠m d̠a̠ roloko bho̠ ima̠ra̠nua̠n ogigh A̠zizo̠s. Ya̠a̠, awa ighil a̠nwunom bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa ipuru d̠o̠ ma̠ elobhiri ma̠ osor. 
\s1 A̠zuda̠s na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ owol A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:14-16; Amaki̠ 14:10-11) 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ Eru Bho̠ a̠d̠igh A̠zuda̠s wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Iskari̠o̠t bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ologi a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠.  
\v 4 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan agu̠o̠ owol A̠zizo̠s onigha̠ awa.  
\v 5 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh awa ma̠ ologi ma̠ opa̠n, sa̠ awa ima̠ra̠nua̠n onigha̠ o̠yo̠ ma̠ ikpoki.  
\v 6 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠nua̠n awa, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan obhel ola̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n i̠na ma̠ owol A̠zizo̠s onigha̠ awa, b̠o̠ka̠ awa eb̠ol i̠na ma̠ obhel ola̠ a̠nwunom o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠kokod̠ia̠n od̠e E̠yal Opel Oten 
\r (Amatiu 26:17-25; Amaki̠ 14:12-21; Azo̠n 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 7 I̠se̠n wa̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ E̠yal Abe̠re̠di̠ Ya̠ Owubh D̠o̠ na̠ a̠lei bho̠, ta̠ ogigh o̠nyi̠ o̠nana i̠ko̠l E̠yal Opel Oten.  
\v 8 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom A̠pita̠ na̠ Azo̠n, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠gi̠e̠ ma̠ ka̠ ekokod̠ia̠n ed̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ i̠yar, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠yar od̠e ma̠ onin esi.” 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ken ka̠ okokod̠ia̠n e̠yal bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Agu̠o̠ bho̠ inyin ud̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rol afa amu̠m ta̠ abi̠ghan inyin. I̠tu̠o̠no̠me̠ i̠na ma̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ otu wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠pel a̠d̠igh bho̠,  
\v 11 ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠pura̠n anwa ma̠a̠: Oken e̠kpe̠ isuloma̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠ami̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠?’  
\v 12 Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠leriom inyin obom e̠kpe̠ otu ola̠ na̠ o̠mar oburi oguri d̠a̠ otu anyu̠. I̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ ekokod̠ia̠n ed̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ awa iten i̠gi̠, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠: sa̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ikokod̠ia̠n ed̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠. 
\s1 Ed̠ia̠n-e̠mu̠gh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amatiu 26:26-30; Amaki̠ 14:22-26; 1 Ako̠ri̠nt 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 14 Igiel obhel bho̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de.  
\v 15 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Na̠ ebhir ami̠ ka̠ obom igiel od̠igh na̠ inyin od̠e E̠yal Opel Oten onon, kisa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠gbika̠.  
\v 16 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ami̠ ko od̠e mu ma̠ ed̠ia̠n i̠nye̠n, a̠ten ka̠ na̠ omuzoghod̠iom d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin okpa̠ko a̠min bho̠, sa̠ ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ibhine ma̠ e̠ru̠gi̠an e̠d̠a.  
\v 18 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ami̠ ko o̠d̠a mu ma̠ a̠min a̠grep\f + \fr 22:18 \fq A̠grep \ft Odi a̠d̠ien oriren d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l, ola̠ na̠ amala sa̠ na̠ a̠mum itu ya̠ ubhelegi ma̠ a̠grep ola̠ na̠ obhin na̠ omutiom a̠min\f*, a̠ten ka̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru.” 
\p  
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin abe̠re̠di̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠puiny a̠nigha̠ awa, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Onon ozu d̠ami̠ wa̠ na̠ onigha̠ inyin bho̠. Igire ma̠ o̠ko̠no̠n ma̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 20 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa na̠ ed̠e e̠we̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Okpa̠ko onon omom i̠zo̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ola̠ na̠ ozu ma̠ asi̠ d̠ami̠, ma̠ obhin o̠ta inyin.  
\v 21 Ya̠a̠, ikpone! Agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol ami̠ bho̠, od̠i na̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ onin akpata od̠e bho̠.  
\v 22 Ta̠ ogir onigha̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ o̠to̠ oguri bho̠. Ya̠a̠, itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠!”  
\v 23 Sa̠ odi ake̠ ma̠ opura̠n odi ma̠a̠, a̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a bho̠? 
\s1 Aku̠anan o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa bho̠ 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ aku̠a̠nan a̠sor d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa ma̠a̠: “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ i̠na abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠?”  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Aru̠li̠le̠ma ogbo o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠, na̠ ebhin ibom a̠limon na̠ erileghom a̠nwunom d̠awa, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ awa na̠ erileghom bho̠ na̠ ebhelegi awa ma̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom.  
\v 26 Ya̠a̠, o̠ri̠la d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin. Ari̠la ka̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ i̠na aki̠r a̠pu; ya̠a̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠rileghom bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ ka̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu.  
\v 27 D̠a̠ inyin ka̠ a̠nyen abu̠gh a̠pu? I̠na wa̠ d̠a̠ akpata od̠e bho̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠na wa̠ na̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠? I̠na wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ akpata od̠e bho̠! Ya̠a̠, ami̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin ka̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ aru̠gi̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.  
\v 28 Inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh na̠ ami̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ rad̠agi̠an d̠ami̠.  
\v 29 Agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de irileghom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠dila̠de irileghom bho̠,  
\v 30 b̠o̠ka̠ inyin od̠igh na̠ ami̠ od̠e, o̠d̠a d̠a̠ akpata od̠e d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ irileghom d̠ami̠. Sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠ri̠la d̠a̠ ibom ra̠dila̠de irileghom, orileghom d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal roghol Izre̠l bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ ma̠ A̠pita̠ ta̠ aku̠a i̠na 
\r (Amatiu 26:31-35; Amaki̠ 14:27-31; Azo̠n 13:36-38) 
\p  
\v 31 “Asai̠mo̠n, Asai̠mo̠n, kpona̠! Eru Bho̠ na̠ a̠puru ma̠ onyegi eb̠la̠ inyin, ma̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ obhin ozeghema̠ na̠ ozeghe ma̠ i̠bu̠kpa.  
\v 32 Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠siseiny a̠nigha̠ nyam, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom ko od̠im d̠o̠. Igiel anwa na̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠, ghu̠ame̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠rumor d̠oyom.” 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n o̠tu̠o̠no̠m oyom o̠gi̠ ikoli sekina̠ omugh.” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran A̠pita̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠pita̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, kisa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r-e̠ma ta̠ alal a̠didon, anwa ta̠ aku̠a ami̠ i̠sar igiel ma̠ anwa na̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ami̠.” 
\s1 E̠kpa ikpoki, okuru, na̠ alapa ogidi 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Obhel bho̠ ami̠ iruom inyin ka̠ o̠gba ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ifugh ma̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠b̠ar na̠ o̠kara, e̠kpa, bo̠d̠o̠ agbaka ma̠ ebhin e̠gi̠ bho̠, abar ola̠ akparama inyin aro̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “E̠e̠nyi̠, abar ola̠ akparama i̠yar na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.” 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “A̠b̠eton i̠se̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ e̠kpa ikpoki a̠bhin; onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ okuru anya. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ alapa ogidi, a̠wol obom akapa d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ na̠ o̠lagha d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠ a̠gho ma̠ odi.  
\v 37 Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha inyin ma̠a̠, ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom abar wa̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠ire iwowa̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘U̠wal ani̠ i̠na o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ogbo id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.’\x - \xo 22:37 \xt Azaya 53:12\x* Sa̠, eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ i̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ami̠ bho̠ ta̠ emite ga̠i.” 
\p  
\v 38 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, kpone, i̠nye̠n i̠wal ipod̠i ralapa ogidi.” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “I̠marame̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠siseiny d̠a̠ Igu Oliv 
\r (Amatiu 26:36-46; Amaki̠ 14:32-42) 
\p  
\v 39 A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ igu Oliv ma̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠guri gha̠n na̠ a̠gir bho̠; sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 40 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠misi ma̠ esi bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kikiom awa ma̠a̠, “Isiseinye b̠o̠ka̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠te̠i̠ inyin.”  
\v 41 Sa̠ i̠na a̠toka̠n ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ ogbeiny d̠o̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpuluma̠n a̠siseiny ma̠a̠,  
\v 42 “O̠we̠de̠, ku̠gba ma̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom, si̠ghe̠ ma̠ okpa̠ko onon d̠a̠ ozu d̠ami̠; ku̠ku̠m eka̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠ami̠, aro̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom.”  
\v 43 [Sa̠ orileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru ra̠ aghu̠ame̠ni̠ i̠na.  
\v 44 Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emutuma̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ i̠na alo̠gh e̠mi̠ a̠siseiny ka̠ ate̠i̠ esi ola̠, onumor d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ e̠gharaghu̠ d̠a̠ a̠de ma̠ agu̠o̠ ikpokpogh asi̠.]\f + \fr 22:44 \ft Idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire bho̠ inwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ro̠go̠go̠ i̠nye̠n (43, 44)\f* 
\p  
\v 45 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ a̠siseiny bho̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh ka̠ awa na̠ ekod̠u d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠ku̠nu̠.  
\v 46 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ inyin na̠ okod̠u? Ib̠etina̠ ma̠ esiseiny, b̠o̠ka̠ ad̠agi̠an na̠ o̠te̠i̠ inyin.” 
\s1 Ub̠ol A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:47-56; Amaki̠ 14:43-50; Azo̠n 18:3-11) 
\p  
\v 47 I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh, sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iru. O̠ni̠ wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zuda̠s bho̠, odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠, a̠rileghom awa a̠ru. Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin i̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh\f + \fr 22:47 \fq I̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh: \ft A̠nwunom Izre̠l na̠ ebhin i̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh ab̠akagba na̠ ebhelegima̠ ma̠ ipelegima̠.\f* a̠bhelegi ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 48 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠zuda̠s, anwa na̠ a̠bhin ibheleguma̠ i̠pi̠pi̠o̠bh na̠ a̠wol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 49 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ eru ra̠ omite bho̠, sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar obhin ralapa ogidi bho̠ owe awa ke̠re̠?”  
\v 50 Sa̠ odi awa a̠sobh od̠iom a̠to ogoni ta̠ we̠mu̠ okur bho̠ a̠b̠uton. 
\p  
\v 51 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠: “Na̠ a̠bhon. O̠ni̠ ka̠ ogir o̠ku̠a!” Sa̠ i̠na a̠kula̠n a̠to o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠koko. 
\p  
\v 52 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ we̠mu̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ ikei bho̠, ya̠ iru ra̠ ob̠ol o̠yo̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n o̠ni̠ ke̠re̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ obhin ralapa ogidi na̠ re̠ba̠m na̠ oru ra̠ ob̠ol ami̠?  
\v 53 Ami̠ i̠ri̠la na̠ inyin ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ ka̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ya̠a̠ inyin ub̠ol d̠o̠ ami̠. Ya̠a̠, onon obhel d̠inyin wa̠ a̠limon a̠d̠io azi̠m na̠ a̠rileghom bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠pita̠ aku̠a ma̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 26:57-58; Amatiu 26:69-75; Amaki̠ 14:53-54; Amaki̠ 14:66-72; Azo̠n 18:12-18; Azo̠n 18:25-27) 
\p  
\v 54 Sa̠ awa ib̠ol i̠na irileghom i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, ya̠a̠ A̠pita̠ aro̠ ma̠ esi egbeiny atu̠o̠no̠m awa.  
\v 55 Obhel bho̠ awa na̠ egbonogi ma̠ anya d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io etire bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de ikiton anya bho̠, sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ awa ari̠la ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 56 Sa̠ odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu o̠nyani̠ a̠bhin e̠b̠alab̠al anya bho̠ a̠lelegi ma̠ A̠pita̠, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ onon ari̠la na̠ A̠zizo̠s.” 
\p  
\v 57 Sa̠ i̠na aku̠a a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “Ani̠ bho̠, ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ i̠na.” 
\p  
\v 58 O̠nyi̠-o̠gbara obhel a̠ten, sa̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ abi̠gh i̠na sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa odi o̠ni̠ awa.” 
\p Ya̠a̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ bho̠, ami̠ ani̠ d̠o̠!” 
\p  
\v 59 Obhel a̠ten, sa̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ ari̠la ma̠ ofugh ofugh ma̠a̠, “Kagu̠o̠ kagu̠o̠ u̠gba, i̠na odi o̠ni̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na ola̠ Agalili.” 
\p  
\v 60 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ bho̠, ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar anwa na̠ agba.” I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ awi̠oghan sa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r-e̠ma bho̠ alal.  
\v 61 Sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon A̠pita̠. Sa̠ i̠na aru̠ru̠an ikpo a̠fugh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, ya̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na bho̠, ma̠a̠, “Anwa ta̠ aku̠a ami̠ ma̠ i̠sar igiel kisa̠ e̠nu̠r ta̠ alal a̠didon.”  
\v 62 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mite d̠a̠ etire ka̠ a̠leghe agba igbir. 
\s1 Ogbo e̠gham bho̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ed̠ul i̠na 
\r (Amatiu 26:67-68; Amaki̠ 14:65) 
\p  
\v 63 Ogbo e̠gham ya̠ na̠ ekponom A̠zizo̠s bho̠, i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na ed̠ul i̠na.  
\v 64 Sa̠ awa ibhin abar ibinom a̠rid̠ien d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ isorogiom i̠na ma̠ adi̠e̠l ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Wa̠, ma̠ agba ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠b̠or anwa bho̠.”  
\v 65 Sa̠ awa ikpon abar abar ifugh i̠na, ikpon i̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠. 
\s1 U̠marame̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ a̠misigh ikei ebhugh 
\p  
\v 66 A̠d̠io ab̠al a̠sor, sa̠ ikei irileghom bho̠, na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, ikokod̠ia̠n id̠igh ezue, sa̠ irileghom A̠zizo̠s ka̠ i̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo aru̠mu̠ i̠to̠ ebhugh d̠awa.  
\v 67 Sa̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st bho̠ ke̠re̠.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ i̠gba eka̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, inyin ko oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠,  
\v 68 ka̠ ami̠ ipura̠n inyin abar eka̠, inyin ko oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ o̠wo̠ran ami̠.  
\v 69 Ya̠a̠ ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon a̠pu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 70 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a bha̠ anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, d̠u̠ko̠?” 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, “Od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa i̠gba bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 71 Sa̠ awa i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Ezin ola̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠tu̠n o̠bho̠ro̠gh opa̠n onyob̠a̠ d̠a̠ e̠kal abar onon, od̠i ke̠re̠? I̠yar na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n abar bho̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠.” 
\c 23  
\s1 Ubhin A̠zizo̠s ka̠ o̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Apai̠let 
\r (Amatiu 27:1-2; Amatiu 27:11-14; Amaki̠ 15:1-5; Azo̠n 18:28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠egina̠ irileghom A̠zizo̠s ka̠ i̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Apai̠let\f + \fr 23:1 \fq Apai̠let: \ft Odi we̠mu̠ irileghom ebhugh A̠rom\f* 
\v 2 Sa̠ awa iler i̠na ma̠ riku\f + \fr 23:2 \fq Riku: \ft Ikpon a̠d̠ien kerekere igunugha̠ ebhin eb̠ologiom i̠na\f*, ib̠ologiom i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar u̠bi̠gh ka̠ o̠ni̠ onon na̠ abho̠ro̠gh od̠ineni ebhugh d̠i̠yar, sa̠ na̠ a̠kigima̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom otua̠ otua̠-ebhugh onigha̠ A̠siza̠, sa̠ na̠ are̠ma ma̠ i̠na Akrai̠st, O̠li̠le̠ma.” 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠pura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Anwa O̠li̠le̠ma a̠nwunom A̠zu ke̠re̠?” Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa i̠gba bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠tiba̠ra̠ adama ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠ni̠ onon a̠gir api̠e̠ d̠a̠ riku wa̠ inyin uleregi i̠na bho̠.”  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠gba o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ a̠bhin atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠tumugi ma̠ a̠nwunom osorogi akpe̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ A̠zudia̠, ob̠eton d̠a̠ Agalili esi bho̠ i̠na ake̠ bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ra̠ ate̠i̠ enen.” 
\s1 Ubhin A̠zizo̠s ka̠ o̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ E̠ro̠d 
\p  
\v 6 Igiel bho̠ Apai̠let amu̠gho̠n e̠kal onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n ku̠gba ma̠ A̠zizo̠s o̠nyi̠ eghun Agalili.  
\v 7 Igiel bho̠ i̠na ra̠ a̠loghom ma̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠i d̠a̠ ebu i̠to̠ ta̠ E̠ro̠d bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom awa ma̠ obhin A̠zizo̠s o̠gi̠o̠m E̠ro̠d. A̠sora̠n ola̠ E̠ro̠d na̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ma̠ obhel obha̠.  
\v 8 Obhel igiel E̠ro̠d abi̠gh A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhon ologi ma̠ ibom, ezin bho̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gon o̠bi̠gh ani̠ A̠zizo̠s. I̠na na̠ amu̠gho̠n o̠du̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠b̠em ologi ma̠ o̠bi̠gh obhel A̠zizo̠s ta̠ a̠gir ilologia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 9 I̠na a̠bhin obhel a̠pura̠n A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠ien kerekere ipura̠n, ya̠a̠ ekpo abar ola̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 10 Ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ ogbo a̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi bho̠, i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ emulughuom i̠na, na̠ eb̠ologiom i̠na ma̠ ibom ib̠ologiom.  
\v 11 A̠ga̠i E̠ro̠d na̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham d̠o̠yo̠ eka̠, esorogiom i̠na ma̠ adi̠e̠l, e̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na. Sa̠ ibhin obom ob̠eb̠i akapa aru̠li̠la iburi i̠na, sa̠ imulumeni i̠na i̠gi̠o̠m Apai̠let.  
\v 12 A̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠ sa̠ E̠ro̠d na̠ Apai̠let itulugia̠n iten ra̠tologha̠n; ma̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien. 
\s1 Usobh ase̠ obhumeni ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ ogigh o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 27:15-26; Amaki̠ 15:6-15; Azo̠n 18:39; Azo̠n 19:16) 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠kokod̠i ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, na̠ ikei ogbo ya̠ na̠ erileghom ebhugh bho̠, na̠ a̠nwunom bho̠,  
\v 14 sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin ubhin o̠ni̠ onon oruom ami̠, o̠gba ma̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tumugi ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ osorogi akpe̠. Ami̠ na̠ ad̠a i̠na a̠kpon d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠inyin, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, ami̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ ezin ola̠ odin osobh ase̠ obhumeni o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ riku ya̠ inyin uleregi i̠na bho̠.  
\v 15 E̠ro̠d eka̠ na̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ i̠na api̠e̠, obha̠ ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠mulumeni i̠na a̠ruom i̠yar bho̠. Inyin o̠mar o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠, abar ola̠ o̠ni̠ onon api̠o̠m ola̠ odin ogigh o̠yo̠ o̠lo̠gh bo̠.  
\v 16 D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh i̠na, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man i̠na ma̠ oten oyel.”  
\v 17 [D̠a̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠, akpe̠ ma̠ Apai̠let omutiom odi o̠ni̠, d̠a̠ awa ogbo ya̠ u̠lo̠gh ikoli bho̠ onigha̠ awa]\f + \fr 23:17 \ft D̠a̠ idi igbainy ra̠d̠ire bho̠ o̠go̠go̠ onon bo̠.\f* 
\v 18 Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ibhin onin okoroko emulughu, e̠gba ma̠a̠, “Si̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon ma̠ ebhin ka̠ egigh, ma̠ a̠mutiom Abarabas a̠nigha̠ i̠yar!”  
\v 19 (Abarabas o̠ni̠ ola̠ u̠du̠o̠m d̠a̠ ikoli, d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh na̠ ipa̠n ogbo a̠sorogi ma̠ rakpe̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, na̠ owia̠n oghum a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ obhin, sa̠ a̠gigh o̠ni̠ nyen.)  
\v 20 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠nwe a̠bhelegi awa a̠kikiom, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ abho̠ro̠gh omutiom A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 21 Ya̠a̠, awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ omulughu omulughu izul ma̠a̠, “I̠du̠ i̠na ma̠ egigh d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠! I̠du̠ i̠na ma̠ egigh d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠!”  
\v 22 Sa̠ i̠na a̠nwe a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ oleghemeni i̠sar igiel ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, i̠na a̠gir a̠kere a̠d̠ien i̠karabh? Ami̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ ezin ola̠ odin ogigh o̠yo̠. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom o̠gu̠ro̠gh o̠yo̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom i̠na.” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ izul izul i̠nyagh ma̠a̠, o̠du̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren ogigh, sa̠ Apai̠let a̠ma̠ra̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 24 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠sobh ase̠ bho̠ a̠guri ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ epuru bho̠.  
\v 25 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mutiom d̠a̠ ikoli bho̠ ma̠ Abarabas, o̠ni̠ wa̠ awa i̠bho̠ro̠gh omutiom onigha̠ awa bho̠, wa̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ipa̠n ogbo a̠sorogi ma̠ rakpe̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠, na̠ owia̠n oghum a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ obhin bho̠, sa̠ a̠gigh nyen o̠ni̠ bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton A̠zizo̠s alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠awa ma̠ ogir abar rologi d̠awa ibhir. 
\s1 U̠du̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ogigh d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren 
\r (Amatiu 27:32-44; Amaki̠ 15:21-32; Azo̠n 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 26 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ erileghom A̠zizo̠s na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ awa isibh Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ A̠sirin bho̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ i̠na na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠. Sa̠ awa inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ ma̠ orol o̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 27 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na d̠a̠ aman. Idi a̠nwunom d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ anwani̠, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠.  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “E-e anwani̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m! O̠ni̠ ko o̠tu̠n ami̠ ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir, ya̠a̠ i̠gba ma̠ igbir egboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin sekina̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin.  
\v 29 Ezin bho̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ eru d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ma̠ igiel ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘E̠b̠e̠l re̠mar anwani̠, na̠ a̠rutu-i̠mara ya̠ ta̠ o̠mara̠gi̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, na̠ aru̠mu̠mam ya̠ ta̠ o̠nigha̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny amu̠mam bho̠.’  
\v 30 Sa̠ 
\q1 “ ‘Awa ta̠ e̠le̠gh rigu bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Imele ma̠ ebhum i̠yar!” 
\q2 Sa̠ awa ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ efugh enigha̠ ma̠ a̠rugugum bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ikpegiome i̠yar!” ’ 
\m  
\v 31 Ku̠gba ma̠ a̠nwunom na̠ egir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n obhel ola̠ oriren bho̠ od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ omom, ka̠a̠, ere ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ obhel ola̠ oriren bho̠ na̠ aghi̠ghara?”  
\v 32 Awa irileghom ipa̠n i̠wal a̠nwunom, ibom id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, e̠b̠aram na̠ A̠zizo̠s ebhin e̠gi̠ ka̠ ogigh.\fig I̠du̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren|alt="They nailed Jesus to the Cross" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 23:32" copy="LB00328" ref="23:32" \fig* 
\v 33 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ imisi d̠a̠ esi wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ “Okpokoro E̠mu̠ Bho̠,” sa̠ awa i̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren. Awa i̠b̠aram na̠ ibom id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ e̠du̠ d̠a̠ re̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an iriren, odi d̠a̠ agba od̠iom d̠o̠yo̠, uwed̠i d̠a̠ ekiel.  
\v 34 [Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mution okoroko ma̠a̠, “O̠we̠de̠, we̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠awa ma̠ a̠nigha̠ awa! Ezin bho̠, awa iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar awa na̠ egir.”]\f + \fr 23:34 \ft I̠nye̠n bo̠ d̠a̠ idi igba̠iny ra̠d̠ire ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠\f* Sa̠ awa irobh okob̠a̠\f + \fr 23:34 \fq Irobh okob̠a̠: \ft Wa̠ ate̠i̠ e̠nai̠ny sa̠ a̠bhin e̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ukpe bho̠. \f* ma̠ o̠loghom agu̠o̠ awa ta̠ ebhin e̠ru̠gi̠an ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 35 A̠nwunom i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ ekpon; ya̠a̠, ogbo aru̠mu̠ bho̠ sa̠ isorogiom i̠na ma̠ adi̠e̠l ma̠a̠, “I̠na a̠tenemeni gha̠n ipa̠n ogbo; i̠se̠n i̠na a̠tenemeni ani̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, ku̠gba ma̠ i̠na Akrai̠st, O̠ni̠ Wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Aso̠n bho̠ ga̠i.”  
\v 36 Ogbo e̠gham bho̠ eka̠ e̠d̠igh ani̠ esorogiom i̠na ma̠ adi̠e̠l, \x - \xo 23:36 \xt Raso̠r 69:21\x*sa̠ inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠min a̠viniga̠\f + \fr 23:36 \fq A̠min a̠viniga̠: \ft Odi a̠d̠ien a̠min ola̠ a̠gba̠gba̠m d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ma̠ o̠d̠a\f*.  
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ iduom i̠na ifugh ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ anwa O̠li̠la ebhugh ogbo A̠zu ga̠i, bha̠ tenemeni ma̠ ozu d̠oyom.”  
\v 38 Elegh ola̠ u̠du̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ d̠a̠ agba e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠, “ONON O̠LI̠LE̠MA OGBO A̠ZU.”  
\v 39 Odi od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh wa̠ u̠b̠aram u̠du̠ u̠ke̠ri̠ bho̠ eka̠, a̠duom i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Tenemeni ma̠ ozu d̠oyom, ma̠ ab̠ar na̠ i̠yar a̠tenemeni!”  
\v 40 Ya̠a̠, od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh uwed̠i agam a̠nigha̠ i̠na, a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ya̠! Ya̠! Anwa na̠ oghila̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ke̠re̠, ma̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon na̠ i̠yar u̠te̠i̠ onin e̠kal ebhum ase̠ bho̠?  
\v 41 D̠a̠ agba d̠i̠yar, sa̠ a̠sora̠n agu̠o̠ usobh ase̠ bho̠ ubhumeni i̠yar bho̠, ezin bho̠ i̠yar na̠ ob̠u ma̠ asu̠wo̠ i̠karabh ya̠ i̠yar ugir bho̠. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ onon na̠ o̠pi̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ abar.”  
\v 42 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s, siseiny ru̠ru̠ane̠ ami̠ ma̠ igiel anwa na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom d̠oyom.”  
\v 43 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, a̠didon anwa ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ ami̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ Ob̠eb̠i A̠lei bho̠.” 
\s1 Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:45-56; Amaki̠ 15:33-41; Azo̠n 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 44 A̠d̠io bho̠ aro̠ ka̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ azai̠ny, sa̠ azi̠m a̠ru ra̠ a̠kpegiom eb̠la̠ a̠de bho̠ tu̠tu̠n ate̠i̠ i̠sar aki̠lo̠ki̠ d̠a̠ etita̠n a̠d̠io.  
\v 45 Sa̠ e̠b̠alab̠al ogogo bho̠ a̠d̠im; sa̠ ukpe wa̠ ubhin usobhom a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, agu̠an d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io aru̠gi̠an i̠wal a̠bin.\fig Ukpe wa̠ a̠sobhom a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠|alt="The cotton that covered the Holy Place" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 23:45" copy="LB00265" ref="23:45" \fig* 
\v 46 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin obom okoroko ed̠i a̠mulughu ma̠a̠, “O̠we̠de̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠eton e̠mu̠gh d̠ami̠ na̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom.” O̠gba o̠ku̠a o̠we̠le̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ ekpo-epobh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠sobha̠n.  
\v 47 Igiel bho̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠rileghom o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ abi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠tutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠mutiom okoroko ma̠a̠, “Ya̠ a̠ga̠i, onon aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala\f + \fr 23:47 \fq O̠ni̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala: \ft O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠pi̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ abar, sa̠ a̠rugh ib̠eb̠i a̠ma̠rugh na̠ ado̠l igielake̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠\f*.”  
\v 48 Igiel bho̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ isor esi bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, sa̠ awa ikonya̠ imula̠ iyel na̠ i̠ku̠nu̠.  
\v 49 Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ iloghom i̠na bho̠, ka̠ u̠b̠aram na̠ anwani̠ ya̠ i̠ke̠ d̠a̠ Agalili i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na bho̠, i̠mara ma̠ esi egbeiny ekpon i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n. 
\s1 A̠ma̠d̠i ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amatiu 27:57-61; Amaki̠ 15:42-47; Azo̠n 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 50 Odi ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠rugh ado̠l igielake̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ aro̠, i̠na odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ Ogbo I̠to̠ A̠zu.  
\v 51 (Ya̠a̠, i̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠to̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ iyed̠i.) I̠na ola̠ e̠ma Ari̠mati̠a d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠zudia̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ ebhiroma̠ na̠ a̠gon eruoma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 52 I̠na agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ Apai̠let a̠puru ma̠ ozu\f + \fr 23:52 \fq Ozu: \ft Egua̠de bho̠\f* ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 53 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠soroni ma̠ egua̠de bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin ob̠eb̠i ukpe asi̠ni̠ni̠n a̠bhurugi ma̠ egua̠de bho̠. I̠na asu̠ ma̠ egua̠de bho̠ awe̠le̠ sa̠ a̠bhin ka̠ a̠d̠i d̠a̠ omom od̠i, esi ola̠ ub̠u d̠a̠ o̠gbi̠o̠ma umutiom, ola̠ ta̠ od̠i d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.  
\v 54 Obha̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ A̠kokod̠ia̠n ob̠a̠ra̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠-epobh. Obhel bho̠ aro̠ ka̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ osira̠ epobh d̠awa.  
\v 55 Anwani̠ ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Agalili id̠igh na̠ A̠zizo̠s iru bho̠, i̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zose̠fu̠ ka̠ emisi d̠a̠ ogugua̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠bi̠gh a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ ubhin u̠mu̠ni̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ egua̠de bho̠ d̠a̠ ologi.  
\v 56 Sa̠ awa imula̠ iyel i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠gu̠a ma̠ i̠gagaman i̠gho̠gho̠\f + \fr 23:56 \fq I̠gagaman i̠gho̠gho̠: \ft I̠gho̠gho̠ ya̠ obhin owuri egua̠de bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ na̠ o̠nu̠r ab̠o̠r\f* na̠ relo ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠. Ya̠a̠, awa esira̠ ma̠ epobh A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠-epobh bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ oloko bho̠ ato̠ bho̠. 
\c 24  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh 
\r (Amatiu 28:1-10; Amaki̠ 16:1-8; Azo̠n 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 I̠b̠ala A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠a̠ma̠ d̠a̠ esi-a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ anwani̠ bho̠ ib̠on ib̠etina̠ ma̠ obom ame̠ghe̠le̠, sa̠ ibhin i̠gho̠gho̠ ed̠ue̠nu̠nu̠\f + \fr 24:1 \fq I̠gho̠gho̠ ed̠ue̠nu̠nu̠: \ft I̠gho̠gho̠ ya̠ awa ibhin isigh gha̠n omumugh o̠ni̠, ma̠ o̠b̠aram owuri egua̠de bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ o̠nu̠r ab̠o̠r\f* ya̠ awa i̠gbe̠ bho̠ iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠.  
\v 2 Awa i̠bi̠gh ka̠ na̠ od̠ur okpegima̠ od̠i bho̠ otenemeni d̠a̠ a̠d̠ukun,  
\v 3 ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ awa id̠igh d̠a̠ ologi bho̠, awa i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ ozu ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 4 Igiel bho̠ awa od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ abar bho̠, sa̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom imite ma̠ awai̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ aka d̠awa, na̠ ibura̠ ya̠ na̠ esosorogia̠n ka̠ i̠me̠me̠gi̠na e̠nai̠ny.  
\v 5 D̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠rugugu wa̠ a̠sibh awa bho̠, sa̠ awa izuda̠ id̠i ma̠ ra̠misigh d̠awa d̠a̠ a̠de. Ya̠a̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ipura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “A̠mite eka̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io imumugh?  
\v 6 I̠na bo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n; i̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh! I̠ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ inyin igiel bho̠ i̠na aro̠ na̠ inyin d̠a̠ Agalili bho̠,  
\v 7 ma̠a̠, ‘Ta̠ ob̠eton O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh, sa̠ ta̠ o̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren ogigh. Oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.’ ”  
\v 8 Sa̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an iloghoma̠n o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠. 
\p  
\v 9 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠ imula̠ iyel bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gba ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n inigha̠ ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ onin ogbo ogir bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom iyed̠i.  
\v 10 A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠, na̠ A̠zoana, na̠ A̠meri onweni ta̠ A̠zemsi, na̠ ipa̠n anwani̠ ya̠ id̠igh na̠ awa irile bho̠, i̠gba ma̠ abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ogir bho̠.  
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n i̠gu̠b̠an ibhelebhel o̠nu̠ d̠a̠ ra̠to ilobhiri bho̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠ghon, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a awa id̠umom d̠o̠.  
\v 12 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, A̠pita̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠kpo ma̠ eghil agi̠ d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠. I̠na a̠zuma̠n anwi̠nagi̠an d̠a̠ ologi od̠i bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh i̠go̠ro̠go̠r a̠rukpe asi̠ni̠ni̠n ya̠ ubhin ubhurugi ma̠ egua̠de bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠de ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpon bo̠ a̠mula̠ a̠yel, a̠bhin obhel aru̠ru̠an a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠.\fig O̠gbe̠o̠ma a̠kpegiom o̠nu̠ od̠i bho̠|alt="A stone covered the entrance to the tomb" src="Louise Bass" size="col" loc="Luke 24:12" copy="LB00329" ref="24:12" \fig* 
\s1 Erile e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Eten E̠mayo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 16:12-13) 
\p  
\v 13 Onin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, idi i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ A̠zizo̠s irile na̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma E̠mayo̠s, esi erile ola̠ a̠lei agu̠o̠ od̠ua̠l amai̠l\f + \fr 24:13 \fq Amai̠l: \ft Owewegh a̠tobi: ubhin d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ A̠b̠ekei; amato̠ eweghe esi erile, od̠i ka̠ a̠tobi i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ i̠wal e̠wala (880) a̠kub̠u.\f* ma̠ obhin d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ka̠ o̠te̠i̠.  
\v 14 Sa̠ awa od̠i na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠.  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ awa agbo̠gbu̠an a̠rile.  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠sibhom ma̠ ikpo a̠rid̠ien d̠awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ko orue d̠o̠ elelegi i̠na. 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ orile na̠ o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an o̠ku̠a na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ ere?” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠mara kpom ikonya̠ na̠ i̠ku̠nu̠.  
\v 18 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ i̠wal awa, wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠kilopas bho̠, awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa ku̠ku̠m o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠ru ma̠ isuloma̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, ola̠ ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite ma̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠ d̠u̠ko̠?” 
\p  
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “A̠kere a̠d̠ien i̠di̠ar imite?” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t bho̠. I̠na aro̠ ma̠ owil ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom ilelegi, d̠a̠ ebula̠ e̠mi̠ a̠limon o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 20 Ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ na̠ ipa̠n ogbo aru̠mu̠ d̠i̠yar ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠, ib̠eton i̠na e̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ ogigh, sa̠ i̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren igigh;  
\v 21 ya̠a̠, i̠yar ubhin i̠na ob̠em ologi ma̠ i̠na Witenemeni wa̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ o̠bhe̠l ebhugh Izre̠l bho̠. O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, a̠didon oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n imite.  
\v 22 O̠ku̠a bha̠, idi anwani̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠i̠yar ogbo ya̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na bho̠, iru ra̠ i̠gba ma̠ asu̠gbagba ya̠ id̠igh i̠yar ilologia̠n o̠mu̠gho̠n. Awa iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ od̠i d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠ a̠didon,  
\v 23 ya̠a̠ awa i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ologi. Sa̠ awa imula̠ iru ra̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠yar ma̠a̠, awa i̠bi̠gh aghi̠m ola̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ imutuma̠ awa e̠gba ma̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um!  
\v 24 Sa̠ idi ogbo ya̠ id̠igh na̠ i̠yar i̠ro̠ bho̠, iten i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠ ma̠ o̠bi̠gh ani̠. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, awa i̠bi̠gh od̠i bho̠ ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ anwani̠ bho̠ i̠gba bho̠, ya̠a̠ awa i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s.” 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Rema̠ a̠nwunom! Agu̠o̠ na̠ akparama inyin od̠umom eb̠la̠ iwowa̠ ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ iwa̠ bho̠.  
\v 26 U̠gba d̠o̠ o̠se̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, Akrai̠st bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ abi̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu i̠nye̠n kisa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ten a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin obhel agba ase̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ iwowa̠ ya̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ i̠na d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ od̠ud̠ul bho̠, ob̠eton d̠a̠ ra̠d̠ire ta̠ A̠mozizi ka̠ ate̠i̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ i̠ge̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ etua̠n e̠ma wa̠ awa na̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile a̠ten awa a̠kue a̠d̠ighi woma̠ i̠na od̠idia̠ na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠.  
\v 29 Yaa̠, awa ikikiom i̠na e̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, “To̠ na̠ i̠yar. I̠se̠n na̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule, okpegi osor a̠sughonom.” Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ awa aro̠. 
\p  
\v 30 Igiel bho̠ i̠na aro̠ d̠a̠ akpata od̠e bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin abe̠re̠di̠, sa̠ a̠tutumeni, sa̠ i̠na a̠puiny a̠b̠eton a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 31 I̠se̠ kisa̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa i̠kpakpagi̠na sa̠ awa ililegi i̠na. D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ i̠na amai̠ny ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa.  
\v 32 Sa̠ odi a̠tiba̠ra̠ a̠kpon odi a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “To̠ ti̠to̠i̠ny ku, i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠yar igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh na̠ i̠yar a̠rile bho̠, ikul d̠o̠ ma̠ rologi d̠i̠yar ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 33 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠ sa̠ awa imula̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m. Sa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh d̠iobh na̠ onin ogbo ogir bho̠, na̠ ipa̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh gha̠n awa na̠ erile bho̠, na̠ ekokod̠ia̠n i̠se̠  
\v 34 na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i! Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh, sa̠ na̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n nyen.”  
\v 35 Sa̠ i̠wal awa ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ E̠mayo̠s imula̠ iru bho̠ eka̠, i̠gba ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imutuma̠ awa d̠a̠ eten bho̠, sekina̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ awa ibhin ilelegi i̠na, ma̠ obhel bho̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton abe̠re̠di̠ a̠puiny a̠ni̠gha awa bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amatiu 28:16-20; Amaki̠ 16:14-18; Azo̠n 20:19-23; Rogir 1:6-8) 
\p  
\v 36 Awa od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an i̠nye̠n, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ agu̠o̠ a̠mite amara d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, sa̠ a̠du ma̠ o̠gho̠r a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ekima̠ aro̠ na̠ inyin.” 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠ ikpa̠ra̠numa̠, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa, ezin bho̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ awa i̠bi̠gh egua̠de.  
\v 38 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ o̠tu̠n ere na̠ okpa̠ra̠noma̠. Ezin ka̠ ere wa̠ rologi d̠inyin na̠ e̠gba i̠wal i̠wal bho̠?  
\v 39 Ikpone ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠sike d̠ami̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ ologhom ma̠ ami̠ na̠ agu̠o̠. Ikula̠ne ami̠ ma̠ ekpon; egua̠de na̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ipulupul ozu o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ na̠ i̠kpo̠kpo̠, ma̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh ozu d̠ami̠ bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 40 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mutiom okoroko onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠leriom awa ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 41 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, awa id̠umom d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ awa imuzo na̠ a̠libhon ologi na̠ ilologia̠n. Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin onwuna̠ abar od̠e ma̠ i̠se̠n ke̠re̠?”  
\v 42 Sa̠ awa ib̠eton o̠bhu̠gi̠an ena̠ i̠nigha̠ i̠na,  
\v 43 sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ena̠ bho̠ a̠puron awa d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa. 
\p  
\v 44 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “I̠nye̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ i̠kpe̠re̠me̠ni̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin igiel bho̠ ami̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠a̠, ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi bho̠, na̠ a̠riwil bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire Raso̠r bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 45 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kpekpegion rologi d̠awa ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.  
\v 46 Sa̠ i̠na a̠nimeta̠n awa ma̠a̠, “U̠ge̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠a̠, Akrai̠st ta̠ abi̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mugh, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.  
\v 47 U̠b̠aram u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠, ta̠ o̠ke̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m obhin a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠, o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba ya̠ otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh, na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh onigha̠ o̠ni̠, o̠saragi̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom.  
\v 48 Inyin ronyob̠a̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n.  
\v 49 Ami̠ ta̠ afi̠ri̠ma inyin abar wa̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ a̠gua̠n bho̠; o̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ tu̠tu̠n a̠limon ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ra̠ ate̠i̠ inyin.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhun d̠a̠ Ote̠nai̠ny 
\r (Amaki̠ 16:19-20; Rogir 1:9-11) 
\p  
\v 50 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rileghom awa a̠mutiom ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠, sa̠ a̠b̠egion aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ agi̠o̠m anyu̠, sa̠ a̠tutumeni awa.  
\v 51 Od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ ologi agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠tutumeni awa bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠toka̠n ad̠u̠a d̠awa, sa̠ ukpobh i̠na ubhuneni d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny.  
\v 52 Sa̠ awa ikpud̠ia̠n i̠ko̠l i̠na, sa̠ awa imula̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m na̠ ibom a̠libhon ologi.  
\v 53 Sa̠ awa ibhin eb̠la̠ obhel d̠awa, i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ itututumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.